\id MAT TA - Hona Bible
\h MATTA
\toc1 MATTA
\toc2 MATTA
\toc3 MATTA
\mt1 Matta
\mt2 Laɓara na Mbǝnggǝn aten Yeeso
\imt1 Katǝra laɓaara
\im Matta tal ahur fa fatsahaya Yeeso ndǝn chirethgha ɗeleewar ɗiya. Laɓara na Mbǝnggǝn aten Yeeso yi Matta pǝrangɗǝ ndaarha ƙǝm Yeeso Ƙǝrǝsti ni. Ndǝghǝnni tǝ hǝrǝkrha lǝɗangna Faara ɗǝf miighǝn a nafiyighǝn ahu Ɗeleewar Faara tǝ Peɗǝnda yi ƙǝtǝm. Laɓarɗi na Mbǝnggǝn ya mbǝ a Yahudaya katendan wa, amma a ƙǝshiirha kahad. Chireethleng Matta ǝnggina hai katǝragha hai tǝtal-tǝtal. Katǝranggǝn hai tǝ laɓar nggǝtta Yeeso, tǝ mbaptisǝmadghǝn tǝ ƙǝƙǝrrǝghǝn. Tǝ ƙǝm kwamanɗi katǝrang nǝn pǝr laɓar Faara, tǝ tsahadghǝn ha, tǝ ƙǝnang nda fiya a Nggalili. Pǝrɗǝ laɓar wiid Yeeso thliinǝn a Nggalili ɗǝnǝn Urshalima ɗǝ; tǝ ǝngya katǝragha hai atenggǝn har tawang nanda ɗǝ tǝ thliidghǝn sǝ ahu mǝra. Laɓara na Mbǝnggǝn aten Yeeso yi Matta kyadɗa ndǝn a pǝpal tǝ ndaarha Yeeso Ƙǝrǝsti mamnda tǝmalǝmnda ni. Nǝghǝn tǝ sǝsǝmnda yi fǝlang nda Ngyakhrha Faara hai ma Musa.
\ip Tsahang Matta hai pǝmnggǝn tuf: 1. Tsahad Yeeso ha a mbǝrha na ɗangkam, aten ǝngya kamngga a tsauka wangya Kutǝryid Faara (5-7). 2. Tsahang ɗǝ fatsahayighǝn ha kumkap sǝri, kwamana kamngga a ǝna taara nda mǝmǝl (10). 3. Na karapu sǝ ɗǝɗamǝn-ɗǝɗamǝn tsahana Yeeso ha aten kutǝryid Faara (13). 4. Kwamana na a tsauka tǝ mbu samad Yeeso (18). 5. Tsaha ɗaha aten mii ngwala ƙǝshiirha tǝ ǝngya na a katǝrarha hai a farɗi (24-25). Əngya na ahurghǝn.
\io1 Chichiiya Yeeso tǝ nggǝttǝghǝn hai 1:1-25; 2:23
\io1 Tarya ǝnana Yahaya tǝ Mbaptisǝma 3:1-12
\io1 Mbaptisǝmad Yeeso tǝ ƙǝƙǝrrǝghǝn 3:13-17; 4:11
\io1 Tarya ǝnana Yeeso a chehweed Nggalili 4:12, 18:35
\io1 Mal Yeeso Nggalili ɗǝgha Urshelima ɗǝ 19:1-30; 20:34
\io1 Mii ngwala tar Yeeso a Urshelima 21:1-46; 27:30
\io1 Taurha Yeeso ɗǝ tǝ mǝrrǝghǝn 27:32-66
\io1 Thlid Yeeso sǝ hu mǝra tǝ kyatta fadghǝn 28:1-20
\ib
\c 1
\s1 Chichiiya Yeeso
\r (Luka3:23-38)
\p 
\v 1 Kulo thlǝmngya chichiiya Yeeso Ƙǝrǝsti ya, chichid Ndauda tǝ Ibrahim.
\b
\li1 
\v 2 Ibrahim nggǝtgha Ishaku,
\li1 Ishaku nggǝtgha Yakubu.
\li1 Yakubu nggǝtgha Yahuda tǝ wan manggighǝn.
\li1 
\v 3 Yahuda nggǝtgha Peres tǝ Dzara. Ma ndan ndǝna Tamar.
\li1 Peres nggǝtgha Hesron,
\li1 Hesron nggǝtgha Aram,
\v 4 Aram nggǝtgha Aminadab,
\li1 Aminadab nggǝtgha Nashon,
\li1 Nashon nggǝtgha Salmon.
\li1 
\v 5 Salmon Nggǝtgha Mboz. Man ndǝna Rahap.
\li1 Mboz nggǝtgha Obed. Man ndǝna Ruth.
\li1 Obed nggǝtgha Djeshi,
\li1 
\v 6 Njessi nggǝtgha kutǝra Ndauda.
\li1 Ndauda nggǝtgha Sulemanu. Man ndǝna Mbasheba, nu mǝra Uriya.
\li1 
\v 7 Sulemanu nggǝtgha Rehobom,
\li1 Rehobom nggǝtgha Abidja,
\li1 Abidja nggǝtgha Asa,
\li1 
\v 8 Asa nggǝtgha Djehoshafat,
\li1 Djehoshafat nggǝtgha Djoram,
\li1 Djoram nggǝtgha Adzariya,
\li1 
\v 9 Adzariya nggǝtgha Djothlam,
\li1 Djothlam nggǝtgha Ahas,
\li1 Ahas nggǝtgha Hedzekiya,
\li1 
\v 10 Hedzekiya nggǝtgha Manasa,
\li1 Manasa nggǝtgha Aman,
\li1 Aman nggǝtgha Djosiya,
\li1 
\v 11 Djosiya nggǝtgha Djekoniya \f + \fr 1:11 \fk Djekoniya:\ft sǝn ndan ƙǝm tǝ thlǝma “Djehoyakin”. Ƙǝlang 2 Kutǝrya 25:27\f* tǝ wanmanggighǝn, a sayidɗi ƙǝsang ngganda nafiya Yahuda ngyaɓang tsaurha nda kanda fa hu chehweed Mbabila ɗǝ.\x * \xo 1:11 \xt 2 Kutǝrya24:14-15; 2 Ɗeleewar fa sǝngya36:10; Irmiya27:20\x*
\b
\li1 
\v 12 A kwasamadɗi ɗǝna nda tǝ kanda a Mbabila ɗǝ, Djokoniya nggǝtgha Sheyaltiyel,
\li1 Sheyaltiyel nggǝtgha Dzerubabel,
\li1 
\v 13 Dzerubabel nggǝtgha Abihudu,
\li1 Abihudu nggǝtgha Eliyakim,
\li1 Eliyakim nggǝtgha Adzor,
\li1 
\v 14 Adzor nggǝtgha Dzadok,
\li1 Dzadok nggǝtgha Akim,
\li1 Akim nggǝtgha Eliyud,
\li1 
\v 15 Eliyud nggǝtgha Eleyadza,
\li1 Eleyadza nggǝtgha Mattan,
\li1 Mattan nggǝtgha Yakubu,
\li1 
\v 16 Yakubu nggǝtgha Yisufu, chimad Mairamu.
\li1 Mairamu nggǝtgha Yeeso na nda aarha Ƙǝrǝsti.
\b
\m 
\v 17 Chichiiya kumkap faɗa a thlakh mbǝd Ibrahim ɗǝgha thlakh mbǝd Ndauda ɗǝ. Thliirha a thlakh mbǝd Ndauda ɗǝgha hu sayidɗa ɗǝ ngyaɓang nanda tsaurha kanda fa a Mbabila, chichiiya kumkap faɗa ni. Thiirha ƙǝm a sayidɗi mal nanda Mbabila ɗǝgha hu sayidɗa ɗǝ nggǝt nanda Ƙǝrǝsti chichiiya kumkap faɗa ni.
\s1 Nggǝtta Yeeso
\r (Luka2:1-7)
\p 
\v 18 Kulo kwaman nggǝtta Yeeso Ƙǝrǝsti ya. A sayidɗi ngwanna Yisufu Mairamu man Yeeso, amma kanda kula kakhrha, ƙǝlagha Mairamu hai, nǝghǝn ahur yi Sǝsǝna tǝ Peɗǝnda.
\v 19 Yisufu ka niifa ni mbǝ midghǝn sǝ a fǝrang shilee nǝn Mairamu a yid fiya wa, ahu numadghǝn na midghǝn sǝ a kalghǝnǝn hai ɓǝɓee.
\v 20 Amma ndǝghǝn hu numadɗi kee, ɓagha tǝthlǝnda Faara thlǝmadghǝn ɓa hu sǝsǝniirha ndanggǝn, “Yisufu, wan Ndauda, a tǝrǝmna kakh Mairamu wa, ƙǝsǝr huryidɗi keeghǝn yi Sǝsǝna tǝ Peɗǝnda ni.
\v 21 Nǝn a nggǝt wee hǝshin, ɗǝfang thlǝma na Yeeso\f + \fr 1:21 \fk Yeeso:\ft Thlǝmɗi “Yeeso” tǝ mii Helenaya ni, ndǝna “Djeshiwa” tǝ mii Ibraniyaya. Thlǝmɗi ndaarha ni, “Faara tǝ hǝrǝkrha ni”\f* Ƙǝsǝr ndǝghǝn ni a hǝrghang nafiyighǝn ahu ɗimiyid ndan.”
\p 
\v 22 Ənggini heu ya katǝra nǝn hai ka a lǝɗang ngganda ˈya ndana annabi.
\b
\q1 
\v 23 “Na wutararha a ɗǝfrha hur nggǝt wee hǝshin nǝn
\q2 ɗǝfang thlǝma nda Imaniyel.”
\m Thlǝmɗi ndaarha ni, “Faara nǝghǝn tǝ ƙǝm ha.”\x * \xo 1:23 \xt Ishaya7:14\x*
\p 
\v 24 Mehenna Yisufu sǝ a ɓeena, takkwa ǝn ɗanǝn pǝrangna tǝthlǝnda Faara, kahanggǝn Mairamu.
\v 25 Amma sǝngwa ndǝn wee nuwun wa, ƙǝl a kwasamadɗi nggǝt nǝn wee hǝshin, ɗǝfang thlǝma nǝn Yeeso. \x * \xo 1:25 \xt Luka2:21\x*
\c 2
\s1 Ɓad fasǝngya ɓa a man kyad yanfaara
\p 
\v 1 Akwasamadɗi nggǝt nanda Yeeso a Mbaitalami ahu chehweed Yahudiya, a thlakh mbed kutǝryid Hirdus, ɓagha fasǝngya a Urshelima ɓa a man kyad yanfaara ɓa.
\v 2 Tsakh mee nda, “Ai wanɗi nggǝt nanda kutǝr Yahudaya? Na ɗan wufǝlngarghǝn a man kyad yanfaara, ɓa nan ɓa ka a tǝrang shilee nan in.”
\p 
\v 3 Hǝrǝmna kutǝra Hirdus sǝkƙǝn kee, ɓillagha kaan, heu tǝ nafiya Urshelima.
\v 4 Tǝrgha wumanggǝn mamngya firistaya ɓa, tǝ fasǝngya ngyakhrha Musa, tsahang mee nǝn kanda, “A yanggi na nda a nggǝt Ƙǝrǝsti?”
\p 
\v 5 Ndang ngganda, “Ahu tal Mbaitalami hu chehweed Yahudiya, ƙǝsǝr chirethlengga annabi hai kee tǝ ndaarha:
\b
\q1 
\v 6 ‘Amma sa ƙǝm Mbaitalami na hu chehweed Yahudiya,
\q2 ƙǝɗiwa ahur kutǝryid wupǝriya Yahuda wa.
\q1 Ƙǝsǝr a fadwa na kutǝra a kyarha ɓa,
\q2 nǝn a tsaurha tǝ lafrha nafina Isǝreela.’ ” \x * \xo 2:6 \xt Meka5:2\x*
\b
\p 
\v 7 Tǝrgha Hirdus aah fasǝnggina nǝn ɓa ɓǝɓee, tsahang mee nǝn kanda sayidɗi na nanda wufǝlngarɗi.
\v 8 Thlǝn kanda nǝn Mbaitalami ɗǝ ndanggǝn kanda, “Ɗama ɗǝ ɗun sǝye laɓar wanɗa ɓa ya tǝ sammayirha. A walangɗun, ɓamaɓa ɓun pǝreƙǝn nggima ɗiyaɗǝ ɗi tǝrang shilee teena.”
\p 
\v 9 A kwasamadɗi sǝk nanda laɓarɗi ki kutǝra, thlii nda wii fayindan nda. Wufǝlngarɗi ˈwa nanda narha a man kyad yanfaara ɓa nagha a mbendan ɗǝgha isha a mbǝɗi na wanɗa sǝ.
\v 10 Na nanda wufǝlngarɗi tǝk mbǝnda nda fa kaan.
\v 11 Kyana nda mindǝɗa hai, na wanɗa nda tǝ man Mairamu, ɓǝra nda hai tǝrang shilee nda teena. Tǝrgha inang ngganda yawayindan ɗǝ fǝrang tǝfaasa nda tǝ urdi tǝ mur.
\p 
\v 12 Yanang ngganda kanda ahu sǝsǝniirha a wunda tǝ thlǝmad Hirdus wa, nanǝn kee wuɗa nda tal ndan ɗǝ tǝ kwamana pak.
\s1 Ɗanda Yisufu tǝ Mairamu a Masar ɗǝ
\p 
\v 13 A kwasamadɗi wiina fasǝnggini, tǝrgha tǝthlǝnda Chinǝm ɓagha thlǝmad Yisufu ɓa hu sǝsǝniirha ndanggǝn, “Thliusǝ, tǝrang wanɗi tǝ man ɗaana tǝ kanda a Masar ɗǝ. Tsawama a mbǝɗi ƙǝl a pǝrang ɗi ndǝn kun, ƙǝsǝr Hirdus nǝn a kaɗa wanɗi a ɓǝlanggǝn.”
\p 
\v 14 Tǝrgha thliigha sǝ tǝranggǝn wanɗi tǝ man a fǝɗigɗi wiigha Masar ɗǝ.
\v 15 Tsawa nda a mbǝɗi ƙǝl merna Hirdus. Ənɗiya katǝra nǝn hai ka a lǝɗang ngganda ǝnɗi ndaana Chinǝm a mii annabi, “Aah yi waana ɓa a Masar.” \x * \xo 2:15 \xt Hodzaya11:1\x*
\s1 Ɓǝlang Hirdus wangya hǝshya na nggu-ngguchit a Mbaitalami
\p 
\v 16 Ƙǝlana na Hirdus hai fasǝnggini na a man kyad fara ɓa pǝpǝlǝk ndan hai, sǝbgha hurghǝn ɗǝ kaan. Thlǝnanggǝn sodjaya ɗǝ a ɓǝlangganda wangya hǝshya ɗǝ na nggu-ngguchit a Mbaitalami tǝ tulayighǝn, sǝlna hura yindan sǝri tǝ fingya sǝlwawa, mǝmǝlla sayidɗi pǝrangna fasǝnggini kyana wufǝlngarɗa ɓa.
\p 
\v 17 Tǝrgha ˈya thlǝkna annabi Djermiya lǝghǝdɗǝ:
\b
\q1 
\v 18 “Sǝkɗǝm huhwaarha a Ramah,
\q2 tǝrha tǝ thlee hura,
\q1 Rachal a tǝrha ka wanggighǝn
\q2 karɗǝ nggabrha fa,
\q1 ƙǝsǝr mǝr wanggighǝn ɗǝ.” \x * \xo 2:18 \xt Irmiya31:15\x*
\s1 Wutta Nadzarat ɗǝ
\p 
\v 19 A kwasamadɗi mǝrna Hirdus, tǝrgha tǝthlǝnda Chinǝm kyad fadghǝnǝn a Yisufu hu sǝsǝniirha a Masar,
\v 20 ndanggǝn, “Thliusǝ tǝrang wanɗiya tǝ man wuɗana chehweed Isǝreela ɗǝ, ƙǝsǝr nafini na a kaɗa yiɓǝd wanɗi mǝr nda ɗǝ.”
\v 21 Tǝrgha Yisufu thliigha sǝ, tǝranggǝn wanɗi tǝ man wuɗa nda chehweed Isǝreela ɗǝ.
\p 
\v 22 Amma sǝknǝn wan Hirdus, Arkilus ni hu tsǝnggam chin, a ǝna kutǝryirha a chehweed Yahuda, tǝrǝm ɗǝrha nǝn mbǝɗaɗǝ. Yanangganda hu sǝsǝniirha a ɗǝɗa ɗǝ wa, tǝrgha kyalthgha chehweed Nggalili ɗǝ.
\v 23 Ɗǝgha tsaurha ahu tala na nda aarha Nadzarat, lǝghǝdgha ˈya thlǝkna annabiya: “Na nda aaghǝn Tǝnadzarat.”
\c 3
\s1 Tsahad Yahaya Tǝbaptisǝma
\r (Markus1:1-8; Luka3:1-18; Yahaya1:19-28)
\p 
\v 1 Akwasamad huraya Yahaya Tǝbaptisǝma a pǝr laɓar Faara a fiya a kaheerha na a chehweed Yahuda,
\v 2 nagha a ndaarha, “Malaman ɗimiyid nun, ƙǝsǝr Kutǝryid Talara nduwusɗa ɓa.”
\v 3 Niif ɗani ndaana annabi Ishaya:
\b
\q1 “Urarha a aah farha a kaheerha,
\q2 ‘Tangsaaman kwamana Chinǝm sǝ,
\q2 pǝpǝnaman kwaman sarya ɗǝ a ndǝghǝn.’ ” \x * \xo 3:3 \xt Ishaya40:3\x*
\b
\p 
\v 4 Luwud Yahaya ǝnagha ndan tǝ was thlǝkhmu, ƙǝnanggǝn muwun tǝ paama. Ənnadghǝn mii mbeerha tǝ aam ɗee. \x * \xo 3:4 \xt 2 Kutǝrya1:8\x*
\m 
\v 5 Fiya na a Urshalima tǝ Yahudiya heu tǝ chehweeya kahad na a mii kufad Urdun ɗǝnda thlǝmadghǝn ɗǝ.
\v 6 Kanda a pǝr ɗimiyid ndan, nagha a ǝnang mbaptisǝma kanda a kufad Urdun.
\p 
\v 7 Amma nana Yahaya Farisaya tǝ Sadukiyaya hangga a ɓarha mbǝɗa ɓa nǝn a ǝnang mbaptisǝma fiya sǝ, ndanggǝn kanda, “Kun huthlingya! Wun ƙǝsgha thlǝmad nun a ɗa sǝsad Faara nun hai na ɓayi?
\v 8 Ənama ˈya kyadgha ndaarha malangɗun ɗimiyid nun.
\v 9 A numaɗun ndon kee, ‘Chichid nǝm ni Ibrahim, mbǝ Faara a sǝsang ƙǝm wa.’ Niya ndang nda kun na Faara tǝ sǝsǝmnda ha na a ǝnang wundakhnaya nǝn Ibrahim sǝ tǝ feryini ya.
\v 10 ˈWanda teena pangnda wurra a kul ɗǝfrha, kala ɗǝfrha mbuwa nggǝtta ngga nanda kyathlang nda ɗǝ muwangganda ahu waarha ɗǝ.
\v 11 Niyi a ǝnang mbaptisǝma kun tǝ aama. Amma niifa sǝ na ɓayi kalgha nggi mu, tsǝkki na a kwasanggi sahad pahamggǝn hai wa, ndǝghǝnggi ɓanǝn ǝnang mbaptisǝma kun tǝ Sǝsǝna tǝ Peɗǝnda tǝ waarha.
\v 12 Nǝghǝn tǝ ɗeng pǝra ha, nǝn a pǝrang ɗiɗiirha ɗǝ ngwanggǝn wan hwalidghǝn ahu ɓirukkun hai. Nǝn a njang nda ɗiɗidghǝn ɗǝ tǝ waarha mbuwa mǝra hai.”
\s1 Mbaptisǝmad Yeeso
\r (Markus1:9-11; Luka3:21-22)
\p 
\v 13 Tǝrgha Yeeso thliigha a Nggalili ɗǝgha kufad Urdun ɗǝ ka a ǝnangga Yahaya mbaptisǝma.
\v 14 Amma Yahaya karɗafa a ǝnang mbaptisǝma nǝn Yeeso, ndǝghǝn, “Kamɗǝ sani ǝne mbaptisǝma. Kama na ɓarha thlǝmanna ɓa?”
\p 
\v 15 Nggǝmangga Yeeso ndǝghǝn, “Nanǝnya ngwa tsauka kee, ƙǝsǝr kamɗǝ a lǝɗanggǝm ǝngya heu na mid Faara.” Tǝrgha nggǝmngga Yahaya fa.
\p 
\v 16 Hǝrǝm nanda ǝnang mbaptisǝma Yeeso, kyanǝn sǝ ahur aamɗi kee, tǝrgha talara inggaɗǝ na Sǝsǝn Faara nǝn a tǝra hai ƙǝla tǝtiliurha tsauka a tenggǝn.
\v 17 Sǝk urarha nda a talara hai, “Waana niya, nggǝmni, niyi a tǝk mbǝndǝghǝn fa kaan.”
\c 4
\s1 Ƙǝƙǝrang Sheetan Yeeso
\r (Markus1:12-13; Luka4:1-13)
\p 
\v 1 Tǝrgha Sǝsǝna tǝ Peɗǝnda ɗǝgha tǝ Yeeso a kaheerha ɗǝ ka a ƙǝƙǝrangga sheetan. \x * \xo 4:1 \xt Ibraniyaya2:18; 4:15\x*
\v 2 Yeeso karɗǝ aama yi ɓeena kumnggit faɗa nda fǝɗigrha tǝ yan fara. Akwasamdghǝn ƙǝsgha miirha ndǝn.
\v 3 Tǝrgha sheetan ɓagha thlǝmadghǝn ɓa ndanggǝn, “Ana Wan Faara ni sa, tsawang feryini ya ka mburodi.”
\p 
\v 4 Amma nggǝmangga Yeeso ndanggǝn, “Nǝghǝn chichirethlee hai hu ɗeleewar Faara:
\b
\q1 ‘Mbǝ tǝ mburodi kee na niifa ƙǝra sǝ wa,
\q2 amma tǝ laɓaara na kyarha ɓa a mii Faara.’”
\b
\p 
\v 5 Tǝrgha sheetan tǝranggǝn Urshelima ɗǝ wupǝri tǝ Peɗǝnda, tǝranggǝn ten Ƙǝn Faara sǝ na a Urshelima.
\v 6 Ndanggǝn, “Ana Wan Faara ni sa, puru hweeɗe hai, ƙǝsǝr nǝghǝn chichirethlee hai hu ɗeleewar Faara,
\b
\q1 ‘Nǝn a ndang fathlǝnggighǝn a nggawo wa nda sǝ,
\q2 tǝ haryindan na nda a nggawo sǝ,
\q2 amana ɗǝghang sarwa feera fa.’ ”
\b
\p 
\v 7 Nggǝmangga Yeeso, “Nǝghǝn chichireethlee hai, ‘a ƙǝƙǝrangna Chinǝm Faarwa wa.’ ”
\p 
\v 8 Nggǝrgha Sheetan tǝrang nda a ten wumnda sǝ na nzang kyaɗang kutǝryid ƙǝshiirha nǝn heu tǝ mamnggitghǝn.
\v 9 Ndanggǝn, “Ənggini heu ya niya furo ƙǝn, a ɓǝrna hai fǝree mamnggirha na.”
\p 
\v 10 Ndangga Yeeso, “Kalu kwamanna hai, Sheetan! Ƙǝsǝr nǝghǝn chichirethlee hai hu ɗeleewar Faara:
\b
\q1 ‘Tǝtani a ɗǝfang shilee na Chinǝm Faarwa in,
\q2 ndǝghǝn katenggǝn na fǝrang mamnggirha.’ ”
\b
\p 
\v 11 Tǝrgha Sheetan mal Yeeso nǝn. Ɓagha fathlǝngya Faara ɓa ƙǝlaghǝn ndaha.
\s1 Ƙatǝrang Yeeso targhǝn hai a Nggalili
\r (Markus1:14-15; Luka4:14-15)
\p 
\v 12 Sǝkna Yeeso muwang nda Yahaya hu porsǝna ɗǝ, mal Yahudiya nǝn ɗǝgha Nggalili ɗǝ. \x * \xo 4:12 \xt Matta14:3; Markus6:17; Luka3:19-20\x*
\v 13 ˈWa ɗǝrha nǝn Nadzarat ɗǝ a wudgha Kafarnahum ɗǝ na a mii wuri aama tǝ tsaurha, na a chehweed Dzebulu tǝ Naftali. \x * \xo 4:13 \xt Yahaya2:12\x*
\v 14 Ƙǝsǝr a lǝɗang ngganda ˈya ndana annabi Ishaya tǝ ndaarha:
\b
\q1 
\v 15 “Chehwed Dzebuluna tǝ chehweed Naftali,
\q2 kunna a kwaman wuri aama, tǝ ƙǝsǝr kufad Urdun,
\q1 tǝ ƙǝm chehweed Nggalili yi fingya mbuwa wa Yahudaya.
\q2 
\v 16 Nafiya na tsaurha a wula nanda kukwaryirha kaan,
\q2 Fingya na tsaurha a mishim mǝrra kyad kukwaryirha ɓa.”\x * \xo 4:16 \xt Ishaya9:1\x*
\b
\p 
\v 17 Ka a farɗi ndǝn katǝrangna Yeeso pǝr laɓar Faara hai, nagha a ndaarha, “Malaman ɗimiyid nun, ƙǝsǝr Kutǝryid Talara nduwusɗa ɓa.” \x * \xo 4:17 \xt Matta3:2\x*
\s1 Katǝrang Yeeso wur fatsahayighǝn hai
\r (Markus1:16-20; Luka5:1-11)
\p 
\v 18 Nana Yeeso a wiirha hai a mii wuri aam Nggalili, na nafiya nǝn sǝri a wanmanggi nda Siman na nda aarha Mbiturus tǝ wanman Andǝrawus. Na nda a ƙǝs tǝngya tǝ panggamnggi ndan ahu wuri aamɗi ƙǝsǝr fa ƙǝs tǝngya ni.
\p 
\v 19 Tǝrgha Yeeso ndanggǝn kanda, “Mbuwama samadna, niya tsawang kun fa ƙǝs fiya ɓa.”
\v 20 Tsu a mbǝɗi kee malangganda panggamnggi ndan mbu samadghǝn nda.
\p 
\v 21 Chik nǝn ɗǝrha mbeeɗǝ, nggǝrghǝn na nafiya sǝri a wanmanggi, Yakubu wan Dzabadi tǝ wanman na Yahaya. Kanda ahu kombuwol chii ndan Dzabadi, a tangsang panggamnggi ndan ɗǝ, aagha Yeeso kanda.
\v 22 Tsu a mbǝɗi kee malangganda kombuwol ndan tǝ chi ndan mbu samadghǝn nda.
\s1 Tsahad Yeeso ha tǝ ƙǝm ƙǝnang ɗǝ fiya
\r (Luka6:17-19)
\p 
\v 23 Yeeso wengɗǝ chehweed Nggalili kahad nagha a tsahang fiya ha hu ƙǝn tsahad Yahudaya nagha a pǝr Laɓara na Mbǝnggǝn yi kutǝryid Faara, tǝ ƙǝnang nda fiya natǝ wanhaya ɗǝɗamǝn tǝ ɓeerha farha.
\v 24 Laɓarghǝn ɗǝɗa ɗǝ inggun ta Suriya ɗǝ. Ɓang haya nda ɓa, heu tǝ fingya natǝ wanhaya fa ɗǝɗamǝn-ɗǝɗamǝn, fingya ƙǝnangna ǝnkaheeya kanda hai, tǝ kachelya tǝ fingya mǝrna fandan hai, ƙǝnanggǝn kanda heu.
\v 25 Fiya hangga mbuwa samadghǝn, fingya a Nggalili ɓa, fingya hu chehweerha ɓa na nda aarha talya kum, fingya a Urshelima ɓa tǝ Yahudiya tǝ fingya ƙǝm a pǝm kufad Urdun ɓa.
\c 5
\s1 Tsahad Yeeso ha aten parka a wumnda
\p 
\v 1 Hǝrǝmna Yeeso na fiya wumnda hai hangga, tǝrgha wumnda sǝ tsauka hai. Ɓagha fatsahayighǝn thlǝmadghǝn ɓa,
\v 2 katǝranggǝn tsahang kanda ha.
\s1 Parka r (Luka 6:20-23)
\q1 
\v 3 Fa parkayani nafiya sǝnggasǝ fa yamiya ni hu sǝsǝna,
\q2 ƙǝsǝr Kutǝryid Talara yi ndanni.
\q1 
\v 4 Fa parkayani nafiya na a tǝrha nanǝnya,
\q2 ƙǝsǝr na nda a nggab kanda.
\q1 
\v 5 Fa parkayani nafiya mbuwa tǝrang tendan sǝ,
\q2 ƙǝsǝr na nda a har langad ƙǝshiirha.
\q1 
\v 6 Fa parkayani nafiya na miirha a ƙǝsa tǝ hushim nggayirha;
\q2 ƙǝsǝr nun a nggaala!
\q1 
\v 7 Fa parkaya ni nafiya na fiya a haɗang kanda fa,
\q2 ƙǝsǝr na nda a haɗang Faara fa.
\q1 
\v 8 Fa parkayani nafiya na hur ndan chahal,
\q2 ƙǝsǝr na nda ana Faara.
\q1 
\v 9 Fa parkayani nafiya na ɓang tsau ɗǝɗemnggirha,
\q2 ƙǝsǝr na nda aah kanda wangya Faara.
\q1 
\v 10 Fa parkayani nafiya na a sǝsaarha ka nggayirha,
\q2 ƙǝsǝr Kutǝryid Talara yi ndanni.
\b
\p 
\v 11 Fa parkayani kun, ana fiya a ˈyar kun, sǝsangganda kun, kanda a nggaɓa kun tǝ ndaarha fa mbǝlfeeya ni kun, ƙǝsǝr ka nggi.
\v 12 Ənama wutsǝfayirha tǝ tǝk mbǝnda fa, nun wal ƙǝnaghǝn hangga a talara. Ƙǝsǝr annabiya na ƙǝtǝm sǝsangganda kanda kee.
\s1 Tsahad Yeeso ha aten fǝsa tǝ kukwaryirha
\r (Markus9:50; Luka14:34-35)
\p 
\v 13 Kunni fǝs ƙǝshiirha. Amma a tǝr mbǝnda fǝsa ɗǝ, ƙǝƙǝn nǝm nggǝr nggǝrang ɓa? Ɓalwa targhǝn sǝ wa, ƙǝl iraɗǝ kee ishangga fiya hai.
\p 
\v 14 Kunni kukwaryid ƙǝshiirha. Wupǝri na a mbǝrha na ɗangkam mbǝ ɓǝɓeerha hai wa.
\v 15 Tǝ ƙǝm mbǝm njang patilla tsǝɓanggǝm tǝ tǝɓa wa. A meghedghǝn nǝm ɗǝfang nda a mbǝd wagrǝghǝn tǝnǝn fǝrang kukwaryirha fiya na ahur mindǝɗi.
\v 16 Nǝghǝn kee ƙǝm, ngwa njargha kukwaryid nun hai a mbed fiya naghǝn nda, tǝna kowunni fal Chinun na a talara. \x * \xo 5:16 \xt 1 Mbiturus2:12\x*
\s1 Tsahad Yeeso ha aten ngyakhrha
\p 
\v 17 A numaɗun ndon ɓani ɓa ka ɓi weleng ngyakhrha Musa ɗǝ tǝ yi annabiya wa. Ɓawi ɓa ka ɓi weleng kanda ɗǝ wa, amma ka ɓi lǝɗang nda kanda.
\v 18 Niya pǝrang ƙǝkafek kun, ƙǝl ma ngwala talara tǝ hweeɗe, mbǝ ˈyasǝ na ngguchit a ƙǝtta ɗǝ hu ngyakhrha Musa wa, ƙǝl ma lǝghǝdɗǝ heu.
\v 19 Kala niifa tǝɗangga yanɗi na ngguchit ahu ngyakhkini teena ya, tsahang nggǝnǝn fiya ha ƙǝm, nǝn a tsaurha ngguchit hu Kutǝryid Talara. Kala niifa ƙǝm ǝnagha taara tǝ ngyakhkiniya tsahanggǝn nǝn fiya ha ƙǝm nǝn a tsaurha manggǝn hu Kutǝryid Talara.
\v 20 Niya ndang nda kun, a kalwa nggayid nun yi fasǝngya ngyakhrha Musa tǝ yi Farisaya wa, mbun tam kyarha hu Kutǝryid Talara ɗǝ wa.
\s1 Tsahad Yeeso ha aten sǝbrha hura
\r (Luka12:57-59)
\p 
\v 21 “Sǝkɗun ˈya ndang nanda chichiyinǝm kaar tǝ ndaarha, ‘A ɓǝlɗun farha wa, kala niifa ɓǝlgha farha na a nda a ngwang kumarha sǝ.’
\v 22 Amma nggi ƙǝm niya ndang nda kun, kala niifa sǝbna hurghǝn ɗǝ tǝ shadghǝn na nda a ngwang kumarha sǝ. Niya nggǝr ndang nda kun niifa ndangga shadghǝn, ‘Ka wuɗe,’ na nda ɗǝrha tǝghǝn mbed fa ngwa kumaaya ɗǝ. Amma niifa ndangga shadghǝn, ‘Nura!’ na nda a muwang nda hu waarha ɗǝ mbuwa mǝra hai.”
\p 
\v 23 “Tsaunǝn kee, a nanna a fǝr ǝn fǝrrǝwa a Faara a mbǝd sataka, a ɗalna teena hai sǝɓang na hur shadwa ɗǝ,
\v 24 malu ǝn fǝrrǝwa a mbǝd sataka. Ɗuwa ɗǝ ˈwan ɗun tangsang pathlang nun tǝ shadwa, tǝrgha a ɓana ɓa, ɓa ɗǝrha mbeeɗǝ tǝ fǝrrǝwa.
\v 25 A huhwad niifa sa, kaɗu kwamana na a tangsanggun pathlang nun ƙǝkar kapa nun sǝla kǝn ngwa kumarha ɗǝ. A karna fa, ɗǝnǝn tǝsa a mbed tǝ ngwa kumarha ɗǝ. Tǝ ngwa kumarha ƙǝm nǝn fǝrang sa wan sǝsalya. Wan sǝsalya ƙǝm na nda muworha hu porsǝna.
\v 26 Niya pǝro ƙǝkafek, mba kyarhaɓa wa ƙǝl tiina ǝnɗi kyo nanda heu.”
\s1 Tsaharha Yeeso ha aten kulafayirha
\p 
\v 27 “Sǝkɗun ndǝn tǝ ndaarha, ‘A ǝnanna kulafayirha wa.’
\v 28 Amma nggi ƙǝm niya ndang nda kun kala niifa ƙǝlangga nuneefa sunaghǝnǝn ˈwaɗǝ teena ǝnaɗǝ kulafayirha tǝghǝn ahurghǝn.
\v 29 A kyo yidwa yisǝma hu ɗimiyirha hai, kutethleng sǝ muwangga ɗǝ. A nggushi ƙǝɗeng na patu tal a fadwa ma muwangganda fadwa heu ahu waarha ɗǝ mbuwa mǝra hai.
\v 30 Ana harwa yisǝma a kyorha hu ɗimiyirha hai, kyathlang ɗǝ muwangga ɗǝ. A nggushi ƙǝɗeng na patu tal a fadwa ma muwangganda fadwa heu ahu waarha ɗǝ mbuwa mǝra hai.”
\s1 Tsahad Yeeso ha aten mǝrra kakhrha
\r (Matta19:9; Markus10:11-12; Luka16:18)
\p 
\v 31 “Thlǝk ndan tǝ ndaarha, ‘Kala niifa kalgha nukkun hai tsawang ɗafa tǝta a chireethleng ɗeleewar nǝn sǝ yi kala hai.’
\v 32 Amma nggi ƙǝm niya ndang nda kun kala niifa kalgha nukkun hai a mbǝ aten ɗimid kulafayirha wa, kyang nǝn hu kulafayirha hai. Kala niifa ƙǝm kakhka nuneefa kal nanda hai ǝnanǝn kulafayirha.”\x * \xo 5:32 \xt Matta19:9; Markus10:11-12; Luka16:18; 1 Korontiyaya7:10-11\x*
\s1 Tsahad Yeeso ha aten ɗǝfmee
\p 
\v 33 “Nggǝr ɗun sǝkƙǝn a mii chichiiyi nǝm kaar tǝ ndaarha, ‘A tǝɗang ɗun ˈya in ndaanun a Faara wa, amma ƙǝsaama ɗǝfmi nun ha ǝna nun a Chinǝm.’
\v 34 Amma nggi niya ndang nda kun, a ɗǝf ɗun mee tǝ thlǝm talara wa, ƙǝsǝr mbǝd tsawud Faara ni.
\v 35 A ɗǝf ɗun mee tǝ thlǝm hweeɗe wa, ƙǝsǝr ndǝna mbǝd yiɓǝd sar Faara. A ɗǝf ɗun mee tǝ thlǝm Urshalima wa, ƙǝsǝr wupǝri ni yi Faara, kutǝra na manggǝn.
\v 36 A ɗǝf ɗun mee tǝ thlǝm ten nun wa, ƙǝsǝr mbun mbang nggǝrang was nun hai tsauka pǝpet nduwa iˈim wa.
\v 37 ˈYa kamngga kee, ‘Yoo’ tsauka ‘Yoo,’ tǝ ƙǝm ‘Awo’ tsauka ‘Awo.’ Kala laɓaara kalgha yanɗamu ya kyaghǝn ɓa a mii tǝmbǝlfedɗi.”
\s1 Tsahad Yeeso ha aten nggǝr haara mu
\r (Luka6:29-30)
\p 
\v 38 “Sǝkɗun ndǝn tǝ ndaarha, ‘Yirha a meghed yirha, thlaana a meghed thlaana.’ \x * \xo 5:38 \xt Kyarhaɓa21:24; Livitikus24:20; Ɗeleewar fa ngwa kumaya19:21\x*
\v 39 Amma niya ndang nda kun, a karɗun tǝ mbǝlfeerha fa wa. A mbi niifa sa hu ƙǝmeng wa yisǝma, kyakhrang man patu ɓa ƙǝm.
\v 40 A huhwad niifa sa ka a thlanggǝn luwudwa, fǝrang kaɓad wa ƙǝm.
\v 41 A ngyaɓo niifa hu wiirha hai mel tal, weema ɗǝ kyab mel sǝri.
\v 42 Kala niifa hwanowa ˈya, fǝrang, kala niifa kaɗagha kumarha a harwa a ˈyaɗang na wa.”
\s1 Nggǝmama fa tsangginun
\r (Luka6:27-28,32-36)
\p 
\v 43 “Sǝkɗun ndǝn tǝ ndaarha, ‘Nggǝmama tula yinun kar fatsan ngginun nun.’ \x * \xo 5:43 \xt Livitikus19:18\x*
\v 44 Amma niya ndang nda kun, nggǝmama fa tsangginun, hwana man Faara nafiya teena na a sǝsang kun.
\v 45 A naɗun kee, nun tsaurha wangya Faara na a talara, ƙǝsǝr nǝn fǝr yanfaara a ka nafiya tǝ fa mbǝlfeeya. Nǝn ɓa ˈyaara a nafiya na tǝ nggayirha fa tǝ fingya mbuwa tǝ nggayirha fa.
\v 46 Ana ɗun a nggǝm nafiya na a nggǝm kun kee, ƙǝƙǝn nun wal parka? Ko fathlǝ tsamngya ni ma mbǝna nda ǝnaarha kee wa?
\v 47 A naɗun a ǝna nggayirha a pashiyi nun kee, ma nun a ǝnaarha kalgha fingya mu? Mbǝna fa ɗahaya ǝnaarha kee wa?
\v 48 Amma tsawama lǝlǝgɗa ƙǝla nana Chinun na a talara lǝlǝgɗa.”
\c 6
\s1 Tsahad Yeeso ha aten ǝnfǝra
\p 
\v 1 Kwarama a kyad ɗun nggayirha a mbed fiya ka a na kun nda wa. A ǝna ɗun kee, mbun wal ƙǝnaghǝn a har chinun na a talara wa.
\p 
\v 2 A naɗun a fǝra a kalɗun miighǝn ɗǝ ƙǝla na fa thlǝrɓuya ǝnaarha hu Ƙǝn Faara, tǝ ten kwamangya, ahur wure ka a fal kanda nda wa. Niya pǝrang ƙǝkafek kun, ˈWanda teena thlǝnda yi ndan ƙǝna.
\v 3 Amma a naɗun a fǝrang niifa ˈya na midghǝn, a nggǝmɗun fa sǝngga yi kawa ˈya na yisǝma a fǝra wa.
\v 4 No a fǝra ɓǝɓee, tǝrgha tsu na a na ˈya na a ǝnaarha ɓǝɓee nǝn a fǝro ƙǝnaghǝn.
\s1 Tsaharha ha aten hwan Faara
\r (Luka11:2-4)
\p 
\v 5 “Anaɗun a hwan Faara, a ǝna ɗun ƙǝla fa thlǝrɓuya wa. Ƙǝsǝr kanda na mindan sǝ hwan Faara ƙǝt ƙǝkǝɗa a ƙǝngya yi hwan Faara, tǝ ƙǝm aten kwamangya ahur tala ka a nagha fiya kanda. Niya pǝrang ƙǝkafek kun ˈwanda teena wal nda ƙǝna ndan.
\v 6 Amma anaɗun a hwan Faara, kyama hur ƙǝnna ɗǝ, nggǝlang nggun kwatminda a hwanang nggun chinun, mbuwawa nǝm a naarha. Tǝrgha Chinun, na a na ˈya ɓǝɓee, nǝn a fǝrang ƙǝnaghǝn kun.”
\p 
\v 7 “Anaɗun a hwan Faara, a nggurɓang ɗun ˈya nun a thlǝkrha ƙǝla nafiya sǝngwa Faara na a ǝnaarha wa. Tamngganda ndaarha na nda sǝk fandan a nanda a nggurɓang pathla mu.
\v 8 A tsauɗun ƙǝla kanda wa, ƙǝsǝr Chinun sǝnɗǝ ˈya na minnun kapa nun tsahang mee.
\v 9 Hwanama kiya.”
\b
\q1 “Chinǝm na a talara
\q2 a chilɓi thlǝm wa nǝm ha.
\q1 
\v 10 Kutǝryid wa ɓagha ɓa.
\q2 ˈYa na midwa a ǝnaghǝnan,
\q2 hu ƙǝshiirha ƙǝla yanɗi na nanda a ǝnaarha a talara
\q1 
\v 11 Fǝrang ǝnnadmid par fara kan.
\q1 
\v 12 Chahang ɗimiyid nan kanɗǝ,
\q2 ƙǝla nan chahanggǝn fingyaɗǝ na a ǝnang ɗimiyirha kan fa.
\q1 
\v 13 A ɗǝnna tǝ kan hu ƙǝƙǝrra ɗǝ wa,
\q2 amma hǝrghang kan a haar tǝmbǝlfedɗi.”
\b
\p 
\v 14 Ƙǝsǝr a chahang ɗun ɗimiyindan fiyaɗǝ ǝnangga ɗimiyirha kun fa, Chinun na a talara ƙǝm nǝn a chahang ɗimiyid nun kun ɗǝ.
\v 15 Amma a chahang nggun ɗimiyid ndan fiya ɗǝ wa, Chinun na a talara ƙǝm mbǝ chahang ɗimiyid nun kun ɗǝ wa.
\s1 Tsaharha ha aten kar aama
\p 
\v 16 “Anaɗun a kar aama, a ndeng ɗun yid nun hai ƙǝla na fa thlǝrɓuya ǝnaarha wa, ƙǝsǝr na nda ndeng yindan hai tǝna fiya sǝndasǝ na nda a kar aama. Niya pǝrang ƙǝkafek kun, ˈwanda teena thlǝnda ƙǝna ndan.
\v 17 Amma ana ɗun a kar aama, tsǝtsǝɗang was wa ƙǝm fǝɗeerha na aten wa,
\v 18 amana fiya sǝnda sǝ nun a kar aama. Chinun mbuwawa nǝm a naarha, na a na ˈya nǝm a ǝnaarha ɓǝɓee, nǝn a fǝrang ƙǝnaghǝn kun.”
\s1 Tsaharha ha aten wumnda ƙǝna a talara
\r (Luka12:33-34)
\p 
\v 19 “A ɗǝfang ɗun ƙǝna alten nun ɗǝ hu ƙǝshidɗiya, na mǝmemngya tǝ hǝla sǝɓang nda ɗǝ, tǝ ƙǝm na ngaarya kyarha ɗǝ tǝrang ngganda wa.
\v 20 Amma ɗǝfa man ƙǝna altennun ɗǝ a talara, mbuwana mǝmemngya tǝ hǝla sǝɓang ɗǝ, tǝ ƙǝm mbuwana ngaarya kyarha ɗǝ ngaara nda.
\v 21 Ƙǝsǝr kala mbǝrha nana ƙǝnawa sǝ ndǝna mbǝd numad wa.”
\s1 Kukwaryid farha
\r (Luka11:34-36)
\p 
\v 22 Yirha ndǝna kukwaryid farha, ana yidwa kanglang hai, fadwa na heu nǝn narha lǝlǝgɗa tǝ kukwaryirha.
\v 23 Amma a mbǝ yidwa kanglang hai wa, fadwa na heu nǝn narha tǝ wula. Ana kukwaryirha na a fadwa wulani, fadwa na heu nǝn narha tikɗik.
\s1 Manang nda Faara wa nduwa ƙǝna wa
\r (Luka16:13)
\p 
\v 24 “Mbǝ mafarha sǝ na ǝnang taara turaya sǝri wa. Tsauɗǝ nǝn nggǝm tal kar tahadghǝnǝn, nduwa ƙǝm mananggǝn tal sar tahadghǝnǝn. Mbǝ ǝnaarha hai ǝnang taara nun Faara tǝ wuɗǝɓǝla kyab wa.”
\s1 A ɓillaɗun wa
\r (Luka12:22-31)
\p 
\v 25 Tsaunǝn kee, niya ndang nda kun, a ɓillaɗun tǝ yiɓǝd nun wa, tǝ ˈya nun ǝnnarhami tǝ sarha wa, nduwa fannun ˈya nun kala fa wa. Kalwa yiɓǝd nun ǝnnarhami wa, nduwa kalwa fannun ˈya nun a kala fa wa?
\v 26 Kǝla man wuɗikkya lee! Mba nda hǝfrha wa, mba nda haathla wa, mba nda tǝ ƙǝn ǝnnarhami nduwa ɓiriukya wa, ko nanǝn kee na Faara fǝrang ǝnnarhami kanda. Sǝngunsǝ mamnggit nun kalɗǝ yi wuɗikkya wa?
\v 27 Wunni ahur nun aten ɓilladghǝn na mbang chik ɓenggǝn hu ƙǝshiirha?
\p 
\v 28 Kama nun ɓillarha aten lukkya? Kǝla man fid ɗǝfya na tsǝrha. Mba nda ǝna taara, ko pu kaɓarha wa.
\v 29 Ko nanǝn kee, niya ndang nda kun, ko kutǝra Sulemanu tǝ mamnggitghǝn ˈwa wa ngwarha fa ƙǝla tal ahur ndan wa.
\v 30 Ana Faara a ngwang nda fid ɗǝfya fa na a hee kiya, hwaliirha nasǝ a weeriya, a ɓinda ƙǝm njigha ɗǝ, sakkwa kun nǝn ngwang kun fa. Kama nanun tǝ yamid fǝrƙǝkafek?
\p 
\v 31 “Nanǝn kee a ɓillaɗun aten ǝngginiya tǝ ndaarha, ‘Ma nan ǝnnarhami? Nduwa, ma nan saarha? Nduwa, ma nan kala fa?’”
\v 32 Ƙǝsǝr nafiya sǝngwa Faara ndǝna kaɗa tur ǝngginiya, Chinun na a talara sǝnɗasǝ na minnun sǝ ǝngginiya.
\v 33 Kaɗama kutǝryid Faara ˈwan tǝ ǝna nggayirha, ǝnggini na heu ƙǝmya nǝn a fǝranggǝn kun.
\v 34 Tsaunǝn kee, a ɓillaɗun tǝ ɓinda wa, ƙǝsǝr ɓinda nǝn a ɓarha ɓa tǝ ɓilladghǝn. Kala parra yanfaara nǝghǝn tǝ ɓillad altenggǝn.
\c 7
\s1 Tsahad Yeeso ha aten ngwang kumarha fingya
\r (Luka6:37-38,41-42)
\p 
\v 1 “A ngwangɗun kumarha fingya wa, kun nggima mba nda ngwang kumarha kun wa.
\v 2 Ƙǝsǝr na nda a ǝnang nda kun ƙǝla ǝnang nun fingya. Tasau nun a ƙǝƙǝrang fiya sǝ ndǝna nda ƙǝƙǝrang nda kun sǝ.
\v 3 Mani na ƙǝlang hwaliirha na a yid shadwa, sa kula ƙǝɗang miwaarha ɗǝ na a yidwa?
\v 4 Ƙǝƙǝn na ndang nda shadwa, ‘Wanya ni a ƙǝɗo hwaliirha ɗǝ a yidwa’ kula sa na miwaarha na yidwa?
\v 5 Sa tǝthlǝrɓu! Katǝrang ƙǝɗang miwadɗǝ ˈwan na yidwa tǝna na mana hai ngga, na a mbangga ƙǝɗang hwaliirha ɗǝ na yid shadwa.”
\p 
\v 6 A fǝrang ɗun ˈya wuɗaya na chahal wa. A tsamang ɗun ǝn thlǝmaaya ɗǝ tǝ ǝn uraya natǝ wuɗǝɓǝla fa a ƙǝlengarya ɗǝ wa. A ǝna ɗun kee, na nda ishang hai a kamu saryi ndan. Na wuɗa yini a kyaharra hai njarang ngganda kun ɗǝ kushir-kushir.
\s1 Tsaharha ha aten hwan Faara
\r (Luka11:9-13)
\p 
\v 7 Naama a hwanda na nda fǝrang kun. Naama a kaɗaarha nun a waala. Naama a ɗǝk kwatminda, na nda inanggǝn kun hai.
\v 8 Ƙǝsǝr kala niifa hwangga, na nda a fǝrang, niifa kaɗagha ƙǝm nǝn a waala. Kǝmɗarha kala niifa ɗǝkka kwatminda nanda inanggǝn hai.
\p 
\v 9 Wunni ahur nun, a hwanang wanggǝn mburodi fǝrang feera nǝn?
\v 10 Nduwa a hwanang ɗǝ tǝna fǝrang hulthne nǝn?
\v 11 A tsauɗǝ, kun na fa mbǝlfeeya sǝnɗun ˈya nun fǝrang nda wangginun ǝngya na ngga, sakwata chinun a talara, nǝn fǝr ǝngya na ngga a nafiya na hwanda.
\p 
\v 12 Tsaunǝn kee, ǝnaman ˈya fiya ƙǝla na mid nun a ǝnang ngganda kun. Ƙǝsǝr tsahad ngyakhrha Ɗeleewar Musa niya tǝ yi annabiya.
\s1 Tsaharha ha aten kwatkirma na iˈyaɓa
\r (Luka13:24)
\p 
\v 13 Kyarha hu kutǝryid Faara ɗǝ tǝtani kyana tǝ kwatkirma na iˈyaɓa. Kwaman ɗǝrha hu waarha ɗǝ nǝghǝn manggǝn, kwatkirǝm nggǝn ƙǝm nǝghǝn ƙǝthlǝng, nafiya hangga wurgha kwaman ɗi.
\v 14 Kwatkirǝm wal yibrha nǝghǝn ngguchit, tǝ ƙǝm kwamanggǝn nǝghǝn pǝɗaghǝn, nafiya na a kyarha sǝ na nda ngguchit.
\s1 Tsahad Yeeso ha aten annabiya fa nggaɓaya
\r (Luka6:43-44)
\p 
\v 15 Kwarama tǝ annabiya fa nggaɓaya. Na nda ɓarha thlǝmad nun ɓa tǝ lukrha fa ƙǝla chauraya, amma hur ndan nǝghǝn ƙǝla mǝmereeya.
\v 16 Nǝm sǝnang kanda hai ahu ǝn ǝnad ndan ƙǝla nǝm sǝn ɗǝfrha tǝ tur wanggighǝn. Mbǝm ɗakh wan inabi ɓa a fad ndaha wa, nduwa wan shiɓarha a fad ndakh mbǝlfeerha wa.
\p 
\v 17 Ɗǝfrha na ngga nǝn nggǝt wan ɗǝfrha na ngga, ɗǝfrha mbuwawa ngga nǝn nggǝt wan ɗǝfrha mbuwawa ngga.
\v 18 Ɗǝfrha na ngga mbǝ nggǝt wan ɗǝfrha mbuwawa ngga wa, tǝ ƙǝm ɗǝfrha mbuwawa ngga mbǝ nggǝt wan ɗǝfrha na ngga wa.
\v 19 Kala ɗǝfrha mbuwa nggǝt wan ɗǝfya ngga na nda kyathlang ɗǝ muwang ngganda ahu waarha ɗǝ.
\v 20 Nǝghǝn kee, ƙǝla nǝm sǝnang ɗǝfrha hai tǝ tur wanggighǝn, nǝm sǝnang annabiya fa nggaɓaya hai kee ƙǝm tǝ ǝn ǝnad ndan.
\s1 Tsahad Yeeso ha aten kyaarha hu Kutǝryid Talara ɗǝ
\r (Luka13:25-27)
\p 
\v 21 “Mbǝ fiya heu na a aah nggi, ‘Chinǝm, Chinǝm,’ na a kyarha hu Kutǝryid Talara ɗǝ wa, amma ƙǝl nafini ǝnagha ˈya na mid Pǝpa na a talara.”
\v 22 “Nafiya hangga na a ndeerha a farɗi, ‘Chinǝm, Chinǝm,’ pǝr ɗan laɓar Faara tǝ thlǝmwa, tǝ ƙǝm kyang ɗan ǝnkaheeya sǝ tǝ thlǝmwa, tǝ ƙǝm ǝna ɗan ǝnwulteengya hangga tǝ thlǝmwa.”
\v 23 “Amma niya nggǝrang kanda sǝ, ‘ˈwawi sǝn kun wa. Weema ma thlǝmadna kun fa mbǝlfeeya!’”
\s1 Karapu aten fa tǝngya sǝri
\r (Luka6:47-49)
\p 
\v 24 Kala niifa kang ngga thlǝmaarha tsahad na fa ǝna taara nǝn sǝ nǝghǝn ndǝndǝl, kǝla niifa tǝngga wurighǝn aten feera.
\v 25 Ɓana ˈyaara hai, lǝghǝdgha kufaarha, ɗǝkka ɓereu ˈyaara wuriɗi amma mbangwa chang hai wa, ƙǝsǝr tǝngga ndan aten feera.
\p 
\v 26 “Amma niifa sǝkka tsahad na ǝnawa taara sǝ wa, nǝghǝn ƙǝla nur niifa tǝngga wurighǝn aten chehweerha.
\v 27 Ɓana ˈyaara hai, lǝghǝdgha kufaarha, ɗǝkka ɓereu ˈyaara wuriɗi chang nggǝn hai hwaf.”
\p 
\v 28 Ngwalang na Yeeso tsahadghǝn ha, fiya wumngga hai ǝna ǝnwulteena nda aten tsahadghǝn ha.
\v 29 Ƙǝsǝr tsahadghǝn ha nǝghǝn ƙǝla niifa na tǝ sǝsǝmnda, mbǝ ƙǝla fatsahaya yi ngyakhrha wa.
\c 8
\s1 Tsaɓang Yeeso niifa ɗǝ na tǝ wanhad termeerha
\r (Markus1:40-45; Luka5:12-16)
\p 
\v 1 Tǝrna Yeeso hai a wumnda, takkwagha fiya ndǝn hangga.
\v 2 Na niifa sǝ na tǝ wanhad termeerha fa, nanǝn Yeeso ɗǝgha thlǝmadghǝn ɗǝ, ɓǝrgha hai a mbedghǝn hwanggǝn nǝn ndanggǝn, “Chinǝm, a nggǝmna fa na mbang tsaɓeeɗǝ.”
\v 3 Tǝrgha Yeeso fǝr harghǝnǝn ɗǝ tsuwarghǝnǝn fa ndanggǝn, “Nggǝmɗi fa a tsaɓana ɗǝ. Tsaɓuɗǝ!” A mbǝɗi tsu kee, termedɗi ndǝkka hai tǝghǝn.
\v 4 Tǝrgha ƙǝsgha Yeeso thlǝmadghǝn ndanggǝn, “A pǝrang nan niifa wa, amma ɗuwaɗǝ kyaɗang fadwa firis na sa nǝn. A ǝno sataka tǝna fiya sǝndasǝ tsabnaɗǝ kǝla ndana ngyakhrha Musa.”
\s1 Yeeso ƙǝnang ɗǝ mafad mamnda sodja Romaya
\r (Luka7:1-10)
\p 
\v 5 Kyana Yeeso Kafarnahum hai, ɓagha mamnda sodja Romaya thlǝmadghǝn ɓa hwanggǝn nǝn ndanggǝn,
\v 6 “Chinǝm, mafadna kalth a wuri mbǝ kanglang wa, mǝr fadghǝn hai nǝghǝn a sǝsarha kaan.”
\v 7 Ndangga Yeeso, “Niya ɗǝrhaɗǝ ɗi ƙǝnang nda.”
\p 
\v 8 Tǝrgha mamnda sodja Romaya nggǝmanggǝn Yeeso ndanggǝn, “Chinǝm, tsǝkki na a ɓana minda kyana ɓa wa, amma a nggǝmna fa kalu sǝ kee a mbǝɗi na nana na mafanna a ƙǝnda.
\v 9 Ƙǝsǝr nggi niyi akamu ngyakhrha niifa, ƙǝmɗa tǝ sodjaya a kamuna. Ni ndangnda yanɗiya, ‘ɗuwaɗǝ’, nǝn ɗǝrhaɗǝ; yanɗi taarha ƙǝm ndanggi ˈɓoɓaˈ, nǝn a ɓarha ɓa, ndanggi mafanna, ǝno kiya, ǝnagha ƙǝla ndangni.”
\p 
\v 10 Sǝkna Yeeso ndǝn kee, wulangga teena. Kyahargha hai ndanggǝn nafini na a mbu samadghǝn, “Niya ndang nda kun, ahur Isǝreela ˈwawi wal niifa tǝ fǝrƙǝkafek fa tǝ kanglanggirha ƙǝla yanɗiya wa.”
\v 11 “Niya ndang nda kun, fiya hangga na a ɓarha ɓa a man kyad yanfaara tǝ man hǝmndǝghǝn, na nda a tǝr mbǝd tsawud ndan tǝ Ibrahim, tǝ Ishaku tǝ Yakubu ahu wutsǝfayidɗi hu Kutǝryid Talara.
\v 12 Amma Isǝreelaya hangga kya nanda ǝna Kutǝryidɗi ka kanda, nanda a muwang kanda ahu wula ɗǝ, a mbǝɗani na nanda a tǝrha sǝ tǝ ƙǝt mee.”
\v 13 Tǝrgha ndangga Yeeso mamnda sodja Romadɗi, “Wuɗu wureeɗǝ, ka fǝrƙǝkafekkid wa ni ǝnagha ndǝn katǝra nǝn hai kee.” Mafadɗi keeghǝn ƙǝngga mǝmǝlla sayidɗi wu.
\s1 Ƙǝnang Yeeso fiya hangga
\r (Markus1:29-34; Luka4:38-41)
\p 
\v 14 Sǝlna Yeeso a minda ki Mbiturus ɗǝ, ɗǝgha wal thlaɓǝr Mbiturus tǝnuwunda fadghǝn ɓee kalth hu sǝra.
\v 15 Tsuwargha Yeeso harghǝn fa, ƙǝngga. Tǝrgha thliigha sǝ fǝrang ǝnnarhami nǝn.
\v 16 Tsǝna figrha hai, nafiya natǝ ǝnkaheeya fa hangga ɓa nda tǝ kanda thlǝmad Yeeso ɓa. Kyanggǝn ǝnkaheeyina sǝ tǝ mee kee, tǝ ƙǝm ƙǝnanggǝn haaya heu.
\v 17 Ənanǝn ǝnɗiya ka a lǝghǝdgha laɓarɗi thlǝkna Chinǝm tǝ mii annabi Ishaya, ndanǝn:
\b
\q1 “Tǝrang ɗǝ ɓeerha fayi nǝm,
\q2 tǝ ƙǝm ƙǝɗanggǝn wanhayi nǝm ɗǝ.” \f + \fr 8:17 \ft Ishaya 53:4 \f*
\s1 Pǝɗayid mbu samad Yeeso
\r (Luka9:57-62)
\p 
\v 18 Ƙǝlang na Yeeso fiya wumngga thlǝmadghǝn ɓa, ndanggǝn fatsahayighǝn a ɗǝnda pǝm wuri aama Nggalili ɗǝ.
\v 19 Tǝrgha tal ahur famalǝmngya ngyakhrha Musa ndanggǝn, “Mala, niya mbusamad wa kala mbǝrha na a ɗǝrha saaɗǝ.”
\p 
\v 20 Nggǝrangga Yeeso sǝ, “Tsarwaya tǝ kwandan sǝ, wuɗikkya na hu ɓereurha tǝ ƙǝndan sǝ, amma Wan Niifa mbǝ mbǝdghǝn sǝ ko na a ɗǝfanggǝn tenggǝn sahai wa.”
\p 
\v 21 Tal ahur fatsahayighǝn ndanggǝn, “Chinǝm, malee ˈwan wuɗi wureeɗǝ ɗi pangnda pǝpa.”
\p 
\v 22 Amma ndangga Yeeso, “Mbuwu samanna nanǝnya! Malang mǝrya pang ngganda mǝrrǝndan.”
\s1 Yanang Yeeso ɓereu ˈyaara
\r (Markus4:35-41; Luka8:22-25)
\p 
\v 23 Tǝrgha Yeeso kyagha hu kombuwol hai katǝranggǝn tǝɗang wuri aamɗi teena tǝ fatsahayighǝn.
\v 24 Kula sǝndǝndan sǝ, ɓagha ɓereu ˈyaara ɓa na kanglang ahu wuri aam ɗaɓa katǝrangga aamɗi kuɗufulla hai nagha aama a pisha ahur kombuwol ɗa hai. Amma tǝrang ɓeena Yeeso ɗǝ.
\v 25 Ɗǝgha fatsahayighǝn ɗǝ mekhneng ngganda sǝ ndang ngganda, “Chinǝm, hǝrghang ƙǝm! Nǝm a hwaarha ɗǝ!”
\p 
\v 26 Amma nggǝrangga Yeeso kanda sǝ, “Kama nun a tǝrǝmnda? Ƙǝɗi fǝrƙǝkafekkid nun!” Tǝrgha thliigha sǝ yanaggǝn ɓereuɗi tǝ kuɗufulla aamɗi, nggasgha mbǝrha hai.
\p 
\v 27 Ƙǝsangga ǝnwulteena fatsahayighǝn tsakhmee nda, “Tur niif wunni ya? Ko ɓereurha ni tǝ kuɗufulla aama na nda a takkwa ˈya ndanǝn!”
\s1 Ƙǝnang Yeeso nafiya sǝri na tǝ ǝnkaheeya fa
\r (Markus5:1-20; Luka8:26-39)
\p 
\v 28 Sǝlna Yeeso a pǝm wuri aam ɗaɗǝ, na a man ki chehweed Nggadaraya, nafiya sǝri na tǝ ǝnkaheeya fa ɓa nda thlǝmadghǝn ɓa. Ɓagha nda ɓa a mbǝd ten kwaya, mbǝ niifa sǝ na mbang mbǝraɗǝ tǝ mbǝɗi wa, ƙǝsǝr tsau nda ǝn tǝrǝmnda.
\v 29 Katǝrang ngganda huhwang nda hai na nda a ndaarha, “Ma djiɗoyiwa tǝ kan, Wan Faara? Ɓana ɓa ka a sǝsangga kan kapa na far ngwa kumad nan tsǝrha hai wa?”
\p 
\v 30 Tsau tǝ mbǝɗi na ƙǝlengarya sǝ na a lafrha.
\v 31 Hwangga ǝnkaheeyini Yeeso, “A kyang na kan sǝ, ɗang kan ahur chiɓǝd ƙǝlengaryina ɗǝ taarha.”
\p 
\v 32 Ndanggǝn kanda, “Ɗaama ɗǝ!” Nanǝn kee kya nda sǝ ɗǝnda ahur ƙǝlengaryina ɗǝ. Chiɓǝd ƙǝlengaryini kahat ɗaa nda ahur wuri aam ɗaɗǝ hwaa nda ɗǝ.
\p 
\v 33 Nafini na a laf ƙǝlengaryini ɗaa nda hur tala ɗǝ pǝr ǝnɗa nda katǝragha hai heu, tǝ ƙǝm ǝnɗi katǝragha hai tǝ nafini sǝri na tǝ ǝnkaheeya fa.
\v 34 Tǝrgha nafiya hur talɗi heu kya nda ɓa ka ɓa nda na Yeeso. Na nanda Yeeso hwanggǝnda a mal chehweed ndan nǝn.
\c 9
\s1 Ƙǝnang Yeeso niifa mǝrna fadghǝn hai
\r (Markus2:1-12; Luka5:17-26)
\p 
\v 1 Kyagha Yeeso ahu kombuwol hai ɗǝgha hu talghǝn ɗǝ mannǝn sǝ Kafarnahum.
\v 2 Ɓagha fingya nafiya ɓa tǝ niifa mǝrna fadghǝn hai kalth ahu ɗǝnggǝla. Nana Yeeso fǝrƙǝkafekkid ndan, ndanggǝn niifɗi mǝrna fadghǝn hai, “A ɓilladna wa waana, chohonda ɗimiyidwa ɗǝ.”
\v 3 Fingya famalǝmgya ngyakrha na nda a ndaarha ahur ndan tǝ ndaarha, “Kamshiɗiya nǝghǝn a sar Faara.”
\p 
\v 4 Sǝnangga Yeeso numad ndan hai ndanggǝn kanda, “Kama nun numad ǝn mbǝlfeerha kiya ahur nun?
\v 5 Yanggini pǝpa, a ndang nggi tǝ mǝrra fadɗi, ‘Chohonda ɗimiyidwa ɗǝ wa,’ nduwa, ‘Thliusǝ wiu wa?’
\v 6 Amma niya kyaɗang ndaarha kun, Wan Niifa nǝghǝn tǝ sǝsǝmnda ha hu ƙǝshidɗiya yi chakh ɗimiya.” Tǝrgha ndanggǝn niifɗi mǝrna fadghǝn hai, “Thliusǝ, tǝrang ɗǝnggǝlwa sǝ, wiina wureeɗǝ.”
\p 
\v 7 Thliigha niifɗa sǝ harad ɗǝgha wureeɗǝ.
\v 8 Nagha fiya wumngga hai ǝnɗi katǝragha hai ƙǝsangga ǝnwulteena kanda. Tǝrgha manang ngganda Faara tǝ thlǝnangga niifa ɓa natǝ sǝsǝmnda fa kaan kiya.
\s1 Aah Yeeso Matta a mbu samadghǝn nǝn
\r (Markus2:13-17; Luka5:27-32)
\p 
\v 9 Nana Yeeso ɗiye mbeeɗǝ tǝ wiirha na niifa nǝn na nda aarha Matta, ndǝghǝn tsau a mbǝd thlǝ tsamnda. Tǝrgha ndangga Yeeso, “Mbuwu samanna.” Thliigha sǝ mbu samadghǝn nǝn.
\p 
\v 10 Tsǝɓaku, na Yeeso a hǝb ǝnnarhami a wuri ki Matta, ɓagha fa thlǝ tsamngya tǝ faɗimiya hangga, hǝb ǝnnarhami nda tǝghǝn tǝ fatsahayighǝn.
\p 
\v 11 Nana Farisayini ndǝn kee, tsahang mee nda fatsahayighǝn ha, “Kama na tǝmalǝm ndǝnun hǝbrha tǝ fathlǝ tsamngya tǝ faɗimiya?”
\p 
\v 12 Sǝkna Yeeso ndǝn kee, nggǝranggǝn kanda sǝ, “Nafiya na ƙǝkanglang hai mba nda kaɗa tǝpurha wa, kǝl nafiya mbuwa ƙǝkanglang.
\v 13 Nanǝnya, ɗamaɗǝ ɗun tsaha ǝnɗi na laɓar Faara a ndaarha, ‘haɗang nda niifa fa ndǝna minna a fannun, mbǝ sataka wa.’ Ƙǝsǝr ɓayi ɓa ka a aah nafiya ni na a numad ndaarha na nda a ǝna nggayirha wa, amma kǝl fa ɗimiya.”
\s1 Tsakhmee aten kar aama
\r (Markus2:18-22; Luka5:33-38)
\p 
\v 14 Tǝrgha ɓagha fatsahaya Yahaya a thlǝmad Yeeso ɓa ndang ngganda, “Ma ǝnagha ndǝn kan tǝ Farisaya a kar aama, amma fatsaha yiwa mba nda kar aama wa?”
\p 
\v 15 Nggǝrangga Yeeso kanda sǝ, “Ƙǝƙǝn na hur pashiya wutsamnda sǝbrha ɗǝ ndǝghǝn wutsamnda ɓalɗǝ a thlǝmad ndan? Na fara ɓayi nanda a tǝrang wutsamnda ma kanda. A farɗa ni na nanda a kar aama.
\p 
\v 16 “Mbǝ niifa sǝ na mbuhwang suhurra lukrha tǝ weerǝnda ɓar kaɓaarha wa, ƙǝsǝr na mbuhudɗi a njarang nda luwudɗa ɗǝ, njarrǝghǝn nǝn a kal yi kaar.
\v 17 Tǝ kǝm mbǝ niifa sǝ na irang nda weerǝnda aam inabi ahu suhurra samsamiya hai wa. A irang nda sa hai, na samsamiyini a ɗathla ɗǝ, na aam inabiɗi a iraaɗǝ, samsamiyini na nda sǝbrha ɗǝ. Weerinda aam anab, kamɗǝ a irang nggǝm ahu weerǝnda samsamiya hai. A ǝnaɗǝm kee na aam inabiɗi tǝ samsamiyini a ɓaala hai.”
\s1 Kǝnang Yeeso wutarad Yayirus tǝ nuneefa
\r (Markus5:21-43; Luka8:40-56)
\p 
\v 18 Yeeso ɓalɗǝ a kalang kanda sǝ, ɓagha mamnda ƙǝn tsahad Yahudaya ɓa ɓǝrgha hai a mbedghǝn ndagha, “Mǝrgha wutarad na kukuling ya, ɓoɓa ɓa tsǝwarghǝn fa, nǝn a thliirha sǝ tǝ yibrha.”
\p 
\v 19 Thliigha Yeeso sǝ tǝ fatsahayighǝn mbu samadghǝn nda.
\p 
\v 20 Tǝrgha na nuneefa sǝ ǝnagha hurarha kumkap sǝri fara a ɓang fa hai. Ɓagha ɓa tǝman ƙǝsǝrghǝn tsuwar mii luwudghǝnǝn fa,
\v 21 ƙǝsǝr numaghǝn tǝ ndaarha, “Ko luwudghǝn tsuwar ni fa kee, niya ƙǝnda.”
\p 
\v 22 Kyaharna Yeeso hai na nǝn ndǝn, ndagha, “A ɓillanna wa, waana, fǝrƙǝkafekkid wa ƙǝnoɗǝ.” Tsu a mbǝɗi kee ƙǝngga.
\p 
\v 23 Kyana Yeeso minda ki mamndǝɗa hai, na fa pi perǝmngya nǝn tǝ fiya wumngga hai kanda a mbeela.
\v 24 Tǝrgha ndagha, “Kyama ƙǝshaaɗǝ, mǝr wa wutaradɗi wa, nǝn a shiirha ni kee.”Amma masangga fiya wumngga hai.
\v 25 Akwasamadɗi rǝk nanda fiya ƙǝshaaɗǝ, kyagha ɗǝ ƙǝs har wutaradɗa nǝn, thliigha sǝ.
\v 26 Laɓar ǝnwulteenɗiya welɗaɗǝ ahu chehwedɗi kahat.
\s1 Ƙǝnang Yeeso kwamaya tǝ niifa mbuwa mbang kaala sǝ
\p 
\v 27 Akwasamadɗi malna Yeeso mbǝɗi, kwamaya sǝri hǝshya mbu samadghǝn nda kanda a aaghǝn, “A haɗowan fa, Wan Ndauda!”
\p 
\v 28 Kyana Yeeso hur minda hai, tǝrgha kwamayini ɗǝnda thlǝmadghǝn ɗǝ, tsahang mee nǝn kanda, “Fǝrɗun ƙǝkafek ni mbang ƙǝnang kun wa?” Nggǝrang ngganda sǝ “Ha i, Chinǝm.”
\p 
\v 29 Tǝrgha tsuwar yiyi ndan nǝn fa ndagha, “Ƙǝsǝr ka fǝrƙǝkafekkid nun, nun a ƙǝnda.”
\v 30 Tǝrgha yiyi ndan inggaɗǝ. Ƙǝsgha Yeeso thlǝmad ndan kaan ndagha, “A pǝrang ɗun ndǝn niifa wa.”
\p 
\v 31 Amma kya nda sǝ pǝr laɓar ɗaa nda ahu chehwedɗi kahat.
\p 
\v 32 Kyana nda sǝ, na niifa sǝ natǝ ǝnkaheerha fa mbǝ mbang kalasǝ wa, ɓa nda tǝghǝn thlǝmad Yeeso ɓa.
\v 33 Kyang na Yeeso ǝnkaheedɗa sǝ, niifɗi mbuwa mbang kalasǝ kalgha sǝ. Fiya wumngga hai ƙǝsgha ǝnwulteena kanda ndaa nda, “ˈWaghǝm tam na ˈya manggǝn ƙǝla yanɗiya a Isǝreela wa.”
\p 
\v 34 Amma ndagha Farisaya, “Mamnda ǝnkaheeya fǝrangga sǝsǝmnda kyang nda ǝnkaheeya sǝ.”
\s1 Ƙǝɗi fatarya
\p 
\v 35 Yeeso wengɗǝ wupǝriya hai tǝ talya heu a tsahang fiya ha ahu ƙǝn tsahad Yahudaya, tǝ pǝr Laɓara na Mbǝnggǝn yi Kutǝryid Faara, tǝ ƙǝm a ƙǝnang nda fiya natǝ wanhaya ɗǝɗamǝn-ɗǝɗamǝn.
\v 36 Nana Yeeso fiya wumngga hai, haɗangga nafina fa, ƙǝsǝr na nda hu sǝsaarha, mbǝ niifa sǝ na ɗang kanda sǝ wa. Na nda kǝla chauraya na kula tǝlafrha.
\v 37 Tǝrgha ndanggǝn fatsahayighǝn, “Mul hathla hai, amma ƙǝɗi fatarya.
\v 38 Tsaunǝn kee, hwanama tǝhedɗi, thlǝn fatarya nǝn ɓa ɓanda hathlang sǝ.”
\c 10
\s1 Wur Yeeso fathlǝngya kumkap sǝri
\r (Markus3:13-19; Luka6:12-16)
\p 
\v 1 Aagha Yeeso fatsahayighǝn kumkap sǝri a thlǝmadghǝn ɓa, fǝrang sǝsǝmnda nǝn kanda a kyang ngganda ǝnkaheeya sǝ tǝ ƙǝm ƙǝnang ngganda wanhaya ɗǝɗamǝn-ɗǝɗamǝn tǝ ɓeerha farha.
\v 2 Kulo thlǝm fathlǝngya Yeeso kumkap sǝri ya:
\b
\li1 Siman nanda aarha Mbiturus,
\li1 Andrawus wanman Siman,
\li1 Yakubu wan Dzabadi,
\li1 Yahaya wanman Yakubu,
\li1 
\v 3 Filibus,
\li1 Mbatalomi,
\li1 Toma,
\li1 Matta tǝ thlǝ tsamnda,
\li1 Yakubu wan Alfiyus,
\li1 Taddiyus,
\v 4 Siman tǝsǝrǝk chehweedghǝn,
\li1 Yahuda Iskaryoti fǝrgha Yeeso ɗǝ.
\s1 Thlǝn Yeeso kumkap sǝri ɗi
\r (Markus6:7-13; Luka9:1-6)
\p 
\v 5 Thlǝngga Yeeso kumkap sǝri ɗi ndanggǝn kanda, “A ɗuɗun thlǝmad fingya ɗǝ mbuwa Yahudaya, nduwa talya Samariyaya wa.
\v 6 Amma ɗaama thlǝmad nafiya Isǝreela ɗǝ, chauraya Faara sahadgha.
\v 7 Ɗaamaɗǝ ɗun ndangnda kanda nduwus Kutǝryid Faara ɓa.
\v 8 Ƙǝnaman haya, thleeman mǝrya sǝ, ƙǝnaman fingya natǝ wanhad termeerha fa, kyaman ǝnkaheeya sǝ. Fǝrang nggandan kun ka, kun ƙǝm fǝramadghǝn ka ƙǝla thlǝnun ndǝn!
\v 9 A ƙǝsɗun wuɗǝɓǝla ha hu panjakwan nun wa, ko tǝfaasa, nduwa wurirha, nduwa kala ˈya na ƙǝla wuɗǝɓǝla wa.
\v 10 A ƙǝsɗun yawarha ha tǝ lukrha tǝ pakhma, nduwa sǝsaala wa. Kala ˈya fǝrang nanda kun a karɗun ndǝn wa, ƙǝsǝr tǝtaara kamɗǝ a wal ǝnnarhami nǝn.”
\p 
\v 11 Kala wupǝri nduwa tala kyanun sahai, kaɗaama ka niifa tsawun ahur mindǝghǝn ta far ɗaɗǝ nun a mal talɗi.
\v 12 A kyaɗun hur minda hai, ndaamaˈya tǝ ƙǝm fǝrang parka nun kanda.
\v 13 Ana ka minda ni ngwa tsauka parkad nun sǝ. Amma a mbusǝ kee wa, ngwa wudgha parkad nun a fad nun ɓa.
\v 14 Kala tala nduwa wure kyanun sahai, a thluwa nda kun fa wa, nduwa kar nda kang thlǝmaarha kun fa, anaɗun a wiirha paman tinid mbǝɗa ɗǝ na a fad sarnun.
\v 15 Niya pǝrang ƙǝkafek kun, a far ngwa kumarha a nggushi nda Sodom tǝ Nggomara na nda a haɗang kanda fa ma talɗi.
\s1 Sǝsaarha na ɓayi
\r (Markus13:9-13; Luka12:11-12; 21:12-19)
\p 
\v 16 Niya thlǝn kun ƙǝla chauraya ahur mǝmereeya ɗǝ. Nanǝn kee tsawama thladwayirha ƙǝla huthlingya tǝ ƙǝm tsawama mǝsǝlǝmnda nafiya ƙǝla kataprakkya.
\v 17 Kwarama! Ƙǝsǝr na nda a ɗǝrha tǝ kun mbed fa ngwa kumaya ɗǝ tǝ ƙǝngya tsahad Yahudaya tsaɗa kun nda.
\v 18 Nanda a ɗǝrha tǝ kun a mbed ngwamnaya ɗǝ tǝ kutǝrya ƙǝsǝr ka nggi. Ənɗaniya na fǝrang kwamana kun pǝrang ƙǝkafek nun kanda atenna.
\v 19 Amma a ƙǝsang nda kun a ɓillaɗun tǝ ˈya nun a thlǝkrha tǝ ƙǝƙǝn nun a thlǝkƙǝn wa. Ƙǝsǝr a mǝmǝlla sayidɗi na Faara a pǝrang ˈya kun nun a thlǝkrha.
\v 20 Ƙǝsǝr mbǝ kunni na a kaala sǝ wa, Sǝsǝn Chinun ni na a kaala sǝ ahur nun.
\p 
\v 21 “Wanmana nǝn a fǝr wanman a ɓǝlang ngganda. Chingya na nda a fǝr wanggindan, na wundakhnaya a thleng fa nggǝt yindan fa a ɓǝlang ngganda kanda.
\v 22 Na fiya heu a kar kun ƙǝsǝr ka nggi. Amma kala niifa ƙǝrǝsgha, nǝn a hǝrǝkrha.
\v 23 A sǝsang nda kun ahu yanɗi tala ya, ɗaama hu tala ɗǝ pak. Niya pǝrang ƙǝkafek kun, Nggi, na Wan Niifa, ni a wutta ɓa kapa nun weng talya Isǝreela hai heu.”
\p 
\v 24 “Wan tǝmakarantarha mbǝ kal tǝmalǝmndǝghǝn wa, tǝ ƙǝm mafarha mbǝ kal turighǝn wa.
\v 25 Wangya makarantaya kamɗǝ a na nda ƙǝla tǝmalǝmndǝn ndan, mafaya ƙǝm a na nda ƙǝla turi ndan. Nanǝn Nggi, na tuwuri ɗi, anda nggi kogna ǝnkaheeya, wangya wuriɗi ƙǝm na nda aah kanda tǝ thlǝma kalgha yina mu!”
\s1 Yanɗi kamngga a tǝrǝmnggǝnǝm
\r (Luka12:2-7)
\p 
\v 26 “Nanǝn kee, a tǝrǝm ɗun fingya na a sǝsang kun wa. Ƙǝsǝr na farghǝn ɓayi kala ˈya na nggǝnggǝla na nda a inang ɗǝ; kala ˈya na ɓǝɓee ƙǝm nǝn a kyarha pǝpal ɓa sǝkƙǝna fiya heu.
\v 27 ˈYa pǝrang ni kun hu wula, tǝraman urad nun sǝ pǝrghǝn nun a yanfaara a ɗalth mbǝrha hai. ˈYa shishiwang ni kun hu thlǝmaarha hai, tǝrama ten ƙǝnna sǝ tǝranggun urad nun sǝ pǝrghǝn nun sǝkƙǝna kowunni!
\v 28 A tǝrǝm ɗun fingya na a ɓǝl farha wa; ƙǝsǝr mba nda mbang ɓǝlang shingnda wa. Amma tǝrmama Faara katenggǝn, ndǝghǝn na mbang ɓǝlang farha tǝ shingnda kyab ahu hwanga.
\v 29 Mbǝ na nda heng wuɗikkya ɗǝ sǝri kobo tal wa? Amma a muk tal a hweeɗe hai na Chinun sǝnda sǝ.
\v 30 Ko was tengginun heu nǝghǝn thlǝthlǝɗa.
\v 31 Nanǝn kee, a tǝrǝm ɗun wa; kal ɗun wuɗikkya hangga a mbed Faara.”
\s1 Kyad sǝnda Yeeso a mbed fiya
\r (Luka12:8-9)
\p 
\v 32 “Niya ndang nda kun, kala niifa ndagha sǝnɗǝ nggi a mbed fiya hu ƙǝshidɗiya, nggi ƙǝm niya ndaarha sǝnɗi ndǝn a mbed Pǝpa na a talara.
\v 33 Amma niifa ƙǝm ndagha sǝngwa nggi wa a mbed fiya hu ƙǝshidɗiya, nggi ƙǝm niya ndaarha sǝngwi ndǝn wa a mbed Pǝpa na a talara.”
\s1 Tsaharha ha aten tsawud ɗǝɗemnggirha tǝ sǝsaarha
\r (Luka12:51-53; 14:26-27)
\p 
\v 34 A numaɗun ndon ɓang ni tsawud ɗǝɗemnggirha ƙǝshiirha ɓa wa. Awo, ɓawi ɓa tǝ tsawud ɗǝɗemnggirha wa, amma thlaukh ƙǝlara.
\v 35 “Ɓani ɓa ka a ɓi wumang yanda a pathlang:
\b
\q1 ‘Nda wee hǝshin tǝ chin,
\q2 nda wutararha tǝ man,
\q1 nda nu wee tǝ
\q2 thlaɓǝrghǝn tǝ nuwunda.
\v 36 Fa saryi nun,
\q2 na nda naarha ahur mindǝnun.’”
\b
\p 
\v 37 A nggǝmna tsu nduwa muwa ma nggi, tsǝkka a tsawana yina wa. Tǝ ƙǝm a nggǝmna wundǝlad wa nduwa wutarad wa ma nggi, tsǝkka a tsawana yina wa.
\v 38 Kala niifa kargha tǝr kaɗidghǝn fa mbu samadna nǝn, tsǝkkwa a tsauka yina wa.
\v 39 Kala niifa nggǝmngga yiɓǝdghǝn, nǝn a ƙǝɗeng nda, tǝ ƙǝm kala niifa ƙǝɗengga yiɓǝdghǝn ka nggi nǝn a walghǝn.
\s1 Tsaharha ha aten ƙǝna
\r (Markus9:41)
\p 
\v 40 “Kala niifa thlǝgha kun fa thlǝnǝn nggi, tǝ ƙǝm kala niifa thlǝgha nggi fa thlǝnǝn Chinɗi thlǝngga nggi ɓa.
\v 41 Kala niifa thlǝgha annabi fa ƙǝsǝr ka nanǝn annabi, nǝn a wal ƙǝnaghǝn yi annabi. Kala niifa thlǝgha ka niifa fa, ƙǝsǝr ka nanǝn ka niifa nǝn a wal ƙǝnaghǝn yi ka niifa.
\v 42 Kala niifa fǝrangga aam saarha na shishiu ahu wuhuleurha a tal ahur fingyayini na nggun-ngguchit ahu fatakkwayina, ƙǝkafek nǝn a wal ƙǝnaghǝn.”
\c 11
\s1 Laɓara aten Yahaya Tǝbaptisǝma
\r (Luka7:18-35)
\p 
\v 1 Ngwalang na Yeeso thlǝghang palthyini a fatsahayighǝn kumkap sǝri, kyagha sǝ ka ɗǝgha tsahang fiya ha tǝ pǝr laɓar Faara hu fingya a talya Yahudaya.
\p 
\v 2 Nana Yahaya tǝ Mbaptisǝma ahu porsǝna, sǝk laɓaara nǝn aten ǝnggini na Ƙǝrǝsti a ǝnarha. Tǝrgha thlǝn fatsahayighǝn nǝn ɗǝ ɗa nda tsahang mee Yeeso.
\v 3 Ndang ngganda Yeeso, “Sani Ƙǝrǝsti ɗi nan a ƙǝlaarha fa wa, nduwa ɗan mbeeɗǝ tǝ ƙǝla niifa fa pak wa?”
\p 
\v 4 Ndangga Yeeso kanda, “Wuɗaama ɗun pǝranggǝn Yahaya ˈya nun a sǝkrha tǝ ˈya nun a naarha.
\v 5 Kwamaya a na mana hai, Sǝfǝngya a wiirha hai, fa tǝrmeeya kanda a wal ƙǝnda, teɓengya a sǝk laɓaara, kanda a thleng mǝrya sǝ tǝ yibrha, tǝ ƙǝm kanda a pǝr Laɓara na Mbǝnggǝn a fa yamiya.
\v 6 Ndaaman, ‘A fǝrangga Faara parka fingya kawaa ƙǝsǝra, ƙǝsǝr ka nggi.’ ”
\p 
\v 7 Nana fatsaha yini ki Yahaya a wiirha, katǝrangga Yeeso tsǝ laɓaara hai aten Yahaya ahu terɗi wumngga hai. Ndanggǝn kanda, “Tur yanggi niifa ni ɗunun ka ƙǝlang nda a kaheerha ɗǝ? Niifa ni na kyakhrang hutenggǝn hai ƙǝla hwaliiya na nzǝnzang na ɓereurha a tsang ˈya fa wa?
\v 8 Nduwa nuwun a numad ndaarha ɗunun ka ƙǝlang niifa ɗǝ ngwagha fa tǝ kari na tǝ wuɗǝɓǝla fa ngga wa? Awo, nafiya na kal kari fa natǝ wuɗǝɓǝla na nda tsaurha a kwakirǝm kutǝra, mbǝ a kaheerha wa.
\v 9 Ɗunun ka kaɗa annabi wa? Yoo, kalɗǝ annabi.”
\v 10 “Ƙǝsǝr Ɗeleewar Faara tsǝɗǝ laɓaara aten Yahaya ndanǝn,
\b
\q1 ‘Niya thlǝn tǝthlǝndǝna ˈwagha mbeeɗǝ ma sa,
\q2 nǝn a takso kwamana ɗǝ kapa na ɓarhaɓa.’” \f + \fr 11:10 \ft Mal 3.1 \f*
\b
\m 
\v 11 Niya, pǝrang ƙǝkafek kun, mbǝ niifa sǝ nggǝt nanda hu ƙǝshidɗiya kalgha Yahaya tǝ mbaptisǝma mamnggirha wa. Amma ko yanɗa ni na ngguchit ahu Kutǝryid Talara kalɗǝ Yahaya mamnggirha.
\v 12 Ka a thlakh mbǝdɗi katǝrangna Yahaya tǝ mbaptisǝma pǝr laɓar Faara hai, ta weeri ɗaɓa ya, Kutǝryid Talara aten ɗǝrha mbeeɗǝ tǝ kanglanggirha, ko nanǝn fa mbǝlfeeya na nda a yanda tǝghǝn.
\v 13 Ƙǝsǝr kapa na Yahaya ɓarha ɓa, annabiya heu tǝ Ɗeleewar ngyakhrha Musa thlǝk nda ˈya ɓagha katǝrarha hai.
\v 14 A naɗun a nggǝmfa tǝ ˈya ndaani, Yahaya ndǝghǝnni Ilya, yanɗi ndana annabiya nǝn a ɓarha ɓa.
\v 15 Kala niifa na tǝ thlǝmad sǝkrha, sǝkƙǝnǝn.
\p 
\v 16 Tǝ ma ni sakh nafiya ƙǝshiid weeriya? Nǝghǝn ƙǝla wundakhnaya na a ɓashaarha a pǝpal kasu, na nda a aah ndan tǝ ndaarha:
\b
\q1 
\v 17 “‘Peng ɗan perǝma kunsǝ,
\q2 karɗun rǝbrha fa,
\q1 ang ɗan amshi mǝrra kunsǝ,
\q2 karɗun tǝrha fa.’
\b
\m 
\v 18 Ɓana Yahaya tǝ Mbaptisǝma ɓa mbǝ a hǝbrha tǝ saarha wa, amma kun a ndaarha, nǝghǝn tǝ ǝnkaheerha fa.”
\v 19 “Wan Niifa ɓa ɗaɓa, a hǝbrha, a saarha kun a ndaarha, ‘Tǝ yakh hǝbrha tǝ saarha, pashid fathlǝ tsamngya ni tǝ fa ɗimiya!’ Amma ana niifa tǝ sǝnda Faara na ǝn ǝnadghǝn kyadghǝn.”
\s1 Talya kargha malang ɗimiyid ndan
\r (Luka10:13-15)
\p 
\v 20 Tǝrgha katǝrangga Yeeso kiki talyi na fa ǝnanǝn ǝnwulteengya sǝ hangga, ƙǝsǝr malangwa nda ɗimiyid ndan kyakhra nda thlǝmad Faara ɓa wa.
\v 21 “Kawa Koridzin! Kawa Mbatseda! Ana ǝnwulteengya ɗǝɗamǝn ǝnanda ahur nun ndǝghǝn ǝnanda a Taya tǝ Sidon, kam ƙǝtǝm ˈwad nafi ndan teena malang nda ɗimiyid ndan, kal kukwasharya nda fa tǝ ƙǝm ƙǝmang ngganda yid ndan tǝ fishe.
\v 22 Niya ndang nda kun, a far ngwa kumarha, na Taya tǝ Sidon haɗang nda Faara fa ma kun.
\v 23 Kun ƙǝm nafiya Kafarnahum; tamngga ndaarha, nanda a mano a talara wa? Awo! Na ɗǝrha hu hwanga ɗǝ. Ƙǝsǝr ana ǝnwulteenggina ni ǝna nanda a kyanun ndǝn ǝna nanda a Sodom, ndǝghǝnni ƙǝm ɓalgha sǝ ta weeri ɓa ya.
\v 24 Niya ndang nda kun, a far ngwa kumarha, na Sodom a haɗang nda Faara fa ma kun.”
\s1 Ɓamaɓa ɓun yibrha a thlǝmadna
\r (Luka10:21-22)
\p 
\v 25 A sayidɗi ndagha Yeeso, “Usaɗi sa Pǝpa, Chinǝm yi talara tǝ hweeɗe, ɓǝɓengna ǝnggini heu ya a nafiya na ndǝndǝl tǝ fa hutengya, kyaɗang nggǝna pakhtǝɗuya.
\v 26 Nǝghǝn kee, Pǝpa, ndǝn kamogha yid!”
\p 
\v 27 Fǝre Pǝpa ǝngya heu, ƙǝsǝr ndǝghǝnni katenggǝn sǝngga Wanɗi. Ƙǝkafek yanɗi sǝngga Chinɗi ndǝna Wanɗi. Amma Wanɗi na midghǝn sǝ pǝrang laɓaara nǝn fingya aten Chinɗi, tǝna nda sǝnggǝn ƙǝm.
\p 
\v 28 “Ɓama thlǝmadna ɓa kun ɗakhna mid nun ɗǝ na tǝ rǝfrha in haaghǝn, niya yiɓang nda kun.
\v 29 Tǝrang miiwadna a kakhpǝniwa tǝna tsaharha a fanna. Mǝsǝlǝmnda niifa ni nggi hu sǝsǝna tǝ sammayirha, ƙǝsǝr nun a wal yibrha.
\v 30 Na tǝrra miiwadna pǝpa, rǝfǝdɗiya ƙǝm fǝrang ni kun nǝghǝn kaftang.”
\c 12
\s1 Tsakhmee aten far Yiɓǝd Yahudaya
\r (Markus2:23-28; Luka6:1-5)
\p 
\v 1 Tsǝɓaku, a sayidɗi na Yeeso a mbǝra ɗǝ tǝ heerha a far Yiɓǝd Yahudaya. Ƙǝsgha miirha fatsahayighǝn, tǝrgha ƙǝs kya ten wan hwaliirha nda na nda a kiighǝn.
\v 2 Amma nagha fingya Farisaya kanda ndang ngganda Yeeso, “Kuloɗǝ, fatsahayiwa a ǝna ˈya ˈyaɗana ngyakhrha na nda kya wan hwalirha a far Yibrha.”
\p 
\v 3 Ndangga Yeeso kanda, “Karatang ngwanun ǝnɗi na hu Ɗeleewar Faara ǝnana Ndauda ƙǝsna miirha ndǝn tǝ pashiyighǝn wa?”
\v 4 Kyagha hu Ƙǝn Faara ɗǝ, kii mburodi nda ɗǝfang nanda ɗǝ ka a kiigha firistaya.
\v 5 Nduwa karatang ngwa nun ahu ngyakhrha Musa ndanǝn nggǝmang nda firistaya fa a ǝna taara ahu Ƙǝn Faara na a Urshalima a far Yibrha wa?
\v 6 Niya ndang nda kun, ƙǝlama niifa ya kalgha Ƙǝn Faara na a Urshalima.
\v 7 Amma andam kwang sǝnang ɗun ˈya hai ndana Ɗeleewar Faara, ʻNa minna sǝ nagha fiya a haɗang kun fa, mbǝ ǝna sataka wa, kam ˈyarwun fatsahayina na ka nafiya wa,
\v 8 Ƙǝsǝr Wan Niifa Chinǝm ni, heu tǝ far Yibrha!
\s1 Ƙǝnang Yeeso niifa mǝrna harghǝn hai
\r (Markus3:1-6; Luka6:6-11)
\p 
\v 9 Tǝrgha wiirha Yeeso kyagha hu kǝn tsahad Yahudaya ɗǝ.
\v 10 A mbǝɗi na niifa sǝ mǝrna harghǝn hai. Tsahangga farisaya mee Yeeso, “Nggǝm ngyakhrha fa a ǝnagha niifa tar kǝnang nda niifa a far Yibrha?” Tamngganda ndaarha na Yeeso a ndaarha ooh, tǝna nda kǝsang nda tǝ ɗimiyirha.
\p 
\v 11 Ndanggǝn kanda, “Ana chaurad nun sǝ mukka hu kwaarha hai a far Yibrha, mbun ɗǝrhaɗǝ ɗun ƙǝɗang sǝ wa?
\v 12 Kal niifa chaurarha kaan, haˈi nggǝmang ngyakhrha niifa fa a ǝna ˈya na ngga a far Yibrha.”
\p 
\v 13 Tǝrgha ndanggǝn niifɗi, “Pǝpǝnang harwa ɗǝ.” Nanǝn kee pǝpǝnangga niifɗi harghǝn ɗǝ, nggǝrgha harɗi mǝmǝl kǝla tahadghǝn.
\p 
\v 14 Tǝrgha wumngga farisayina hai ka a kaɗa kwaman ɓǝlla Yeeso nda.
\s1 Yeeso ndǝna mafad Faara wurnǝn
\p 
\v 15 Sǝnangga Yeeso numad ndan hai. Nanǝn kee mal mbǝɗa nǝn, mbugha fiya samadghǝn hangga, ƙǝnanggǝn fiya heu na fandan ɓee ahur ndan.
\v 16 Amma ƙǝs thlǝmad ndan nǝn a pǝr nda tǝwunni ndǝghǝn wa.
\v 17 Tǝrgha lǝghǝdgha ˈya ndana Annabi Ishaya:
\b
\q1 
\v 18 Kǝlaman Mafanna wurni,
\q2 nggǝmɗi ndǝn, nǝn ǝna ˈya mbǝnegha,
\q1 Niya fǝrang sǝsǝnna,
\q2 nǝn a ǝna nggayirha a fingya heu.
\q1 
\v 19 Mbǝ ǝna kakyathlaanga tǝ fiya,
\q2 nduwa djargha hai ahur fiya wa.
\q1 
\v 20 Nǝn naarha tǝ sammayirha a fingya mbuwa kanglang,
\q2 nǝn fǝrang kaali niifa mbuwa tǝ mbǝrsaarha.
\q2 Akwasamadghǝn, kowunni nǝn a wal kwaman nggayirha.
\q1 
\v 21 Na thlǝmnggǝn a tsau yi mbǝrsad
\q2 ƙǝshiirha kahat.
\s1 Yeeso tǝ kutǝr ǝnkaheeya
\r (Markus3:20-30; Luka11:14-23; 12:10)
\p 
\v 22 Tǝrgha ɓang niifa nda Yeeso ɓa na tǝ ǝnkaheerha fa, na kwamarǝn tǝ ƙǝm mbǝ mbang kalasǝ wa. Ƙǝnanggǝn niifɗi mbanggǝn kaala sǝ tǝ na maana hai kyab.
\v 23 Fiya heu na ǝnwulteena nda tsakhmee nda, “Ndee mbǝ Yeeso ɗa na ya, na wan Ndauda wa?”
\p 
\v 24 Amma sǝkna Farisaya ǝnwulteenɗi ǝnanǝn, ndaa nda, “Mbǝ ngaala sǝ wa kyang ɗǝ ǝnkaheeya sǝ. Ƙǝsǝr walghǝn sǝsǝmnda a ahar Sheetan kutǝr ǝnkaheeya.”
\p 
\v 25 Sǝnangga Yeeso numad ndan hai, nggǝranggǝn kanda sǝ, “Kala kutǝryirha ndǝkka hai tǝ yanda mbǝ tam isha wa, tǝ ƙǝm kala tala nduwa wure ndǝkka hai tǝ kakyathlaanga nǝn weela ɗǝ.
\v 26 Ana sheetan a kyang sheetan sǝ, nǝn a yanda tǝ altenggǝn. Mbǝ kutǝryidghǝn a mǝndaha wa.
\v 27 Ana tǝ sǝsǝmnda Sheetan ni kyan ǝnkaheeya sǝ, tǝ sǝsǝmnda wun na fatakkwayinun kyang kanda sǝ? Fatakkwayinun ni a ngwang kumarha kun sǝ.
\v 28 Amma a kyangɗi ǝnkaheeya sǝ tǝ Sǝsǝn Faara, nanǝn kee Kutǝryid Faara ɓaa ɗǝ pathlang nun ɓa.”
\p 
\v 29 Wunni na kanglang kaan na mbang kyaarha hu minda ki niifa hai na kanglang ƙǝla Sheetan ngaaranggǝn ǝnggighǝn? Ƙǝl ˈwanǝn teena ƙǝnanggǝn niifɗa hai na kanglang ˈwan a mbanggǝn har ǝngya na midghǝn.
\p 
\v 30 Kala niifa mbuwa tǝ nggi, nǝn a tsan nggi. A mba a ɗee sǝ wumang fiya ɓa wa, na a waleng kanda ɗǝ.
\v 31 Niya ndang nda kun, kala tur yanggi ɗimiyirha ǝnana nduwa ndaana na nda a chahoƙǝn ɗǝ. Ko kalna sǝ yi ˈyar Wan Niifa, na nda a chahoƙǝn ɗǝ. Amma a sarna Sǝsǝna tǝ Peɗǝnda, mba nda tam chahoƙǝn ɗǝ wa, ko nanǝnya nduwa ƙǝshiirha na ɓayi.
\v 32 Kala niifa ˈyargha Wan Niifa na nda mbang chahanggǝn ɗǝ, amma kala niifa ˈyargha Sǝsǝna tǝ Peɗǝnda, mba nda tam chahanggǝn ɗǝ wa, ko nanǝnya nduwa ƙǝshiirha na ɓayi.
\s1 Nǝm sǝn ɗǝfrha tǝ tur wanggighǝn
\r (Luka6:43-45)
\p 
\v 33 Ana ɗǝfrha ngga, na wanggighǝn naarha ngga. A mbǝ ɗǝfrha ngga wa, mbǝ wanggighǝn narha ngga wa. Nǝm sǝn ɗǝfrha tǝ tur wanggighǝn.
\v 34 Kun huthlingya, ƙǝƙǝn na nafiya natǝ mbǝlfeerha fa ƙǝla kun thlǝk ˈya na ngga tǝ ƙǝm kamngga? Ƙǝsǝr ˈya na ahurwa ndǝghǝn na a kyarha ɓa thlǝkƙǝna.
\v 35 Ka nafiya na nda ǝna ˈya na ngga ahur ndan sǝ, amma fambǝlfeeya na nda kyang ǝngya ɓa mbuwa ngga ahur ndan sǝ.
\p 
\v 36 Niya pǝrang palthɗi kun ya, a far ngwa kumarha tǝtani a ngwang kumarha nda kun sǝ aten ˈya na ɗimi ndaanun.
\v 37 Ənɗi kyagha ɓa a miiwa nǝn a hǝrworha nduwa ƙǝnoghǝn.
\s1 Famalǝmgya ngyakhrha tǝ Farisaya a kaɗa ǝnsakhrha
\r (Markus8:11-12; Luka11:29-32)
\p 
\v 38 Farɗasǝ fingya famalǝmngya ngyakrha Musa tǝ Farisaya ɓanda thlǝmad Yeeso ɓa ndang ngganda, “Mala, na minnasǝ a kyaɗang sakh ǝnwulteena na kan na a kyad ndaarha furo Faara sǝsǝmnda.”
\p 
\v 39 Amma nggǝrangga Yeeso kanda sǝ, “Nafiya ƙǝshiid weeriya fambǝlfeeya tǝ fa yamid fǝrƙǝkafek ndǝna kaɗa ǝnsakhrha yi wulteena, amma mbǝ ǝn sakhrha sǝ na nda a kyaɗang kanda wa, kǝl yanɗi ki annabi Yunana.
\v 40 Kǝla ǝnana Yunana ɓeena mahan tǝ paara mahan ahur tǝna, nanǝn kee na Wan Niifa a ǝna ɓeena mahan tǝ paara mahan kǝm ahu kwaarha.
\v 41 A far ngwa kumarha na nafiya Nineba a thleng nafiya ƙǝshiid weeri fa ya kyaɗang ndaarha nda kanda ǝnawa nda mǝmǝl wa, ƙǝsǝr kanda malang nda ɗimiyid ndan, ka laɓar Faara thlǝghangna Yunana kanda. Nanǝnya, kulo niifa kalgha Yunana a mbǝɗiya, amma karɗun malang nda ɗimiyid nun!
\v 42 A far ngwa kumarha, na Kwatam nda Sheeba a thleng nafiya ƙǝshiid weeri fa ya kyaɗang ndaarha nǝn kanda ǝnawun mǝmǝl wa. Ɓaghǝn ɓa a mbǝrha na inggun ka ɓagha sǝk sǝnda Sulemanu. Nanǝnya kulo niifa a mbǝɗiya kalgha Sulemanu, amma karɗun kang thlǝmaarha fa.”
\s1 Wutta Ənkaheerha ɓa
\r (Luka11:24-26)
\p 
\v 43 “A kya ǝnkaheerha sǝ a fad niifa, nǝn ɗǝrha ka kaɗa mbǝd yibrha a kaheerha ɗǝ, amma mbǝ waala wa.
\v 44 Tǝrgha nǝn ndaarha, ‘Niya wutta thlǝmad niifɗa ɗǝ kyani saɓa.’ Nanǝn kee wudgha ɓagha wal wuriɗi mal nǝn mbǝ niifa sǝ wa, ngwa wuriɗa ɗǝ ngga, tangsang nda.
\v 45 Tǝrgha na ǝnkaheedɗi a kaɗa ǝnkaheeya ɓa mǝd kalgha ndǝn mbǝlfeerha kya nda hur niifɗa hai tsawa nda sǝ. A kwasamadghǝn, tsawud niifɗiya sǝssadghǝn nǝn kal yi kaar. Nun a tsaurha kee kun fambǝlfeeya ƙǝshiid weeriya.”
\s1 Man Yeeso tǝ wanmanggighǝn
\r (Markus3:31-35; Luka8:19-21)
\p 
\v 46 Nana Yeeso a ndikrha tǝ fiya wumngga hai, man tǝ wanmanggighǝn ƙǝƙǝt a ƙǝshi, na minda sǝ a ndiya nda tǝghǝn.
\v 47 Ndangga niifa Yeeso, “Nda muwa tǝ wanmanggiwa a ƙǝshi, na minda sǝ ndikrha tǝ sa.”
\v 48 Tsakhka Yeeso mee, “Wunni iiya? Mingya ni kǝm wanmanggina?”
\v 49 Tǝrgha kyad fatsahayighǝn nǝn ɗǝ tǝ haara ndǝghǝn, “Ƙǝlama nda iiya tǝ wanman nggina ha ya.
\v 50 Tsaunǝn kee, kala niifa ǝnagha ˈya ndana Pǝpa na a talara, ndǝghǝnni wan pa, wanya tǝ ƙǝm iiya.”
\c 13
\s1 Karapu aten tǝhǝfrha
\r (Markus4:9; Luka8:8)
\p 
\v 1 Tsu a farɗi malgha Yeeso wuriɗi ɗǝgha a mii wuri aam Nggalili ɗǝ.
\v 2 Wumngga fiya thlǝmadghǝn ɓa hangga, nanǝn kee kyagha hu kombuwol hai. Tsauka ahur kombuwolɗi nagha a tsahang fiya ha na ƙǝƙǝt a mii wuri aamɗi.
\p 
\v 3 Tsǝɗǝ asǝɗaya hangga tǝ karapuya, ndǝghǝn: “Kama thlǝmaarha hai! Tǝhuɗaarha ɗǝɗǝ ka hǝfrha ɗǝ.
\v 4 Nanǝn aten wash wiidɗi, hǝrgha fingya hai aten kwamana, ɓagha wuɗikkya ɓa ɗamangganda.
\v 5 Hǝrgha fingya hu hǝreng keela hai, ka mbuwana chehweerha sǝ kaan kya nda sǝ ƙǝkar.
\v 6 Amma tǝkna yanfaara hai, hwara nda ɗǝ mǝra nda, ƙǝsǝr kwa wa nda thlaara hai wa.
\v 7 Fingya wiiya hǝra nda pathlang ndakhkya hai ˈyaɓangga ndakhkini kanda.
\v 8 Amma fingya hǝra nda hu chehweerha hai na ngga kyanda sǝ ǝna wee nda fingya katǝra kumnggit mahan-mahan, fingya ƙǝm kumnggit mikki-mikki har haru-haru.”
\p 
\v 9 “Kala niifa na tǝ thlǝmad sǝkrha, sǝkƙǝnǝn.”
\s1 ˈYa ǝnagha ndǝn na Yeeso tsaharha ha tǝ karapu
\r (Markus4:10-12; Luka8:9,10)
\p 
\v 10 Tǝrgha ɓagha fatsahayighǝn thlǝmadghǝn ɓa tsahang mee nda, “Kama na thlǝk karapuya a nanna a kalang fiya sǝ?”
\p 
\v 11 Nggǝranggǝn kanda sǝ, “Nggǝmang nda kun fa na a sǝn ˈya nun na Kutǝryid Talara ahurghǝn, amma fingya nggǝmang ngwanda kanda fa wa.
\v 12 Kala niifa natǝ ˈya ha na nda chighanggǝn tsǝghanggǝn kaan, amma kala niifa mbuwana ˈyasǝ a harghǝn, na nda a thlang ngguchit tǝɗi na harghǝn.
\v 13 Ndǝghǝnni ni ǝna taara tǝ karapuya a naɗi a kalang kanda sǝ ƙǝsǝr,
\b
\q1 na nda ƙǝlaarha ɗǝ, amma mba nda naghǝn wa,
\q2 na nda kathlǝmaarha hai, amma mba nda sǝkƙǝn nduwa sǝnang ngganda hai wa.”
\b
\m 
\v 14 “Ndǝn na lǝghǝtta ˈya ndaana annabi Ishaya:
\b
\q1 ‘A sǝkɗun ˈya ndaani,
\q2 Mbun sǝnang hai wa,
\q1 A naɗun ˈya ǝnani,
\q2 mbun kukwalang hai wa.
\b
\q1 
\v 15 Ƙǝsǝr na ten ndan kakrak,
\q2 mbǝ thlǝmaayi ndan sǝk ˈya wa,
\q1 nggǝlang nda yid ndan,
\q2 nanǝn kee mbǝ yid ndan na maana hai wa,
\q1 mbǝ thlǝmaayi ndan sǝk ˈya wa,
\q2 Mbǝ ten ndan sǝnang hai wa,
\q1 Mba nda kyaharra thlǝmadna ɓa wa,
\q2 ngwa ƙǝnang nggi kanda.’” \f + \fr 13:15 \xt Ishaya6:9,10\xt*\f*
\b
\p 
\v 16 “Amma na yid nun tǝ parka, ƙǝsǝr na nda namaana hai; tǝ thlǝmaayinun ƙǝm, ƙǝsǝr na nda sǝk ˈya.
\v 17 Niya Pǝrang ƙǝkafek kun, annabiya hangga tǝ ka fiya tǝrmindan na ǝnɗi nanun ya, amma nawa ndan wa. Tǝrmindan sǝk ǝnɗi sǝk nun ya, amma sǝkkwa ndan wa.”
\s1 Pǝr Yeeso ten karapuɗi kii tǝ hǝfrha
\r (Markus4:13-20; Luka8:11-15)
\p 
\v 18 “Nanǝnya kaama thlǝmaarha hai ngga, sǝk ten karapu ɗanun kii tǝhǝfǝdɗi.
\v 19 Fingya sǝkka laɓar Kutǝryid Talara amma sǝnangwa nda hai wa, na nda ƙǝla wiirha hǝrgha hai a kwamana, ɓagha Tǝbǝlfeedɗa ɓa thlanggǝn ǝnɗa ɗǝ hǝf nanda ahur ndan hai.
\v 20 Fingya wiiya hǝrgha aten keela hai nǝghǝn ƙǝla fingya sǝkka laɓarɗi thlǝghǝn nda fa tǝ wutsǝfayirha.
\v 21 Amma kwa wa thlaara hai ngga wa, mbǝ mǝnda ha wa. A ɓa ɓillaarha ɓa nduwa sǝsaarha ƙǝsǝr ka laɓarɗi, mba nda kwas kyaharra hai wa.
\v 22 Fingya wiiya hǝrgha ahu ndakhkya hai, nǝghǝn aten fingya sǝkka laɓarɗi, amma ɓillaarha yi ƙǝshidɗiya tǝ nggǝmnda ƙǝna ˈyaɓang nggǝn laɓarɗi ˈyaɗang tsǝrha nǝn fa mbǝ ˈyasǝ na nda mbang ǝnaarha ngga wa.
\v 23 Amma fingya hǝf nǝn ahu chehweerha na ngga nǝghǝn aten nafiya sǝkka laɓar ɗi, sǝnang ngganda hai wal chikrha nda fingya kumnggit mahan-mahan, fingya kumnggit mikki-mikki, tǝ ƙǝm fingya haru-haru.”
\s1 Karapu aten wuthlaafa ahur wan hwaliirha
\p 
\v 24 Nggǝrgha Yeeso thlǝghang karapu kanda sǝ, ndǝghǝn, “Kutǝryid Talara nǝghǝn kiya: Hǝf niifa wiirha ngga ahu hedghǝn.
\v 25 A fǝɗikrha nana fiya a ɓeena, ɓagha tǝtsanda ɓa hǝf wuthlaafa nǝn a pathlang wiid wan hwalidɗa hai wii fayighǝn nǝn.
\v 26 Katǝrana wan hwalidɗi tsǝrha tǝ yiwee, nagha wuthlaafɗi ƙǝm a tsǝrha.”
\v 27 Tǝrgha ɓagha fatarya tǝhedɗa ɓa ndang ngganda tǝheedɗi, “Tuwuri nan, hedɗi hǝfang na tǝ wiirha ngga lǝghǝdɗǝ tǝ wuthlaafa! Kyagha nda ɓa a yanggi?”
\v 28 Ndagha tǝheedɗi, “ ‘Tǝtsanda ni ǝnagha ǝnɗiya!’” Ndagha fataryini, “Ɗan ƙǝɗang kanda ɗǝ wa?”
\v 29 Ndagha tǝheedɗi, “ ‘Awo.’ a ǝna ɗun kee nun ɗǝ ƙǝɗang kanda ɗǝ heu tǝ wan hwalidɗi.
\v 30 ‘Malaman kanda tsǝnda kyab ƙǝl a shifiirha ana ɗǝm a halthghǝn. Tǝrgha a ndanggi fahalthya wurang ngganda wuthlaafa sǝ, ƙǝnang ngganda kanda djang ngganda ɗǝ, tǝrgha wan hwalidghǝn iree ƙǝnda ahu ɓirwa hai.’ ”
\s1 Karapu aten wiirha na ƙǝla wan parsǝna
\r (Markus4:30-32; Luka13:18,19)
\p 
\v 31 Nggǝrgha Yeeso pǝrang karapu kanda, ndǝghǝn, “Kutǝryid Talara nǝghǝn kǝla wan parsǝna tǝrangna niifa hǝfanggǝn hai ahu hedghǝn.
\v 32 Wiirha ni na ngguchit kaan ahur wiiya, amma tsǝnǝn sǝ, tsauka ɗǝfrha ni na manggǝn kaan ahur ɗǝfya heu, taksaagha wuɗikkya ƙǝn ndan ahu wuharyighǝn.”
\s1 Karapu aten mekhna
\r (Luka13:20,21)
\p 
\v 33 Nggǝrgha Yeeso pǝrang karapu kanda ndǝghǝn, “Kutǝryid Talara nǝghǝn ƙǝla mekhna yangna nuneefa tǝ humbarha tasau mahan ana ɗǝ a ǝna mburodi. Ko nanǝn ǝnaghǝn mehenɗi sahai ngguchit kiya, nǝn chichaɗang hufgha sǝ.”
\s1 Na Yeeso tsaharha tǝ karapu ka a lǝɗanggǝn ˈya nda annabi
\r (Markus4:33,34)
\p 
\v 34 Kala tsaharha na Yeeso ǝnaarha a fiya wumngga hai ƙǝl tǝ karapu, mbǝ ˈyasǝ nǝn thlǝghang kanda kula karapu wa.
\v 35 “Ndǝn lǝghǝdna laɓar Faara ndanǝn a mii annabi,
\b
\q1 Niya kalang kunsǝ tǝ karapu,
\q2 niya pǝr ˈya na ɓǝɓee, ka ǝna nanda ƙǝshiirha.”
\s1 Pǝr Yeeso ten karapuɗi yi wan hwaliirha tǝ wuthlaafa
\p 
\v 36 Malgha Yeeso fiya a ƙǝshi kyagha hur minda hai. Ndangga fatsahayighǝn, “Nan a hwan sa pǝrang ten karapuɗi kan yi wan hwaliirha tǝ wuthlaafa na ahu hedɗi.”
\p 
\v 37 Nggǝrangga Yeeso kanda sǝ, “Tǝheedɗi ndǝna Wan Niifa hǝfgha wiirha na ngga.
\v 38 Hedɗi ndǝna ƙǝshiirha, wiirha na ngga ndǝna aten nafiya Kutǝryidɗi. Wuthlaafa ndǝna nafiya Tǝbǝlfeedɗi.
\v 39 Tǝtsandǝɗi hǝfgha wuthlaafɗi a pathlang wan hwalidɗa ɗǝ ndǝna Sheetan. Halthɗi ndǝna mii ngwala ƙǝshiirha, fahalthyini ƙǝm ndǝna fathlǝngya Faara.
\v 40 Ƙǝla wurang nanda wuthlaafa sǝ djang ngganda ɗǝ hu waarha, nǝn a naarha kee a mii ngwala ƙǝshiirha.
\v 41 Na Wan Niifa a thlǝn fathlǝnggighǝn, ɗa nda ƙǝɗang ǝngya ɗǝ heu na ahu Kutǝryidghǝn na ɓang ɗimiyirha ɓa tǝ fingya na a ǝna mbǝlfeerha.
\v 42 Na nda a muwang kanda ahu waarha ɗǝ mbuwa mǝra hai, a mbǝɗani na nanda naarha tǝrha tǝ ƙǝtmee.
\v 43 Tǝrgha fingya ǝnagha nggayirha na nda a djaara hai ƙǝla yanfaara ahu Kutǝryid Chi ndan. Kala niifa natǝ thlǝmad sǝkrha, sǝkƙǝnǝn!”
\s1 Karapu aten ƙǝna na ɓǝɓee
\p 
\v 44 Nanǝn kee ndagha Yeeso, “Kutǝryid Talara nǝghǝn ƙǝla ƙǝna na ɓǝɓee walang na niifa hu heerha. Nanǝn tǝ wutsǝfayirha nggǝrghǝn ɓǝɓeng hai hu hedɗi, henggǝn ǝnggighǝn ɗǝ heu ka a wal wuɗǝɓǝla nǝn ngga henggǝn hedɗa sǝ.”
\s1 Karapu aten djamkwatar
\p 
\v 45 Ƙǝmɗa, Kutǝryid Talara nǝghǝn ƙǝla tǝshafiliirha na a kaɗa djamkwatar.
\v 46 Ƙǝla nǝn hai na djamkwatarɗi tǝ wuɗǝɓǝla fa, henggǝn ǝnggighǝn ɗǝ heu henggǝn sǝ!
\s1 Karapu aten panggaama
\p 
\v 47 “Tǝ ƙǝm, Kutǝryid Talara nǝghǝn ƙǝla panggaama muwang nanda hu wuri aama ɗǝ ƙǝs tǝngya nǝn ɗǝɗamǝn-ɗǝɗamǝn.
\v 48 Lǝghǝdna panggamɗi, kahang ngganda ƙǝƙǝshɓangnda ɓa. Tǝrgha tsawa nda hai, wurang ngganda tǝngya sǝ na nggǝngga ahu kutaasa hai, amma tsamang ngganda fingyayina ɗǝ mbuwa ngga.
\v 49 Ɓanǝn naarha kee a mii ngwala ƙǝshiirha. Na fathlǝngya Faara a ɓaarha ɓa wurang ngganda nafiya ɗǝ na a ǝna mbǝlfeerha ahur nafiya na a ǝna nggayirha.
\v 50 Na nda a muwang fa mbǝlfeeya ahu waarha ɗǝ mbuwa mǝra hai, a mbǝɗani na nanda naarha tǝrha sǝ tǝ ƙǝtmee.”
\s1 Suhurra tǝ weerǝnda ƙǝna
\p 
\v 51 Tsahangga Yeeso mee fatsahayighǝn, “Sǝnang ɗun ǝnggina hai heu ya wa?” Nggǝrang ngganda sǝ, “Oh, sǝnang ɗan hai.”
\p 
\v 52 Tǝrgha nggǝrghǝn chikƙǝn ndaagha, “Kala tǝmalǝmnda ngyakhrha tsauka tǝtsaharha ahu Kutǝryid Talara nǝghǝn ƙǝla tuwure kyangga hurad tǝ weerǝnda ǝnggighǝn sǝ a mbǝrha ɗǝ ɗǝfnǝn ƙǝnaghǝn sǝ.”
\s1 Kar nda Yeeso a Nadzarat
\r (Markus6:1-6; Luka4:16-30)
\p 
\v 53 Ngwalangna Yeeso pǝr karapu yini mal mbǝɗa nǝn.
\v 54 Wudgha hu talghǝn ɗǝ Nadzarat. Tsaha nǝn ha hu ƙǝn tsahad Yahudaya, fiya heu sǝkka ndǝn ǝna ǝnwulteena na nda, na nda a ndaarha, “Walgha niifɗi tur sǝndǝɗi tǝ sǝsǝmnda ǝna ǝnwulteengya a yanggi?”
\v 55 Tǝrgha na nda a ndaarha, “Mbǝ wan kafinta ɗani ya, sǝnɗǝm Mairamu man, tǝ wanmanggighǝn nda Yakubu tǝ Yisufu, tǝ Siman tǝ Yahuda?
\v 56 Kulo wanmanggighǝn nishya ya ahur nǝm. Tsahaghǝn ǝnggini a yanggi ya?”
\v 57 Nanǝn kee, karghǝnda fa, fǝr wanda ƙǝkafek tǝghǝn wa. Tǝrgha ndangga Yeeso kanda, “Na nda manang nda annabi ko a yanggini ƙǝl ahur talghǝn ahu nafiyighǝn.”
\v 58 Əna ǝnwulteengya nǝn ngguchit kee, ƙǝsǝr ka yamid fǝrƙǝkafekkid ndan.
\c 14
\s1 Mǝrra Yahaya Tǝbaptisǝma
\r (Markus6:14-29; Luka9:7-9)
\p 
\v 1 A sayidɗi Sǝkna Hirdus Kutǝr chehweed Nggalili laɓar Yeeso,
\v 2 ndanggǝn fataryighǝn, “Yahaya Tǝbaptisǝma ni ya thliigha sǝ hu mǝrra! Ndǝn nanǝn tǝ sǝsǝmnda ǝna ǝnwultenggini ya.”
\p 
\v 3 Nanǝnya Hirdus ˈwaɗǝ teena ƙǝsang ɗǝ Yahaya, ƙǝnanggǝn, muwanggǝn hu porsǝna ɗǝ ka Herodiya nu wanman Filibus kahang nǝn.
\v 4 Ƙǝsǝr Yahaya nǝn naarha ndang nda Hirdus ahu ngyakhrha Yahudaya kamngwa a kahanggǝn Herodiya wa.
\v 5 Na mid Hirdus sǝ a ɓǝlanggǝn Yahaya, amma nǝghǝn a tǝrǝm fiya, ƙǝsǝr fiya heu fǝr nda kǝkafek tǝ ndaarha Yahaya Annabi ni.
\p 
\v 6 Amma a far wutsǝfayid lǝghǝtta ɓen nggǝtta Hirdus, wutarad Herodiya rǝɓanggǝn kanda sǝ, mbǝnanggǝn Hirdus kaan.
\v 7 Nggǝmɗa fa har tǝ aah thlǝm Faara, kala ˈya na midghǝn nǝn a fǝranggǝn.
\p 
\v 8 Ndangga man wutaradɗi ɗǝgha ndaarha, “Ten Yahaya Tǝbaptisǝma na minna ahu pǝlee.”
\p 
\v 9 Kutǝrɗi ƙǝm ǝna masǝnɗi kee nǝn aten ˈya ndanǝn, amma ƙǝsǝr ka thlǝm Faara aah nǝn a mbed nafiya mbunǝn ɓa, ǝnang ǝnɗa nda ndanǝn.
\v 10 Thlǝn sodjaya nǝn a kyathlang ngganda ten Yahaya ɓa ahu porsǝna.
\v 11 Ɓang ten ɗa nda wutaradɗa ɓa ahu pǝlee, ɗanggǝnǝn man ɗǝ.
\v 12 Tsǝɓaku ɓagha fatsahaya Yahaya ɓa tǝrang ngganda mǝrrǝghǝn ɓa pang ngganda, tǝrgha ɗǝnda ɗǝ pǝranggǝn nda Yeeso.
\s1 Hǝɓang Yeeso nafiya haru kumnggit tuf
\r (Markus6:30-44; Luka9:10-17; Yahaya6:1-14)
\p 
\v 13 Sǝkna Yeeso laɓarɗi, kyagha hu kombuwol hai, mal mbǝɗa nǝn ɗǝgha mbǝrha ɗǝ ka a tsauka katenggǝn. Amma sǝkna fiya mbǝɗi nanǝn sǝ, mbu samadghǝn nda tǝ saara ahu talya ɓa hangga.
\v 14 Tǝrna Yeeso hai ahu kombuwol ɗi, na fiya nǝn hangga haɗangganda fa, ƙǝnanggǝn haya.
\p 
\v 15 Na figrha a tsǝrha hai, ɓagha fa tsahayighǝn a thlǝmadghǝn ɓa, ndang ngganda, “Kaheerha ni ya tǝ kǝm tsǝ figrha hai, kalu fiya hai ɗǝnda hu talya ɗǝ, tǝna nda ɗǝ hii ǝnnarhami.”
\p 
\v 16 Amma nggǝrangga Yeeso kanda sǝ, “Kamngwa a wii nda a miirha wa, fǝraman ˈya kanda ǝna nda mii.”
\p 
\v 17 Ndangga nda, “Mburodi tuf ni kee a harnan, tǝ tǝngya sǝri.”
\p 
\v 18 Ndagha, “Ɓemadghǝn mbǝɗa ɓa ya.”
\v 19 Tǝrgha ndanggǝn fiya tsawanda hai a ten hwaliirha, tǝranggǝn mburodi ɗa sǝ tuf tǝ tǝnggini sǝri, kǝlagha talara sǝ, ɗǝfang parka nǝn in. Kyanggǝn mburodi ɗa hai fǝranggǝnǝn fatsahayighǝn ndǝghang nggǝnda fiya.
\v 20 Kii nda kanda heu kǝla na mindan pa tsǝghanggǝn kanda, tǝrgha fatsahayighǝn wumangga nda katǝbghǝn kutasya kumkap sǝri.
\v 21 Hǝshya kiigha mburodi ɗi sǝl nda haru kumnggit tuf, thlǝɗang ngwa nda nishya tǝ wundakhnaya wa.
\s1 Wii Yeeso a ten aama
\r (Markus6:45-52; Yahaya6:15-21)
\p 
\v 22 Tsu a mbǝɗi kee, ndangga Yeeso fatsahayighǝn kya nda hu kombuwal hai tǝɗang ngganda wuri aama teena, ndǝghǝnggi ƙǝm ishgha hai kal fiya nǝn hai.
\v 23 A kwasamad ɗi kal nǝn fiya hai, tǝrgha wumnda sǝ katenggǝn ka a hwan Faara nǝn, tsǝgha figrha hai ndǝghǝn a mbǝɗi katenggǝn.
\p 
\v 24 Amma ahu sayidɗiya kombuwol ɗi inggun ma ƙǝkǝshɓanda, fatsahayini a habɓaarha tǝ ɓereurha tǝ kuɗufulla aama.
\p 
\v 25 Takhna mbǝrha a ɗathla hai ɓagha Yeeso thlǝman ndan ɓa, a wiirha aten aama.
\v 26 Nana fatsahayighǝn ndǝn a wiirha aten aamɗi tǝrma nda. Ka hǝreenga huhwa nda, tamngganda ndaarha mǝnda-mǝnda ni.
\p 
\v 27 Amma tsu kee kalangga Yeeso kanda sǝ, “A tǝrǝm ɗun wa nggini ƙǝrsaama.”
\p 
\v 28 Ndangga Siman, “Chinǝm, ana ƙǝkafek sani, ndee ɗi thlǝmad wa ɗǝ a aten aamɗi.”
\p 
\v 29 Ndangga Yeeso, “Haˈi, ɓoɓa,” tǝrgha siman tǝrgha hai ahu kombuwal ɗi, ƙǝs wiirha nǝn aten aamɗi a thlǝmad Yeeso ɗǝ.
\v 30 Amma nanǝn ɓereu ˈyaarɗi tǝrǝmngga, nagha a timnda hai, huhwagha ndagha, “Hǝrye Chinǝm.”
\p 
\v 31 Tsu kee Ƙǝsgha Yeeso harghǝn ƙǝsanggǝn ɓa, ndangga Yeeso, “Ƙǝɗi fǝrƙǝkafekkid wa, ƙǝn fǝr waana ƙǝkafek na mbang wiirha aten aamɗi?”
\p 
\v 32 Kyana nda ahu kombuwal hai, ishgha ɓereu ˈyaarɗi.
\v 33 Tǝrgha fatsahayighǝn ɗǝfang shilee nda in, na nda a ndaarha, “Ƙǝkafek Wan Faarani Sa.”
\s1 Ƙǝnang Yeeso haaya a Djanasarat
\r (Markus6:53-56)
\p 
\v 34 A kwasamadɗi tǝɗang na nda wuri aamɗi teena, tǝra nda hai a Djanasarat.
\v 35 Kukwalang na nafiya talɗa hai Yeeso ni, thlǝn farha nda ahu talya ɗǝ na ahu chehwedɗi kahat. Nagha fiya a ɓarha ɓa tǝ haaya, ka a ƙǝnanggǝn kanda.
\v 36 Hwanggǝnda a malanggǝn haaya tsuwar mii kotodghǝnda fa kee, kala niifa tsuwargha ndǝn fa ƙǝnɗǝ.
\c 15
\s1 Tsahad chichiiya ha
\r (Markus7:1-13)
\p 
\v 1 Tǝrgha fingya Farisaya tǝ famalǝmngya ngyakhrha thliigha ɓa a Urshalima tsahang mee nda Yeeso,
\v 2 “Kama na fatsahayiwa hwasang ǝntin shingginǝm? Mba nda tsaɓang haryi ndan ɗǝ a hǝb ǝnnarhami nda wa!”
\p 
\v 3 Nggǝrangga Yeeso kanda sǝ, “Kama nun hwasang nda ǝngya ndaana Faara ka ǝntinggi nun?
\v 4 Ƙǝsǝr ndagha Faara, ‘Fǝrang mamnggirha nda muwa tǝ tsu’ tǝ ƙǝm ‘Kala niifa sargha man nduwa chin tǝtani a ɓǝlang ngganda.’
\v 5 Amma nun tsaharha ha tǝ ndaarha ana ˈya sǝ a haar niifa na a ɗanggǝn chin sǝ nduwa man, nǝn ndaarha ‘ˈya nun a kya waala a fanna ɗǝfang ɗi ndǝn Faara ɗǝ.’
\v 6 Ahu kwamana kiya Mǝmǝlwa a fǝrang mamnggirha nǝn fa nggǝtyighǝn tǝghǝn wa. Nanǝn kee kar laɓar ɗanun fa ndaana Faara ka ǝntin nun.
\v 7 Kun fathǝrɓuya! Laɓar Faara ndaana Ishaya aten nun mǝmǝlni:
\b
\q1 
\v 8 ‘Nafiniya ahu mii ndan ni kee na nda fǝre mamnggirha,
\q2 amma huryi ndan nǝghǝn inggun ma nggi;
\q1 
\v 9 ka ni kee na nda ɗǝfee shilee teena,
\q2 ƙǝsǝr ɗǝfang ngganda tsahad ngyakhkya fiya ha a mbee a meyed laɓar Faara.’ ”\x * \xo 15:9 \xt Ishaya29:13\x*
\s1 Əngya na tsawang nda niifa ɗimi a mbed Faara
\r (Markus7:14-23)
\p 
\v 10 Tǝrgha aagha Yeeso nafini wumngga hai a thlǝmadghǝn ɓa ndǝghǝn, “Keema thlǝmaarha fa tǝnun sǝn ǝnɗi niya thlǝkrha.
\v 11 ˈYa kyagha hur niifa hai mbǝ ndǝna tsawang tǝ ‘paarha’ fa wa, amma ƙǝl ˈya na a kyarha ɓa a miighǝn ndǝna tsawang tǝ ‘paarha’ fa.”
\p 
\v 12 Tǝrgha fatsahayini ɓa nda thlǝmadghǝn ɓa tsahang mee nda, “Sǝnna sǝ sǝb hur Farisayina ɗǝ sǝk nanda laɓarɗi?”
\p 
\v 13 Nggǝrangga Yeeso kanda sǝ, “Kala hǝfrha a mbǝ pǝpa na a talara hǝfgha ndǝn wa, na nda a ƙǝɗang ɗǝ tǝ thlarghǝn.
\v 14 Malaman kanda. Na nda ƙǝla mangya kwamaya na nda a ƙǝs sǝsal kwamaya. Ana kwamarha a ƙǝs sǝsal kwamarha, kanda kyab na nda a mukrha hu kwaarha hai.”
\p 
\v 15 Ndangga Mbiturus Yeeso, “Pǝrang ten karapuɗi kan ya.”
\p 
\v 16 Tsahangga Yeeso mee kanda, “Ɓal wun kula sǝnang hai wa?
\v 17 Kala ˈya ǝnana niifa mii nǝn kyarha hurghǝn ɗǝ nggǝrghǝn kyarha sǝ a fadghǝn.
\v 18 Amma ǝnɗi na a kyarha ɓa ahu mee, kyaghǝn sǝ ahur niifa. Ndǝghǝnni na tsawang nda niifa tǝ ‘paarha’ fa.
\v 19 Ƙǝsǝr ahur niifa sǝ ndǝna numad mbǝlfeerha kyarha ɓa, tǝ ɓǝl farha, tǝ kulafayirha, tǝ pateyirha, tǝ ngaara, tǝ ƙǝnang paama nggaɓaarha mu tǝ sǝb thlǝma.
\v 20 Əngginiya ndǝna tsawang niifa tǝ paarha fa a mbed Faara, amma hǝb ǝnnarhami kula tsab haara mbǝ ndǝna tsawang niifa tǝ paarha fa a mbed Faara wa.”
\s1 Fǝrƙǝkafekkid nuneefa tǝ kanˈaniyarha
\r (Markus7:24-30)
\p 
\v 21 Tǝrgha Malgha Yeeso Nggalili ɗǝgha hu chehweed Taya ɗǝ tǝ Sidon.
\v 22 Na nuneefa sǝ tǝ Kanˈana ɓagha thlǝmadghǝn ɓa hwanggǝnǝn, “A haɗoyi fa Chinǝm, Wan Ndauda, ƙǝsǝr wutarad na nǝghǝn tǝ ǝnkaheerha fa nǝn naarha sǝsang nda kaan.”
\p 
\v 23 Amma nggǝrang ngwa Yeeso sǝ wa. Tǝrgha ndangga fatsahayighǝn, “Ndang a wiigha, nǝghǝn a ɓilla ƙǝm tǝ hwanda.”
\p 
\v 24 Nggǝrgha Yeeso sǝ, “Thlǝnna nda nggi ɓa ka ɓi ɗang nda chauraya Isǝreela sǝ sahadgha kee.”
\p 
\v 25 Ɓagha nuɗa ɓa ɓǝrgha hai a mbedghǝn nggǝrghǝn hwanggǝn, “Chinǝm ɗeesǝ!”
\p 
\v 26 Nggǝrgha Yeeso sǝ, “Kamngwa tǝranggǝm ǝnnadmid wundakhnaya fǝranggǝnǝm wuɗaya wa.”
\p 
\v 27 Nggǝrangga nuɗa sǝ, “Ƙǝkafek ni Chinǝm, amma ko wuɗaya ni na nda hǝb fǝfǝsǝrra ǝnnarhami hǝrgha hai a mbǝd ɗauyad turi ndan.”
\p 
\v 28 Tǝrgha nggǝrangga Yeeso sǝ, “Sa nuneefa na fǝrƙǝkafekkid wa manggǝn kaan, ˈya na midwa wal nan.” Tsu kee ƙǝngga wutaradɗi keeghǝn.
\s1 Ƙǝnang Yeeso nafiya hangga
\p 
\v 29 Malgha Yeeso mbǝɗi ɗǝgha wuri aam Nggalili ɗǝ tǝrgha wumnda sǝ tsauka hai.
\v 30 Wumngga fiya thlǝmadghǝn ɓa hangga. Ɓa nda ɓa tǝ sǝfǝngya, tǝ kwamaya, tǝ fingya mǝrna fandan hai, tǝ fingya mbuwa mbang kaala sǝ tǝ fingya haaya hangga. Ɗǝfang ngganda kanda hai a mbed Yeeso, ƙǝnanggǝn kanda heu.
\v 31 Ƙǝsangga ǝnwulteena fiya wumngga hai na nanda fingyayini mbuwa mbang kaala sǝ kanda a kaala sǝ, fingya mǝrna fandan hai wal nda ƙǝnda, sǝfǝngya a wiirha hai tǝ ƙǝm kwamaya a na maana hai. Na nda a fal Faara yi Isǝreela.
\s1 Hǝɓang Yeeso nafiya haru kumnggit faɗa
\r (Markus8:1-10)
\p 
\v 32 Tǝrgha aagha Yeeso fatsahayighǝn ɓa ndanggǝn kanda, “Na nafini a haɗee fa ya. Ɓeena mahan kanda a thlǝmadna a mbǝɗiya, tahang ngwa ˈya kanda ha na a ǝna nda mii wa. Mbǝ minna sǝ kal kanda ni hai wii nda wureɗǝ a miirha wa, asǝmha ɗǝgha shiwid kanda teena a kwamana.”
\p 
\v 33 Nggǝrangga fatsahayighǝn sǝ, “A yanggi ɗǝnǝm wal mburodi ɓa a kahedɗi ya na a tsǝghanggǝn fiya hangga kiya?”
\p 
\v 34 Tsahangga Yeeso mee kanda, “Mburodi kurmi ni a har nun?” Ndang ngganda, “Mǝd tǝ tǝngya na miɗiɗi ngguchit.”
\p 
\v 35 Ndangga Yeeso fiya wumngga hai a tsawa nda hai a hweeɗe.
\v 36 Tǝrgha haranggǝn mburodi yina sǝ mǝd tǝ tǝnggini, usa nǝn Faara, kyanggǝn hai kutelth-kutelth. Fǝranggǝnǝn fatsahayighǝn ndǝghang nggǝnda fiya ɗǝ.
\v 37 Kanda heu kii nda nggaala nda. Wumangga fatsahayini katǝbghǝn kutasya mǝd.
\v 38 Nafiya hǝbgha ǝnnadɗami hǝshya haru kumnggit faɗa kula thlǝɗang nda nishya tǝ wundakhnaya.
\v 39 Akwasamadɗi kalna Yeeso fiya hai, kyagha ahu kombuwol hai ɗǝgha chehweed Manggadan ɗǝ.
\c 16
\s1 Kaɗa mamngya ǝnsakhrha
\r (Markus8:11-13; Luka12:54-56)
\p 
\v 1 Farɗasǝ Farisaya tǝ Sadukiyaya ɓa nda thlǝmad Yeeso ɓa ka a ƙǝƙǝrang ngganda, na mindan sǝ a kyaɗang ǝnsakhrha nǝn kanda yi wulteena a talara hai tǝna nda sǝndasǝ nǝghǝn tǝ sǝsǝmnda Faara fa.
\v 2 Nggǝranggǝn kanda sǝ, “A tsǝ figrha hai, a naɗun fǝrakh amshi tsǝɗǝ yiɓa, nun ndaarha na mbǝrha a naarha kukwar a ɓinda.
\v 3 A tsar ƙǝm a naɗun fǝrakh amshi yiɓa, nun ndaarha a weeriya na ˈyaara a ɓaarha. Kun a sǝnang ǝngya hai na a katǝrarha hai a fǝrakh amshi, amma mbun a sǝnang ǝnsakhkya ƙǝshiid weeri hai ya wa.
\v 4 Ƙǝl fa mbǝlfeeya, tǝ kulafaya ƙǝshiid weeriya kandani na kaɗa ǝnsakhkya, amma ǝnsakhrha niya kyaɗang kanda ndǝna yi annabi Yunana.” Tǝrgha malgha Yeeso kanda wii fayighǝn nǝn.
\s1 Mehen Farisaya tǝ yi Sadukiyaya
\r (Markus8:14-21)
\p 
\v 5 Akwasamadɗi tǝɗang nanda wuri aam Nggalili teena ƙǝlagha fatsahayina hai takhkwa nda mburodi ha ɓa wa.
\v 6 Ƙǝsgha Yeeso thlǝmandan, “Kwarama tǝ mehen Farisaya tǝ yi Sadukiyaya.”
\p 
\v 7 Katǝrang ngganda ngaala hai tǝ ndan ƙǝsǝr ka takhkwa nanda mburodi ha ɓa.
\p 
\v 8 Sǝnangga Yeeso ǝnɗa hai na nanda a ndikrha atenggǝn, nanǝn kee ndanggǝn kanda, “Ƙǝɗi fǝrƙǝkafekkid nun! Kama nda nun a ngaala tǝ ndan ka mbuwana mburodi sǝ a har nun?
\v 9 Ɓal wun kula sǝnang hai wa? Ɗal wun teena hai tǝ mburodi tuf hǝɓang ni nafiya haru kumnggit tuf wa, tǝ ƙǝm kutasya kurmi wumang nun katǝpghǝn?
\v 10 Nduwa mburodi mǝd hǝɓang ni nafiya haru kumnggit faɗa, kutasa kurmi wumang nun katǝpghǝn?
\v 11 Mani sǝnangwa nun hai tǝ ndaarha mbǝ aten mburodi ni niya tsǝ laɓaara wa? Niya nggǝr ndaarha, ‘Kwarama tǝ mehen Farisaya tǝ yi Sadukiyaya.’ ”
\p 
\v 12 Tǝrgha a mbǝɗiya sǝnangga fatsahayina hai mbǝ a tsǝ laɓaara aten mekhna na ahu mburodi wa, amma aten tsahad Farisaya ni tǝ yi Sadukiyaya.
\s1 Fǝr Mbiturus ƙǝkafek Yeeso ndǝghǝnni Ƙǝrǝsti
\r (Markus8:27-30; Luka9:18-21)
\p 
\v 13 Ɓana Yeeso chehweed Kaisariya Filibi ɓa, tsahang mee nǝn fatsahayighǝn, “Na fiya a ndaarha wunni Wan Niifa?”
\p 
\v 14 Ndang ngganda, “Fingya a ndaarha Yahaya Tǝ Mbaptisǝma, fingya Ilya, fingya ƙǝm Irmiya nduwa tal ahur annabiya.”
\p 
\v 15 Ndangga Yeeso kanda, “Amma kun wu nuwun a ndaarha wunni nggi?”
\p 
\v 16 Ndangga Mbiturus, “Sani Ƙǝrǝsti, Wan Faara natǝ yibrha ha.”
\p 
\v 17 Ndangga Yeeso, “Tǝ parka ni sa, Siman wan Yunana, mbǝ niifa ni thlǝwogha ǝnɗiya wa, amma Pǝpa ni na a talara.
\v 18 Niya ndorha sa Mbiturus, aten ferɗiya ndǝn niya tǝn ƙǝn hwan Faarna, mbuwana sǝsǝmnda hwanga mbang chang hai.
\v 19 Niya furo ǝncha kwatmingya yi Kutǝryid Talara. Kala ˈya ƙǝnang nun hai ahu ƙǝshiirha nǝghǝn ƙǝƙǝna hai kee a talara, tǝ ƙǝm kala ˈya kwasang nun hai hu ƙǝshiirha nǝghǝn kukwasa hai ƙǝm a talara.”
\v 20 Tǝrgha ƙǝs thlǝmad fatsahayighǝn nǝn a pǝrang ndan niifa ndǝghǝnni Ƙǝrǝsti wa.
\s1 Thlǝk Yeeso kwaman mǝrrǝghǝn
\r (Markus8:31-38; 9:1; Luka9:22-27)
\p 
\v 21 Ka a farɗi katǝrangga Yeeso pǝranggǝn fatsahayighǝn a pǝpal tǝ ndaarha tǝta ni a ɗǝgha Urshalima ɗǝ ɗǝgha sǝsaarha aten ǝngya hangga ahar shingya tǝ firistaya tǝ famalǝmngya ngyakhrha. Na nda a ɓǝlang nda, amma a far ɓeena yi mahan nǝn a thliirha sǝ ahu mǝrra.
\p 
\v 22 Amma ɗǝgha Mbiturus tǝghǝn man patu ɗǝ ndanggǝn, “A kaptangga Faara ɗǝ, Chinǝm, mbǝ tam katǝrarha hai tǝ sa kee wa!”
\p 
\v 23 Kyahargha Yeeso hai ndanggǝn Mbiturus, “Nduwu hai tǝ nggi sa Sheetan, tsauna fer kii saara ka nggi. Na a ƙǝlang ǝngya kee na mid fiya, amma mbǝ yi Faara wa.”
\p 
\v 24 Tǝrgha ndangga Yeeso fa tsahayighǝn, “Ana mid niifa sǝ tsauka tǝ mbusamad na, tǝta ni malanggǝn nggǝm altenggǝn, tǝranggǝn kaɗidghǝn sǝ mbu samad na nǝn.
\v 25 Ƙǝsǝr kala niifa na midghǝn ɗǝfang yiɓǝdghǝn ɗǝ nǝn a ƙǝɗeng nda. Amma kala niifa ƙǝɗengga yiɓǝdghǝn ka nggi, ɗǝfang nǝn ɗǝ.
\v 26 Ma chighang nǝn niifa a walɗǝ ǝn ƙǝshiirha heu ƙǝɗenggǝn shingndǝghǝn? Nduwa mani kalgha shingndǝghǝn mu?
\v 27 Ƙǝsǝr wan Niifa nǝn a ɓarha ɓa ahu mamnggid Chin tǝ fathlǝnggighǝn ngwang kumarha nǝn fiya heu aten ǝngya ǝnana nda.
\v 28 Niya pǝrang ƙǝkafek kun, na fingya sǝ ƙǝƙǝt a mbǝɗiya mba nda a mǝra wa ƙǝl ma nanda Wan Niifa ɓayi ahu Kutǝryidghǝn.”
\c 17
\s1 Mamnggid Yeeso
\r (Markus9:2-13; Luka9:28-36)
\p 
\v 1 Akwasamad ɓeena mikki tǝrangga Yeeso Mbiturus tǝ Yakubu tǝ Yahaya wanman Yakubu tǝraa nda wumnda sǝ, tǝna nda narha katendan.
\v 2 A mbǝɗi nagha fiya ndǝn nggǝrɗa hai a mbed ndan. Nagha pǝmnggǝn a chimnda fa ƙǝla yanfaara, tǝ ƙǝm lukkighǝn tsawa nda pǝpet ƙǝla kukwaryirha.
\v 3 Kula sǝndǝndan sǝ kyagha nda Ilya ɓa tǝ Musa katǝrang ngganda ndikrha hai tǝ Yeeso.
\p 
\v 4 Ndangga Mbiturus Yeeso, “Chinǝm, nǝghǝn ngga nanǝm a mbǝɗiya, a nggǝmna fa, ngwa ǝna chama ni mahan-tal yiwa, tal yi Musa tǝ ƙǝm tal yi Ilya.”
\p 
\v 5 Ndǝghǝn aten ndikrha kee, ɓagha hashbe ɓa nggǝlanggǝn kanda, sǝk urarha nda hai ahur hashbiɗi tǝ ndaarha, “Waana niya, nggǝmni. Kaaman thlǝmaarha fa!”
\p 
\v 6 Sǝkna fatsahayini uradɗi kee fǝla nda hweeɗa hai ka hǝreenga.
\v 7 Tǝrgha ɓagha Yeeso ɓa tsuwar kanda nǝn fa ndanggǝn kanda, “Thleema sǝ, a tǝrǝm ɗun wa.”
\v 8 Tǝrang nanda tendan sǝ, ƙǝla nda ɗǝ ko niifa, ƙǝl Yeeso katenggǝn.
\p 
\v 9 Na nanda a tǝraa hai a wumndǝɗi, ndangga Yeeso kanda, “A pǝrang ɗun ˈya niifa nanun wa, ƙǝl a thlid Wan Niifa sǝ ahu mǝra.”
\p 
\v 10 Tǝrgha tsahangga fatsahayighǝn mee, “Mani na famalǝmngya ngyakhrha ndaarha annabi Ilya ni a ˈwa wutta ɓa ma Ƙǝrǝsti?”
\p 
\v 11 Nggǝrgha Yeeso sǝ, “Ƙǝkafek ni na Ilya a ˈwa ɓarha ɓa ka ɓagha tangsang ǝngya heu mǝmǝl.
\v 12 Amma niya ndang nda kun, ˈwad Ilya teena ɓaɗa ɓa, sǝnangwanda hai wa, amma ǝnang ˈya nda fa ƙǝla tǝrna mid ndan. Nǝghǝn kee ƙǝm ɓana Wan Niifa sǝsaarha ahar ndan.”
\p 
\v 13 Tǝrgha fatsahayini sǝnang ngganda hai nǝghǝn a ndikrha aten Yahaya Tǝbaptisǝma.
\s1 Ƙǝnang Yeeso Wundǝlaarha na tǝ ǝnkaheerha fa
\r (Markus9:14-29; Luka9:37-43a)
\p 
\v 14 A sar wumndǝɗi, fiya hangga wumngga hai a ƙǝla kanda fa. Ɓagha niifa thlǝmad Yeeso ɓa ɓǝrgha hai ndǝghǝn,
\v 15 “Chinǝm, a haɗowa waana fa. Nǝghǝn tǝ kacheela fa nǝn sǝsang nda kaan. Nǝn yakh muwang nda hu waarha hai nduwa ahu aama hai.
\v 16 Ɓang ɗi ndǝn fatsahayiwa ɓa, amma mbang ngwanda ƙǝnang wa.”
\p 
\v 17 Ndagha Yeeso, “Kun nafiya ƙǝshiid weeriya, mbuwa tǝ fǝrƙǝkafek fa mbǝlfeeya! Pakwanɗǝ ni tsaurha tǝ kun? Tǝ ƙǝm pakwanɗǝ ni ƙǝrǝssa tǝ yamid fǝrƙǝkafekkid nun? Fǝreema wanɗa ɓa.”
\v 18 Tǝrgha Yanangga Yeeso ǝnkaheedɗi na ahur wanɗi, kyagha sǝ mal wanɗa nǝn. Tsu a mbǝɗi kee ƙǝngga.
\p 
\v 19 Akwasamadghǝn tsahangga fatsahayighǝn mee ɓǝɓee, “Mani ǝnagha ndǝn kyangwa nan ǝnkahedɗa sǝ?”
\p 
\v 20 Ndangga Yeeso kanda, “Ƙǝɗi fǝrƙǝkafekkid nun. Niya pǝrang ƙǝkafek kun, ana fǝrƙǝkafek sǝ a fad nun ngguchit ƙǝla wan parsǝna, nun a ndang nda wumndǝɗi ya, ‘Ndusu a mbǝɗiya a mbǝɗa ɗǝ taarha,’ nǝn a nduwussa. Mbǝ ˈya sǝ na kal kun mu wa.”
\s1 Nggǝr Yeeso ndikrha aten mǝrrǝghǝn
\r (Markus9:30-32; Luka9:43b-45)
\p 
\v 22 Akwasamadɗi nggǝr nanda wumnda hai a Nggalili, ndangga Yeeso fatsahayighǝn, “Na nda a fǝr Wan Niifa a har fiya hai.
\v 23 Na nda a ɓǝlang nda, amma akwasamad ɓeena mahan na nda a thleng sǝ ahu mǝrra.” Lǝghǝdgha fatsahayini tǝ sǝbrha hura.
\s1 Tii tsamnda Ƙǝn hwan Faara na a Urshalima
\p 
\v 24 Ɓana Yeeso tǝ fatsahayighǝn a Kafarnahum ɓa, fathlǝ tsamngya Ƙǝn Faara na a Urshalima ɓa nda thlǝmad Mbiturus ɓa ndang ngganda, “Mbǝ tǝmalǝm ndǝnun tii tsamnda Ƙǝn hwan Faara na a Urshalima wa?”
\p 
\v 25 Nggǝranggǝn kanda sǝ, “Haˈi, nǝn tiirha.” Kyana Mbiturus hur minda hai tsauna Yeeso sǝ, katǝrangga Yeeso kalang sǝ, “Siman, mana ndaarha aten tsakh miiɗi ya? A har wun na kutǝrya ƙǝshidɗiya thlǝ tsamnda, ahar wanggindan nduwa ahar nafiya pak wa?”
\p 
\v 26 Ndagha Mbiturus, “Ahar nafiya pak.” Ndagha Yeeso, “Nanǝn kee mbǝ wanggindan tiirha wa.
\v 27 Amma mbǝ minnǝm sǝ ƙǝsangganda ƙǝm tǝ ɗimiyirha wa, ɗuwa hu wuri aama ɗǝ ɗa muk nggal aama. Tǝna ˈwana ƙǝsa, inang miighǝn hai na a wal wuɗǝɓǝl wurirha na a tsǝk tii tsamndǝɗi. Harang ɗa tii tsamnduwa tǝ yina.”
\c 18
\s1 Wunni manggǝn hu Kutǝryid Faara
\r (Markus9:33-37; Luka9:46-48)
\p 
\v 1 Ahu sayidɗiya ɓagha fatsahaya thlǝmad Yeeso ɓa tsahang mee nda, “Wunni manggǝn hu Kutǝryid Faara?”
\p 
\v 2 Aagha Yeeso wundakhne ɓa na ngguchit ishanggǝn a maɗufun ndan.
\v 3 Tǝrgha ndaagha, “Niya pǝrang ƙǝkafek kun, a malanggun ɗimiyid nun tsawun ƙǝla wanɗi na ngguchit ya wa mbun tam kyarha hu Kutǝryid Faara ɗǝ wa.
\v 4 Nanǝn kee kala niifa manangwawa altenggǝn tsauka ƙǝla wanɗi na ngguchit ya ndǝghǝn ni na manggǝn hu Kutǝryid Faara.
\v 5 Kala niifa thlǝgha wundakhne fa ƙǝla yanɗiya ahu thlǝmna nggini thlǝnǝn fa.”
\s1 Əngya na kyang niifa hu ɗimiyirha hai
\r (Markus9:42-48; Luka17:1-2)
\p 
\v 6 Amma ana niifasǝ kyangga tal ahur wanggini na nggu-ngguchit ya fǝrgha ƙǝkafek a nggi ahu ɗimiyirha hai, a nggushi waghang nda fǝn hǝrha ura mughang ngganda ahu wuri aama ɗǝ.
\v 7 Kawa ƙǝshiirha ƙǝsǝr ka ǝnggini na nda ǝnaarha kyang ngganda fiya hu ɗimiyirha hai. Ənggini na kyang nda fiya hu ɗimiyirha hai tǝtani a ɓagha ɓa, amma na sǝbrha hura a ƙǝla niifɗa fa ǝnagha kee.
\p 
\v 8 Ana harwa nduwa sarwa a kyorha hu ɗimiyirha hai, kyathlang ɗǝ muwangga ɗǝ. A nggushi kyana hu ahu yibrha ɗǝ mbuwa ngwalarha tǝ haara tal nduwa saara tal ma nana tǝ haara kyab nduwa saara kyab muwo wanda ahu waarha ɗǝ mbuwa mǝra hai.
\v 9 A kyo yidwa ahu ɗimiyirha hai, ƙǝɗang ɗǝ muwangga ɗǝ. A nggushi kyana ahu yibrha ɗǝ mbuwa ngwalarha tǝ yirha tal, ma muwo wanda ahu waarha ɗǝ mbuwa mǝra hai tǝ yidwa kyab.
\p 
\v 10 Kwarama, a sarɗun wanggini na nggu-ngguchit ya wa. Ƙǝsǝr niya ndang nda kun a talara wan thlǝngya Faar ndan na nda naarha a mbed Pǝpa na a talara.
\v 11 Ƙǝsǝr Wan niifa ɓanǝnɓa ka a hǝrghanggǝn fingya sahadgha.
\s1 Karapu aten chaurarha sahadgha
\r (Luka15:3-7)
\p 
\v 12 Ana niifa tǝ chauraya haru tal, tǝrgha tal sahadgha, ma nǝn ǝnaarha? Mbǝ mal kumnggit wutarihe kap wutarihe a mbǝd lafrha ɗǝgha ka kaɗa yanɗaɗǝ sahadgha wa?
\v 13 A walang ɗaɓa, niya pǝrang ƙǝkafek kun, nǝn tǝk mbǝnda fa kaan aten chauradɗi tal ma kumnggit wutarihe kap wutarihe ɗi sahadwa wa!
\v 14 Nǝghǝn kee ƙǝm, mbǝ nggǝmnda hur Pǝpa ni na a talara ko tal ahur wanggini na nggu-ngguchit ya sahadgha wa.
\s1 A ǝno shadwa ɗimiyirha fa
\r (Luka17:3)
\p 
\v 15 A ǝno shadwa ɗimiyirha fa, ɗuwa thlǝmadghǝn ɗǝ kyaɗang ɗimiyidghǝn, a pathlang nun kun sǝri. A koɗǝ thlǝmaarha fa, wuɗang na ɓa.
\v 16 Amma a kowa thlǝmaarha fa wa, turu niifa tal nduwa sǝri ɗun thlǝmadghǝn ɗǝ tǝna laɓaara kyarhaɓa a mii nafiya sǝri nduwa mahan tsauka shedawaya atenggǝn.
\v 17 A karɗǝ kang thlǝmaarha kanda fa, pǝranggǝn mamngya Ƙǝn Faara. A karɗǝ kang thlǝmaarha mamngya Ƙǝn Faara fa, tsawang niifɗiya tǝ takkwa ɗaharha ni nduwa tǝ thlǝ tsamnda.
\p 
\v 18 Niya pǝrang ƙǝkafek kun, kala ˈya ƙǝnang nun hai hu ƙǝshiirha nǝghǝn ƙǝƙǝna hai ƙǝm a talara. Kala ˈya kwasang nun hai hu ƙǝshiirha, nǝghǝn kukwasa hai kee a talara.
\p 
\v 19 “Niya nggǝr ndang nda kun, ana nafiya sǝ sǝri ahur nun hu ƙǝshiirha nggǝmngga fa aten ˈya nun a hwanda, Pǝpa na a talara a fǝranggǝn kun.
\v 20 Ƙǝsǝr kala mbǝrha wumna fiya sa hai sǝri nduwa mahan ahu thlǝmna niyi a pathlang ndan.”
\s1 Karapu aten mafarha kargha chakh ɗimiyirha fa
\p 
\v 21 Tǝrgha ɓagha Mbiturus thlǝmadghǝn ɓa tsahang mee nǝn, “Chinǝm, saara kurmi ni chahanggǝn shadna ɗǝ a ǝneeɗǝ ɗimiyirha fa? Saara mǝd wa?”
\p 
\v 22 Nggǝrangga Yeeso sǝ, “Awo, mbǝ katǝra mǝd kee wa, amma kumnggit mǝd katǝra mǝd!
\v 23 Tsaunǝn kee, Kutǝryid talara nǝghǝn ƙǝla kutǝra na midghǝn kirassa ƙǝnaghǝn na a har mafayighǝn nzǝmngga wuɗǝɓǝla a harghǝn.
\v 24 Katǝrang nǝn hai kee, ɓang niifa nda ɓa nǝn a takkwarha wuɗǝɓǝl wurirha haru kumnggidghǝn tuf.
\v 25 Nanǝn mbǝ mbang tiighǝn wa, tǝrgha kutǝrɗi ndǝghǝn a heng ngganda ɗǝ tǝ nukkun, tǝ wanggighǝn tǝ ǝngya nanǝn tǝghǝn ha heu a tii kumadɗa nǝn.
\v 26 Ɓǝrgha mafadɗa hai a mbedghǝn hwanggǝnǝn, ‘Niya hwan sa, ƙǝrsu tǝ nggi, niya tiighǝn heu.’
\v 27 Tǝrgha kutǝrɗi haɗanggǝn fa, kalghǝnǝn hai chahang kumadɗa nǝn ɗǝ.”
\p 
\v 28 “Amma kyana mafadɗi ƙǝshaaɗǝ, ɗǝgha wal shadghǝn mafarha nǝn a takkwarha wuɗǝɓǝl wurirha haru tal. Ƙǝsanggǝn, ˈyaɓanggǝn, ndanggǝn, ‘Tee kumad na.’
\v 29 Ɓǝrgha shadɗa hai keeghǝn hwanggǝnǝn, ‘Ƙǝrsu tǝ nggi niya teuƙǝn.’
\v 30 Amma kargha fa ƙǝsanggǝn muwanggǝn ahu porsǝna ɗǝ ƙǝl tii nǝn wuɗǝɓǝlɗi heu.
\v 31 Nana fingya mafaya ǝnɗi katǝragha hai, sǝbgha hur ndan ɗǝ. Ɗǝnda thlǝmad kutǝrɗa ɗǝ pǝrang ǝnɗa nda katǝragha hai.
\v 32 Tǝrgha kutǝrɗi aah mafadɗa nǝn ɓa chahang nǝn kumarha ɗǝ ndanggǝn, ‘Sa ka wuɗi mafarha! Chahoɗi kumarha ɗǝ na a tenwa ka hwanna nggi.
\v 33 Mbǝ shadwa mafarha haɗo fa ƙǝla haɗoni fa wa?’
\v 34 Tǝrgha kutǝrɗi hu sǝbrha hura muwanggǝn hu porsǝna ɗǝ ƙǝl a tii ɗǝ kumadɗi heu.
\v 35 Na Pǝpa na a talara a ǝnang kun kee a kowunni kargha chahang ˈya shadghǝn ɗǝ tǝ hura tal.”
\c 19
\s1 Tsahad Yeeso ha aten ɓǝlla kakhrha
\r (Markus10:1-12; Luka16:18)
\p 
\v 1 Ngwalang na Yeeso thlǝk ǝnggini ya, mal Nggalili nǝn ɗǝgha hu chehweed Yahudiya ɗǝ na a pǝm kufad Urdun.
\v 2 Fiya hangga takkwagha samadghǝn ƙǝnanggǝn kanda a mbǝɗi.
\p 
\v 3 Ɓagha fingya Farisaya thlǝmadghǝn ɓa ka a ƙǝƙǝrang ngganda. Tsahang mee nda, “Nggǝm ngyahad nǝm fa a kalgha niifa nukkun hai aten kala ˈya ǝnanǝn wa?”
\p 
\v 4 Nggǝrangga Yeeso kanda sǝ “Karatang nggun ahu ɗeleewar Faara wa? A katǝra ǝna ƙǝshiirha ‘ǝna Faara nuneefa tǝ hǝshneefa.’ Nggǝrghǝn ndaarha,\f + \fr 19:4 \ft Katǝrarha 1:27; 5:2\f*
\v 5 ‘Ndǝghǝn ni ǝnagha ndǝn na niifa malang nda man tǝ chin thlǝthlǝɓanggǝn nukkun fa, kanda kyab tsau nda tal.’\f + \fr 19:5 \ft Katǝrarha 2:24\f*
\v 6 Nanǝn kee mba nda sǝri wa, amma tal ni. Tsaunǝn kee, ˈYa wumangna Faara, a ndǝghang niifa hai wa.”
\p 
\v 7 Tsahang mee nda, “Kama nda ndaana Musa niifa mbuwana midghǝn nukkun a fǝrang ɗeleewar kaala nǝn hai, ndanggǝn wiu?”\f + \fr 19:7 \ft Nggurub Ngwa Kumaarha24:1-4; Matta 5:31\f*
\p 
\v 8 Nggǝrangga Yeeso kanda sǝ, “Ndaana Musa kee ƙǝsǝr ka kakrakkid ten nun. Amma a katǝradghǝn mbǝ kee wa.
\v 9 Niya ndang nda kun kala niifa kalgha nukkun hai, a mbǝ nana nuɗi a ǝna kulafayirha wa, nggǝrghǝn kakh nuneefa pak ǝnaɗǝ kulafayirha.”\f + \fr 19:9 \ft Matta 5:32; 1 Korontiyaya 7:10-11\f*
\p 
\v 10 Ndangga fatsahayighǝn, “Ana ˈyasǝ kee a pathlang nda nuneefa tǝ chimadghǝn nggushi tsauna niifa kula kakhrha.”
\p 
\v 11 Amma ndagha Yeeso, “Mbǝ fiya heu na nggǝm palthɗa fa ya wa, ƙǝl fingya nggǝmang na Faara kanda fa.
\v 12 Na fingya sǝ nggǝt nanda kulabrha, fingya sǝ ƙǝm firang nanda kanda, fingya sǝ mbǝ mid ndan sǝ kakhrha wa ƙǝsǝr ka Kutǝryid talara. Yi na a mbang thlǝ laɓarɗi ya thlǝghǝnǝn.”
\s1 Ɗǝfang Yeeso parka wundakhnaya teena
\r (Markus10:13-16; Luka18:15-17)
\p 
\v 13 Tǝrgha ɓang wundakhnaya nda Yeeso ɓa na nggu-ngguchit ka a ɗǝfang parka nǝn kanda teena tǝ ƙǝm hwangga aten ndan. Amma fatsahayighǝn na nda yanang nda nafini na a ɓaarha ɓa tǝ wanggini.
\v 14 Amma ndangga Yeeso kanda, “Malaman wundakhnaya ɓa nda thlǝmad na ɓa. A karang ɗun kanda fa wa. Ƙǝsǝr Kutǝryid talara yi fingya ni na ƙǝla wanggini ya.”
\p 
\v 15 Ɗǝfang haara nǝn kanda teena fǝrang parka nǝn kanda a wiigha.
\s1 Tǝ ƙǝna
\r (Markus10:17-31; Luka18:18-30)
\p 
\v 16 Ɓagha Niifa thlǝmad Yeeso ɓa tsahang mee nǝn, “Mala, mani ǝnaarha na ngga tǝni wal yibrha mbuwa ngwalarha?”
\p 
\v 17 Ndangga Yeeso, “Mani na tsahe mee aten ˈya na ngga? Niifa tǝtal ni kee na ngga. Ana mid wa yibrha mbuwa ngwalaarha, ǝno taara tǝ ngyakhkini.”
\p 
\v 18 Ndangga niifɗi Yeeso, “Yanggi?” Nggǝrangga Yeeso sǝ, “A ɓǝlna farha wa. A ǝnanna kulafayirha wa. A ngaarna wa. A pǝrna nggaɓaarha aten niifa wa.\f + \fr 19:18 \ft Kyarhaɓa 20:13-16; Nggurub Ngwa Kumaarha 5:17-20\f*
\v 19 Fǝrang mamnggirha nda muwa tǝ tsu. Nggǝmu tuladwa ƙǝla alten wa.”\f + \fr 19:19 \ft Kyarhaɓa 20:12; Nggurub Ngwa Kumaarha 5:16; Ɗeleewar Firistaya 19:18\f*
\p 
\v 20 Ndagha wundǝladɗi, “Lafɗi ngyakhkini ya heu. Ma takhka tsauka tǝta a ǝnee?”
\p 
\v 21 Ndangga Yeeso, “Ana mid wa sǝ tsawana lǝlǝgɗa, ɗuwa ɗǝ ɗa heng ǝnggiwa ɗǝ heu fǝrang wuɗǝɓǝlghǝna fa yamiiya, na wal mbǝd ɗǝfǝdghǝn a talara. Tǝrgha ɓa na ɓa mbu samadna na.”
\p 
\v 22 Amma hǝrǝmna wundǝladɗi sǝkrha kee, wii fayighǝn nǝn hurghǝn sǝsǝɓa ɗǝ, ƙǝsǝr tǝƙǝna ni kaan.
\p 
\v 23 Tǝrgha ndangga Yeeso fatsahayighǝn, “Niya pǝrang ƙǝkafek kun, nǝghǝn pǝɗaghǝn kyagha tǝƙǝna hu Kutǝryid Talara ɗǝ.
\v 24 Niya nggǝr ndang nda kun, nǝghǝn pǝpa kyagha thlǝkhmu ɗǝ tǝ kwat libra ma tǝƙǝna kyagha hu Kutǝryid Faara ɗǝ.”
\p 
\v 25 Sǝkna fatsahayighǝn kee, wulangga teena kanda tsakh mee nda, “A tsauɗǝ kee wunni wal hǝrǝkrha?”
\v 26 Amma ƙǝlangga Yeeso kanda ɗǝ ndǝghǝn, “A fad niifa tǝ wasa in mbǝ ǝnaarha hai wa, amma a fad Faara nǝghǝn pǝpa.”
\v 27 Tǝrgha ndangga Mbiturus, “Malang ɗan ǝngya heu mbuɗan samadwa nan, ma nan waala?”
\v 28 Ndangga Yeeso kanda, “Niya pǝrang ƙǝkafek kun, ahu ƙǝshiirha na ɓayi, a sayidɗi na Wan Niifa a tsaurha hu mamnggit tsǝnggam Kutǝryidghǝn, kun mbuwa samadna nun a tsaurha hu tsǝnggamngya kumkap sǝri, non a ngwang kumarha turya kumkap sǝri yi Isǝreela.\f + \fr 19:28 \ft Matta 25:31; Luka 22:33\f*
\v 29 Kala niifa malgha wure nduwa wanmanggighǝn hǝshya nduwa wanmanggighǝn nishya nduwa chin nduwa man nduwa wanggighǝn nduwa ǝnggighǝn, ka nggi, nǝn a wal ƙǝnaghǝn katǝra haru kum tǝ ƙǝm nǝn a wal yibrha mbuwa ngwalaarha.
\v 30 Amma fingya ˈwagha kanda ni a nggǝl mee, fingya nggǝlgha mee kanda ni a tsaurha a mbee.” \f + \fr 19:30 \ft Matta 20:16; Luka 13:30\f*
\c 20
\s1 Karapu aten fatarya a hed inabi
\p 
\v 1 “Ƙǝsǝr Kutǝryid talara nǝghǝn ƙǝla tǝheerha wargha ka kaɗa fatarya ɗǝ ka ɓa nda ǝnang taara ahu hed inabidghǝn.
\v 2 Ƙǝnang nanda wuɗǝɓǝl paara hai puwanggǝn kanda ahu hedghǝn ɗǝ.
\v 3 Tǝrna yanfaara sǝ, kyagha sǝ ɗǝgha wal fiya ahu kasu mbǝ ˈyasǝ na nanda a ǝnaarha wa.
\v 4 Ndanggǝn kanda ɗaa nda huɗaarha ahu hedghǝn nǝn a teng kanda ˈya kamngga ahu paara.
\v 5 Nanǝn kee ɗǝnda ɗǝ ɗaa nda huɗang sǝ. Yanfara a sǝrǝkrha tǝ ƙǝm yarna yanfaara hai ǝnagha kee.
\v 6 A figrha ɗǝgha wal fingya ƙǝƙǝt. Tsahang mee nǝn kanda, ‘Kama nanun ƙǝƙǝt a mbǝɗiya mbǝ ˈyasǝ nun a ǝnaarha wa?’”
\v 7 Nggǝrang ngganda sǝ, “Mbǝ niifa sǝ aagha kan wa.” Ndangga tǝhedɗi kanda, “Tsaunǝn kee ɗamaɗǝ ɗun wal fingya na a huɗaarha hu hed na.”
\p 
\v 8 Mukna yanfaara hai, ndangga tǝhedɗi niifɗi na aten hedghǝn, “Ooh fatar yina ɓa teng wuɗǝɓǝl paara na kanda, katǝrang hai tǝ fingya ɗǝgha ɗǝ a kwasamarha ta ten fingya ɗǝ ˈwagha ɗǝ.” \f + \fr 20:8 \ft Ɗeleewar Firistaya 19:13; Nggurub Ngwa Kumaarha 24:15\f*
\v 9 Fingya ɗǝgha ɗǝ a figrha teng ngganda kanda, kowunni walɗǝ wuɗǝɓǝl paara.
\v 10 Fingya ˈwagha ɗǝ ɓa nanda ka thlǝ yindan ɓa, tamngganda ndaarha na yindan a kal yi fingya. Amma teng wuɗǝɓǝl paara nda kanda ƙǝm.
\v 11 Thlǝna ndan katǝrang ngganda huhurumnda hai aten tǝhedɗi.
\v 12 “‘Nafini ya ɓagha nda ɓa a samarha amma tengga kanda mǝmǝl tǝ kan ǝnagha taara ka a tsar ahu weng-weng nda yanfaara.’”
\p 
\v 13 “Amma nggǝranggǝn tal sǝ ahur ndan, ‘Pashidna, hukki sa wa! Mbǝ ƙǝnanggǝm hai niya teurha wuɗǝɓǝl paara na nda tiirha wa?
\v 14 Thlu wuɗǝɓǝl wa wiina. Hurna nggǝmngga niya teng nda nafini ɓagha ɓa a samarha mǝmǝl ƙǝla teu ni.
\v 15 Kamngwa a ǝna ˈya ni tǝrna minna tǝ wuɗǝɓǝl na wa? Na sǝrǝkrha ka ɗang ni fingya sǝ wa?’”
\p 
\v 16 “Nanǝn kee yi nggǝlgha mee ndǝna a ˈwaarha, yi ˈwaagha ndǝna a nggǝl mee.”\f + \fr 20:16 \ft Matta 19:30; Markus 10:31; Luka 13:30\f*
\s1 Nggǝr Yeeso thlǝk kwaman mǝrrǝghǝn
\r (Markus10:32-34; Luka18:31-34)
\p 
\v 17 Na Yeeso a ɗǝrha Urshalima ɗǝ, kyalthgha Yeeso man patu ɗǝ tǝ fatsahayighǝn kumkap sǝri ndanggǝn kanda,
\v 18 “Nǝm a ɗǝrha ta Urshalima ɗǝ, Na nda a fǝr Wan Niifa a har mamngya firistaya hai tǝ famalǝmngya ngyakhrha. Na nda a ngwang kumad mǝrra sǝ.
\v 19 Tǝrgha na nda fǝrghǝn a har Romaya hai, waghǝn nda, tsaɗaghǝn nda tǝ ƙǝm tawang ngganda ɗǝ. Amma a far paara yi mahan nǝn a thliirha sǝ ahu mǝra.”
\s1 Hwanda man Yakubu tǝ Yahaya
\r (Markus10:35-45)
\p 
\v 20 Tǝrgha man wangya Dzabadi. Nda Yakubu tǝ Yahaya, ɓagha thlǝmad Yeeso ɓa tǝ wanggighǝn. Ɓǝrgha hai tǝ waɗedghǝn ka a hwanang ˈya nǝn na midghǝn.
\p 
\v 21 Tsahangga Yeeso mee, “Mana midwa?” Nggǝranggǝn Yeeso sǝ, “Tsawang wanggini kyana na sǝri ya tal a yisǝmad wa, tal ƙǝm a yi kawad wa ahu Kutǝryid wa.”
\p 
\v 22 Amma nggǝrangga Yeeso kanda sǝ, “Sǝnggun ˈya nun a tsakhrha wa! Nun mbang saarha tǝ wuhuleuɗi ɗini saarha wa?” Nggǝrang ngganda sǝ, “Haˈi nan mbang nda.”
\p 
\v 23 Ndangga Yeeso kanda, “Nun mbang saarha tǝ wuhuleuɗi, amma tsaurha a yisǝmanna nduwa yi kawad na mbǝ nggini fǝrghǝn wa. Taksaagha Pǝpa mbǝyini ya a nafini wurnǝn.”
\p 
\v 24 Sǝkna fingya fatsahaya kum ǝnɗi hwanna nda Yakubu tǝ Yahaya sǝbgha hur ndan ɗǝ tǝ kanda.
\v 25 Amma aagha Yeeso kanda thlǝmadghǝn ɓa ndanggǝn kanda, “Sǝnɗunsǝ kutǝrya na hu ƙǝshidɗiya mbuwa Yahudaya na nda kyad sǝsǝmnggit ndan aten nafi ndan, mamnggi ndan ƙǝm na nda kyad sǝsǝmnda aten nafiya na a kamu ndan.
\v 26 Amma ahur nun nǝn a naarha pak. Kala niifa na midghǝn tsauka ndǝghǝnni mamnda tǝtani tsauka niifa ni na a ǝnang taara kun.\f + \fr 20:26 \ft Luka 22:25-26\f*
\v 27 Kala niifa na midghǝn a nagha a mbee, tǝtani a tsauka mafad nun.\f + \fr 20:27 \ft Matta 23:11; Markus 9:35; Luka 22:26\f*
\v 28 Ƙǝsǝr ɓad Wan Niifa ɓa mbǝ ka a ǝnang taara nda wa, amma a ǝnang taara nǝn fingya tǝ ƙǝm fǝr yiɓǝdghǝnǝn ka a hǝrghanggǝn fiya hangga.”
\s1 Ƙǝnang Yeeso kwamaya sǝri
\r (Markus10:46-52; Luka18:35-43)
\p 
\v 29 Hǝrǝmna Yeeso tǝ fatsahayighǝn mal Djeriko, mbuwa fiya samadghǝn hangga.
\v 30 Tǝrgha kwamaya sǝri tsau ami kwamana. Sǝnna nda sǝ na Yeeso a mbǝra ɗǝ tǝ kwamanɗi, katǝrang ngganda tǝrang urad ndan sǝ, “Chinǝm, Wan Ndauda, a haɗowan fa!”
\p 
\v 31 Yanangga fiya kanda a nggasa nda hai, amma ɗǝnda mbeeɗǝ tǝ tǝrang urad ndan sǝ kaan, “Chinǝm, Wan Ndauda, a haɗowan fa!”
\p 
\v 32 Sǝkna Yeeso kanda, ishgha hai aah kanda nǝn, “Mana minnun a ǝnanggi kun?”
\p 
\v 33 Nggǝrang ngganda sǝ, “Chinǝm, na minnan sǝ a na mana nan hai!”
\p 
\v 34 Haɗangga nafini Yeeso fa tsuwar yindan nǝn fa, tsu a mbǝɗi kee na mana nda hai. Tǝrgha mbu samadghǝn nda.
\c 21
\s1 Kyad Yeeso Urshalima hai ƙǝla kutǝra
\r (Markus11:1-11; Luka19:28-40; Yahaya12:12-19)
\p 
\v 1 Na Yeeso tǝ fatsahayighǝn a takh ndusang Urshalima fa, ɓa nda hu tala ɓa na nda aarha Mbetafaji ahu Wumngya ɗǝfya Dzaitun. Thlǝngga Yeeso fatsahayighǝn sǝri a ˈwa nda mbeeɗǝ.
\v 2 Ndanggǝn kanda, “Ɗama hu talɗa ɗǝ na a mbǝɗi taarha, a kyaɗun sa hai, nun awal kwaara ƙǝƙǝna hai tǝ wanggǝn a thlǝmadghǝn. Kwasaman kanda hai mbee kanda nun ɓa.
\v 3 A tsahang niifa mee kun, ndaman kee, ‘Na mid Chinǝm sǝ kanda,’ tsu a mbǝɗi kee nǝn a malang kun ɗun ɗǝ tǝ kanda.”
\p 
\v 4 Katǝrana ǝnɗa haya ka lǝɗang ngganda ˈya ndaana annabi:
\b
\q1 
\v 5 “Ndang nafiya Urshalima,
\q2 ‘Kulo, Kutǝr nun ɓayi thlǝmannun ɓa.
\q1 Niifa ni mbuwana tenggǝn kakrak
\q2 ɓayi a ƙǝsǝr kwaara,
\q2 Nǝghǝn ɓayi a ƙǝsǝr wan kwaara.’”\x * \xo 21:5 \xt Dzakariya9:9\x*
\b
\p 
\v 6 Ɗǝgha fatsahayina ɗǝ ǝna nda kǝla ndangna Yeeso kanda.
\v 7 Ɓang kwarɗa nda ɓa tǝ wan kwarɗi, lǝlǝɓang ngganda lukki ndan a ƙǝsǝr wan kwarɗa sǝ tsauka atenggǝn.
\v 8 Lǝlǝɓangga fiya lukki ndan hai aten kwamana a mbedghǝn, fingya kǝm kyalth shiiya nda ɓa lǝlǝɓang ngganda a tǝn kwamana.
\v 9 Nafiya ˈwagha mbeeɗǝ ma ndǝghǝn tǝ fingya na mbusamadghǝn tǝrang ngganda urayi ndan sǝ, kanda ndaarha:
\b
\q1 “Faala a tsauka aten Wan Ndauda!
\q2 Parka tsauɗǝ aten,
\q1 niifɗi na ɓayi ahu thlǝm Chinǝm!
\q2 Falama Faara na manggǝn a talara!”\f + \fr 21:9 \ft Dzabura 118:25-26\f*
\b
\m 
\v 10 Kyana Yeeso a Urshalima hai, wupǝri ɗi kahad wulangga teena kanda, na nda tsakh miiya tǝ ndaarha “Wunni ya?”
\p 
\v 11 Nggǝmangga nafini, “Yeeso ni, annabi ɗi ɓagha ɓa a Nadzarat na a Nggalili.”
\s1 Rǝghang Yeeso fa shafiliya ɗǝ a Wuri Faara
\r (Markus11:15-19; Luka19:45-48; Yahaya2:13-22)
\p 
\v 12 Kyagha Yeeso Kǝn Faara ɗǝ na Urshalima katǝranggǝn rǝghang nda nafiya ɗǝ na a hiirha tǝ hǝng nda maɓiya ɗǝ ka sataka. Changgǝlanggǝn tebǝrya fa mbeɗed wuɗǝɓǝlya ɗǝ tǝ kulohod fingya na a heng kataprakkya ɗǝ.
\v 13 Ndanggǝn kanda, “Ndagha ɗeleewar Faara,
\q1 ‘Kǝnna nǝm aaghǝn Kǝn hwanda Faara,’\f + \fr 21:13 \ft Ishaya 56:7\f*
\q2 Amma tsawanggun mbǝd ɓǝɓed ngaarya!”\f + \fr 21:13 \ft Irmiya 7:11\f*
\b
\p 
\v 14 Ɓagha kwamaya ɓa tǝ sǝfǝngya a thlǝmadghǝn ɓa ahu Kǝn Faara, ƙǝnanggǝn kanda.
\v 15 Amma nana mamngya firistaya tǝ famalǝmngya ngyakhrha Musa ǝnwultenggini ǝnanǝn, wundakhnaya ma kanda a huhwarha a pǝpal Ƙǝn Faara kanda ndaarha, “Faala tsauɗǝ aten Wan Ndauda.” Amma mamnggini sǝbgha hur ndan ɗǝ.
\v 16 Tsahang mee nda Yeeso, “Sǝkna ǝnɗi na wanggini ndaarha ya wa?” Nggǝmangga Yeeso, “Hǝng, ˈWawa nun karatang nda ɗeleewar Faara wa? Ƙǝsǝr ndagha nda,
\b
\q1 ‘Tsahang ɗun wundakhnaya ha tǝ wufar waya,\f + \fr 21:16 \ft Dzabura 8:2\f*
\q2 ka a fal kun nda.’ ”\f + \fr 21:16 \ft Dzabura 8:2\f*
\b
\p 
\v 17 A mbǝɗi kee mal kanda nǝn wudgha Mbetani ɗǝ mǝngga hai a mbǝɗi.
\s1 Shiwang Yeeso Ɗǝf Shiɓaarha
\r (Markus11:12-14,20-24)
\p 
\v 18 Ɗalthna mbǝrha hai nanǝn a wutta Urshelima ɗǝ, ƙǝsgha miirha ndǝn.
\v 19 Na shiɓarha nǝn a ƙǝlar kwamana, ɗǝgha thlǝmadghen ɗǝ kǝlagha hai ko wee a uradghǝn kǝl shiiya kee. Tǝrgha ndanggǝn shiɓadɗi, “Ma nggǝrna tam nggǝtta ɓalwa!” Tsu kee hwargha ɗǝfǝdɗa ɗǝ.
\p 
\v 20 Nana fatsahayighǝn ǝnɗi katǝragha hai, ƙǝsgha ǝnwulteena kanda kaan, ndanda, “Ƙǝƙǝn hwarna shiɓadɗa ɗǝ ƙǝkar kee ya?”
\p 
\v 21 Tǝrgha ndangga Yeeso kanda, “Niya pǝrang kǝkafek kun, anaɗun tǝ fǝrƙǝkafek fa ngaalanggun alten nun wa, nun a ǝna ǝngya kǝla yanɗiya, nduwa kalgha yanɗamu ya. Nun mbang ndang nda wumndǝɗi ya, ‘Thliusǝ muwana hu wuri aamɗa ɗǝ ya,’ nǝn a katǝrarha hai kee.\f + \fr 21:21 \ft Matta 17:20; 1 Korontiyaya 13:2\f*
\v 22 Nun hwanang Faara kala ˈya na minnun, a fǝrɗun kǝkafek, nun walghǝn.”
\s1 Tsakhmee aten sǝsǝmnda Yeeso
\r (Markus11:27-33; Luka20:1-8)
\p 
\v 23 Wudna Yeeso ahu Ƙǝn Faara ɗǝ na a Urshelima katǝranggǝn tsaharhaha, Mamnda Firistayini tǝ shingya nafini ɓanda thlǝmadghǝn ɓa. Tsahang mee nda, “Tǝ sǝsǝmnda wun na ǝna ǝnggini hǝu ya? Wun fǝrowa sǝsǝmndǝɗi ya?”
\p 
\v 24 Nggǝmangga Yeeso kanda, “Niya tsahang mee kun ha tal. A nggǝreeɗun sǝ, niya pǝranggǝn kun tǝ wun fǝreegha Sǝsǝmnda niya ǝna ǝngginiya.
\v 25 Wun fǝrangga kwamana Yahaya ǝna mbaptisǝma nǝn? Faara fǝrangga wa, nduwa fiya wa?” Tǝrgha thliigha ngaala sǝ a pathlang ndan, ndaa nda, “A ndaa ɗǝm, ‘Faara fǝrangga,’ nǝn a tsakh mee, ‘Kama fǝrwa nun ƙǝkafek tǝghǝn?’”
\p 
\v 26 “Amma a ndaɗǝm, ‘Fiya fǝrangga,’ nǝm a tǝrǝm fiya, ƙǝsǝr fǝr nda ƙǝkafek Yahaya annabi ni.”
\v 27 A kwasamadghǝn nggǝrang ngganda sǝ, “Sǝngwan wa.” Tǝrgha ndanggǝn kanda, “Nggi ƙǝm mbi pǝranggǝn kun wun fǝreegha sǝsǝmnda niya ǝna ǝnggini ya wa.”
\s1 Karapu aten wundǝlaya sǝri
\p 
\v 28 “Amma ma numa nun? Na niifa sǝ tǝ wundǝlayighǝn sǝri, ɗǝgha thlǝmad tǝ pamǝnda ɗǝ ndanggǝn, ‘Waana, a weeriya ɗǝwa ɗǝ ɗa ǝna taara ahu hed inabi.’
\v 29 Tǝrgha ndagha wundǝladɗi, ‘Mbi ɗǝrha ɗǝ wa,’ amma numagha ɗǝgha ɗǝ.
\v 30 Tǝrgha chin ɗǝgha thlǝmad tahad wundǝlad ɗaɗǝ ndanggǝn, ‘sa ɗǝwa ɗǝ,’ ndagha wundǝladɗi, ‘hǝng pǝpa, niya ɗǝrha ɗǝ.’ Amma ɗǝwa ɗǝ wa.”
\v 31 “A hur ndan na sǝri ya yanggi ǝnagha ˈya na mid chin?” Nggǝra nda sǝ, “Yanɗi ˈwanǝn thlǝnda.” Ndangga Yeeso kanda, “Niya pǝrang kǝkafek kun, fathlǝ tsamngya tǝ susuwaya nanda ˈwarha hu kutǝryid Faara ɗǝ ma kun.”
\p 
\v 32 Ƙǝsǝr Yahaya tǝ Mbaptisǝma ɓaɗa ɓa kyaɗang ɗǝ kwamana kun na a tsawun ngga a mbed Faara, amma fǝr wun kǝkafek wa, amma fathlǝ tsamngya tǝ susuwaya fǝr nda kǝkafek tǝghǝn. Ko nanun ǝnggini a katǝrarha hai, karɗun fa fǝrƙǝkafek nun tǝghǝn. 21:32 Luka 3:12; 7:29-30.
\s1 Karapu aten fahuɗaya nzǝmngga hed inabi
\r (Markus12:1-12; Luka20:9-19)
\p 
\v 33 Nanǝnya kaaman thlǝmaarha asǝɗarha fa pak. Na niifa sǝ pagha wan ɗǝfya inabi, kanggǝn tǝ kalthmaana, ra mbǝd ˈyaɗa wan inabi nǝn ahurghǝn, nggǝrghǝn ra sǝfa na nzang na tǝƙǝla hedɗa ha a tsaurha a tenggǝn. Tǝrgha nzǝmang hed inabi ɗa nǝn fahuɗaya ha wii tala nǝn.
\m 
\v 34 Tsǝna shifirha hai, thlǝn mafayighǝn nǝn ɗa nda thlang yighǝn ǝnnarhami ɓa.
\v 35 Amma fa nzǝm heeyini kǝsang ngganda mafayini; ɗǝk tal nda, ɓǝlang ngganda tal, muk tahadghǝn nda tǝ ferya.
\v 36 Tǝrgha nggǝrghǝn thlǝn fingya mafaya thlǝmad ndan ɗǝ, kalgha yanggini ˈwa nǝn thlǝn nda ɗǝ. Fa nzǝm hedɗi nggǝrgha nda ǝnang kanda kǝla yi ƙǝtǝm.
\v 37 Akwasamadghǝn tǝ hedɗi thlǝn wan hurghǝn nǝn a thlǝman ndan ɗǝ nǝghǝn a numad ndaarha, “‘Mbǝ ngaala sǝ wa na nda fǝrang mamnggirha waana.’”
\v 38 “Amma nana fa nzǝm heeyini wanɗi keeghǝn ɓayi, ndang ngganda ndan, ‘Yo, kulo tǝ har langaad hedɗi ɓayi ya. Taama ɓǝlanggǝm tǝnǝm har langaad hedɗi.’”
\v 39 Tǝrgha ƙǝsang ngganda, kahang ngganda ƙǝsǝr kadɗa ɗǝ, ɓǝlang ngganda.
\p 
\v 40 “A ɓad tǝ hedɗa ɓa, ma nǝn ǝnang nda fa nzǝm hedɗi?”
\v 41 Mamngya fatakkwayini ndaa nda, “Nǝn a ɓǝlang fa mbǝlfeyini tǝ sǝsaarha na pǝɗaaghǝn, fǝrang hedɗa nǝn nafiya pak, na narha fǝrang yighǝn ǝnnarhami kala shifirha.”
\p 
\v 42 Tǝrgha tsahangga Yeeso mee kanda, “ˈWawanun karatang nda ahu ɗeleewar Faara wa? Ndanǝn:
\b
\q1 ‘Ferɗi karna fa tǝngya,
\q2 ndǝn tsaukwa ka feera.
\q1 Yanɗiya ˈya ni ǝnana Chinǝm,
\q2 ǝnwulteena ni a yid nǝm.’ ”\f + \fr 21:42 \ft Dzabura 118:22-23\f*
\b
\p 
\v 43 “Tsaunǝn kee, niya ndang nda kun, na nda a thlang nda kutǝryid Faara a harnun, fǝrang nggǝnda chehweeya na fǝr wan ɗǝfya ngga.”
\v 44 Kala niifa mukka ten ferɗa hai, nǝn hwasarha fa ɓatal, ɓatal, amma yi mukna ferɗi tenggǝn hai nǝn a tsarang ɗǝ.
\p 
\v 45 Sǝkna mamngya firistayini tǝ Farisayini karapu ɗi, walang ngganda nǝn a thlǝk asǝɗadɗi aten ndan kanda ni fahuɗayini na tǝ mbǝlfedɗa fa.
\v 46 Na mid ndan sǝ a kǝsang ngganda, amma kanda tǝrǝm fiya wumngga hai, ƙǝsǝr na fiya a ndaarha annabi ni.
\c 22
\s1 Karapu aten wutsǝfayid kakhrha
\r (Luka14:15-24)
\p 
\v 1 Nggǝrgha Yeeso pǝrang laɓara kanda tǝ karapu, ndǝghǝn,
\v 2 Kutǝryid talara nǝghǝn ƙǝla kutǝra ngwagha fa ka ǝna wutsǝfayid kakhrha nǝn a wanggǝn.
\v 3 Thlǝnanggǝn mafayighǝn ɗǝ ɗa nda aah nafina ɓa mbu nanda kanda ɓa, amma kar nafini ɓarha fa ɓa.
\v 4 Tǝrgha nggǝrghǝn thlǝn fingya mafaya ɗǝ tǝ ndaarha, “Ndaaman nafini mbu ni, ngwaɗi wutsǝfayidɗa fa, thleeɗi urad thlaaya na ndǝndaura tǝ kwelya, ngwaɗi fa, ɓamaɓa ƙǝkar.”
\v 5 Amma nafini mbu nǝn ɗǝf wanda teena sǝ wa, tal ɗǝgha heeɗǝ, tahadghǝn ƙǝm ɗǝgha ka ǝna shafilidghǝn ɗǝ.
\v 6 Fingya ƙǝsang ngganda mafayighǝn hai, ɗǝk kanda nda tǝ kǝm ɓǝllang ngganda kanda.
\v 7 Hufgha kutǝrɗi hur kaan. Thlǝnanggǝn sodjayighǝn ɗǝ ɓǝllang ngganda fa ɓǝl fayina ɗǝ, tǝ kǝm njang ngganda wupǝri ndan ɗǝ.
\v 8 Tǝrgha ndanggǝn mafayighǝn, ʻNgwala ngwa wutsǝfayid kahadɗa fa, amma nafini mbu nǝm ɓa mbǝ kanda ni kamngga a ɓa nda ɓa wa.
\v 9 “Nanǝnya, ɗaama hu kwaman hu wuraya ɗǝ mbu fiya nun ɓa kala niifa nanun ɓa nda hu wutsǝfayidɗa ɓa.”
\v 10 Nanǝn kee, ɗǝgha mafayini ahu kwaman hu wuraya ɗǝ mbu ka nafiya nda ɓa na nanda tǝ ndǝrwaya, lǝghǝdgha ƙǝn wutsǝfayid kahadɗi tǝ rongya.
\p 
\v 11 Amma kyana kutǝr ɗa ɓa ka ɓagha na ronggi ni mbunǝn ɓa, na niifa nǝn kalwawa kari yi wutsǝfayid kahadɗi.
\v 12 Tsahang mee nǝn, “Pashinna, ƙǝƙǝn kyana mbǝɗa ɓa ya kula sa kal karid wutsǝfayid kahadɗa fa?” Amma mbangwa kamshiɗi nggǝrang sǝ wa.
\v 13 Tǝrgha kutǝrɗi ndanggǝn nafiya na ǝnang taara, “Ƙǝnaman haarghǝn tǝ sarghǝn muwanggun ƙǝshaaɗǝ ahu wula ɗǝ mbǝɗi nanda a tǝrha tǝ ƙǝt mee.”\f + \fr 22:13 \ft Matta 8:12; 25:30; Luka 13:28\f*
\p 
\v 14 “Ƙǝsǝr nafiya hangga aah nanda, amma ngguchit wurna nda hasǝ.”
\s1 Tsakhmee aten tii tsamnda a Kaisar
\r (Markus12:13-17; Luka20:20-26)
\p 
\v 15 Tǝrgha Farisayini wuma nda hai kaɗa kwamana nda a ɗǝfang takthleera nda Yeeso ka a thlǝk ˈya nǝn tǝna nda ƙǝsang nda.
\v 16 Thlǝn fatsaha yindan nda ɗǝ tǝ nafiya Hirdus ka a tsahang mee nda, ndaa nda, “Mala sǝnɗansǝ ka niifa ni sa, na tsahang kwaman Faara fiya ha tǝ ƙǝkafekkirha. Sa kǝm mba wurahasǝ wa.
\v 17 Nanǝnya pǝranggǝn kan, mani numad wa aten ǝnɗiya, nǝghǝn mǝmǝl a teng tsamnda nan kaisar wa nduwa awo?”
\p 
\v 18 Amma Yeeso sǝnɗǝ numad mɓǝlfedɗi na ahur ndan, ndagha, “Kun fathlǝrɓuya, kama na mid nun a ɗǝfee takthleera?
\v 19 Keɗeema pene tii tsamndǝɗi. Fǝrang pene ɗa nda.”
\p 
\v 20 Tsahang mee nǝn kanda, “Shishingnda wunni tǝ thlǝm wun a tenggǝn?”
\p 
\v 21 Ndang ngganda, “Yi Kaisar.” Ndanggǝn kanda, “Fǝraman Kaisar ˈya tsauka yi Kaisar, tǝ kǝm fǝraman Faara ˈya tsauka yi Faara.”
\p 
\v 22 Sǝk nanda kee, ǝna ǝnwulteena nda pa wii fayindan nda.
\s1 Tsakhmee aten thliirha sǝ ahu mǝrra tǝ kakhrha
\r (Markus12:18-27; Luka20:27-40)
\p 
\v 23 Tsu a farɗi fingya Sadukiyaya ndagha mbǝ thliirha sǝ hu mǝra wa ɓa nda thlǝmad Yeeso ɓa tǝ tsakhmee.\f + \fr 22:23 \ft Tar Fathlǝngya 23:8\f*
\v 24 Ndang ngganda, “Mala, ndangga Musa kan, ‘A mǝr wan man niifa malɗǝ nukkun hai kula nggǝtta, na wan man tǝrangsǝ hu langaarha ka a nggǝɗanggǝn sǝ.’\f + \fr 22:24 \ft Nggurub Ngwa Kumaarha 25:5\f*
\v 25 Nanǝnya, na nafiya sǝ mǝd a wanmanggi. Tǝ pamǝnda kakhka mǝrgha kula wal wee, tǝrgha yi sǝri tǝranggǝn nuɗasǝ.
\v 26 Amma wan man yi sǝri mǝrgha ƙǝm, yi mahan wai kee har ta ten yi mǝd ɗǝ.
\v 27 Akwasamadghǝn, nuɗi ƙǝm mǝrgha.
\v 28 Nanǝnya, ahu thliirha sǝ hu mǝrra na nuɗi tsaurha yi wun tsaunǝn kanda heu mǝd, tǝrang nda nuɗasǝ?”
\p 
\v 29 Nggǝrangga Yeeso kanda sǝ, “Numad nun mbǝ mǝmǝl wa ƙǝsǝr sǝnggun Laɓar Faara na chichireethlee hai tǝ sǝsǝmndǝghǝn wa.
\v 30 Thliirha sǝ hu mǝra mbǝ nishya tǝ hǝshya kakhrha wa. Nanda tsaurha kǝla fathlǝngya Faara a talara.
\v 31 Amma aten thliirha sǝ hu mǝra, karantanggun ˈya ndang na laɓar Faara kun wa?
\v 32 ‘Nggini Faara yi Ibrahim, Faara yi Ishaku, tǝ ƙǝm Faara yi Yakubu’. Mbǝ Faara ni yi mǝrya wa, amma yi fingya natǝ yibrha fa.”\f + \fr 22:32 \ft Kyarhaɓa 3:6\f*
\p 
\v 33 Sǝkna fiya ndǝn wumngga hai, ǝna ǝnwulteena nda tǝ tsahayighǝn ha.
\s1 Ngyakhrha na manggǝn
\r (Markus12:28-34; Luka10:25-28)
\p 
\v 34 Amma sǝkna Farisayini tǝ ndaarha nggǝlangga Yeeso mii Sadukiyayini tǝ laɓaara nggǝrang nǝn kanda sǝ, wuma nda hai ka a nggǝra nda tsahang mee.
\v 35 Tal ahur famalǝmngya ɗeleewar Musa, na midghǝn sǝ a ɗǝfang takthleera nǝn tsahang mee nǝn Yeeso,
\v 36 “Mala yanggini manggǝn ahur ngyakhkya heu?”
\p 
\v 37 Nggǝmangga Yeeso, “Nggǝmu Chinǝm Faarwa tǝ hurwa heu, tǝ shingnduwa heu tǝ huten wa heu.\f + \fr 22:37 \ft Nggurub Ngwa Kumaarha 6:5\f*
\v 38 Yanɗiya ndǝna katǝra ngyakhrha na mam.
\v 39 Yi sǝri ƙǝm nǝghǝn manggǝn: ʻNggǝmu tuladwa ƙǝla altenwa.
\v 40 Ngyakhrha heu tǝ tsahad annabiya ha na nda aten ngyakhkini sǝri ya.”
\s1 Tsakh mee aten Ƙǝrǝsti
\r (Markus12:35-37; Luka20:41-44)
\p 
\v 41 Wumna Farisaya hai tsahangga Yeeso mee kanda,
\v 42 “Mani numad nun aten Ƙǝrǝsti? Wan wunni?”
\p Ndang ngganda, “Wan Ndauda ni.”
\p 
\v 43 Nggǝrangga Yeeso kanda sǝ, “Ƙǝƙǝn na Ndauda tǝ sǝsǝmnda Sǝsǝna aaghǝn ‘Chinǝm’? Ƙǝsǝr ndagha Ndauda,
\b
\q1 
\v 44 Ndangga Chinǝm yina China:
\q2 ‘Tsawu a yisǝmanna,
\q1 ƙǝl a tsawangɗi fatsanggiwa
\q2 a kamu saryiwa.’\f + \fr 22:44 \ft Dzabura 110:1\f*
\v 45 Ana Ndauda a aah Ƙǝrǝsti ‘Chinǝm,’ ƙǝƙǝn nǝn tsaurha wanggǝn?”
\p 
\v 46 Mbǝ niifa sǝ mbangga nggǝrang sǝ wa, ka farɗi mbǝ niifa sǝ ndengga yidghǝn nggǝrghǝn tsahang mee wa.
\c 23
\s1 Yanang Yeeso Famalǝngya ngyakhrha
\r (Markus12:38-39; Luka11:43,46; 20:45-47)
\p 
\v 1 Tǝrgha Yeeso ndanggǝn fiya wumngga hai tǝ fatsahayighǝn,
\v 2 “Famalǝmgya ngyakhrha tǝ Farisaya kanda ni nggǝmang na nda kanda fa a pǝr ngyakhrha Musa nda.
\v 3 Nanǝn kee tsahama tǝ ƙǝm ǝna taara nun tǝ ˈya ndang nanda kun, amma a ǝnaɗun kǝla nanda ǝnaarha wa, ƙǝsǝr mba nda ǝna ˈya na nanda a tsaharhaha wa.
\v 4 Nanda ɗǝfang rǝfrha fiya in na haghǝn, amma kanda tǝ alten ndan mba nda thlar kanda ko tǝ wan haara wa.”
\v 5 Na nda ǝna tar ndan ka a nagha fiya kanda, nanda ƙǝn masparma natǝ chireethla laɓar Faara a pǝmnggindan, na nda ndǝn pǝratsan nzǝnzang a mii karindan.\f + \fr 23:5 \ft Matta 6:1; Ɗeleewar Kirassa 15:38; Nggurub Ngwa Kumaarha 6:8\f*
\p 
\v 6 Yakh mid ndan tsaurha a mbǝd tsaukya na nggǝngga hu teera, tǝ kǝm mbǝd tsaukya natǝ thlǝma a ƙǝn tsahad Yahudaya.
\v 7 Na mid ndan a ndangˈya nda kanda yi mamnggirha a nan nda a wiirha hai ahu kasu, tǝ ƙǝm nagha fiya a aah kanda, Mala.
\v 8 “A nggǝmna fa a aah sa nda ‘Mala,’ wa ƙǝsǝr tǝmalǝmnda tǝtal ni, kun heu nuwun tal a wanmanggi.
\v 9 A aah ɗun kowunni ahu ƙǝshidɗi ya ‘Pǝpa’ wa, ƙǝsǝr Faara na talara ndǝna Pǝpa hu Sǝsǝna.
\v 10 A nggǝmna fa aagha kowunni sa ‘Mala’ wa, ƙǝsǝr tǝmalǝmnda tǝtali ni, ndǝna, Ƙǝrǝsti.
\v 11 Yi na manggǝn ahur nun tǝta ni a tsauka mafad nun.\f + \fr 23:11 \ft Matta 20:26-27; Markus 9:35; 10:43-44; Luka 22:26 \f*
\v 12 Amma kala nafiya manangga altenggindan nanda tsaurha ngguchit, tǝ kǝm nafiya tsawangga altenggindan ngguchit nanda manang kanda.\f + \fr 23:12 \ft Luka 14:11; 18:14\f*
\p 
\v 13 “Amma kawama, kun famalǝmngya ngyakhrha Musa tǝ Farisaya, fathlǝrɓuya! Nggǝlanggun kwatminda kyarha hu kutǝryid talara ɗǝ ma fiya. Kun tafad nun kyawun sa ɗǝ wa, ˈyaɗang kwamana nun fiya na mindan kyarha sa ɗǝ.”
\v 14 Kawama famalǝmngya Ngyakhrha tǝ Farisaya, ndirwiya, nun hǝb karid nishya mǝrna chimayi ndan, non naarha hwan Faara kaan ka a na kun nda. Tsaunǝn kee na nda a ngwang kumarha kun sǝ na pǝɗaghǝn.
\p 
\v 15 Kawama, famalǝmgya ngyakhrha tǝ Farisaya, fathlǝrɓuya! Nun wii tala aten chehweerha tǝ wuri aama ka wal niifa nun malangga ɗimiyidghǝn, a malang ɗǝ ɗimiyidghǝn, nun sǝɓang nda ɗǝ kaan kal kun nǝn ɗimiyirha.
\p 
\v 16 Kawama, kwamaya na kyad kwamana! Nun ndaarha, “Kala niifa aagha thlǝm Faara tǝ Ƙǝn Faara, mbǝ ɓillarha sǝ wa, amma kaala niifa aagha thlǝm Faara tǝ tǝfasa yi Ƙǝn Faara, tsau ɗǝ tǝta a ǝna ǝnɗa nǝn aah nǝn Faara a tenggǝn.”
\v 17 Kun nur kwamaya! Yanggi ni manggǝn, tǝfasa wa nduwa Ƙǝn Faara na a Urshalima tsaɓangga tǝfasa ɗǝ wa?
\v 18 Nun ndaarha, “Kaala niifa aagha Faara tǝ ‘mbǝd fǝr Sataka,’ mbǝ ɓillarha sǝ wa, amma niifa aagha thlǝm Faara tǝ ǝnfǝra na a mbǝd ǝna Sataka, tǝtani ǝna ǝnɗa nǝn ndanǝn nǝn a ǝnaarha.”
\v 19 Kun kwamaya! Yanggini manggǝn, ǝnfǝrɗi wa nduwa mbǝd nji sataka tsaɓangga ǝnfǝr ɗaɗǝ wa?
\v 20 Tsaunǝn kee, kala niifa aagha thlǝm Faara tǝ mbǝd nji ǝnfǝra, aah nǝn Faara tǝ ˈya na tenggǝn heu.
\v 21 A anna thlǝm Faara tǝ Ƙǝn Faara na a Urshalima, aah na thlǝm Faara na tǝ tsaurha a mbǝɗi.
\v 22 A anna thlǝm Faara tǝ Talara, na aah tsǝnggam Faara, tǝ ndǝghǝn na tǝ tsaurha ahu tsǝnggamɗi.\f + \fr 23:22 \ft Ishaya 66:1; Matta 5:34\f*
\p 
\v 23 Kawama famalǝmngya ngyakhrha Musa tǝ farisaya, fathlǝrɓuya! Nun fǝr ǝn fǝrrǝ nun tal ahu kum yi shi chimbee amma malanggun ǝngya na nggǝngga ahu ngyakhrha, ndǝna, ƙǝkafek, haɗang ndan fa, tǝ nggayirha. Ənggina ni kamngga na nggǝngga a ǝnon ya, a malang ɗun fingya wa.\f + \fr 23:23 \ft Ɗeleewar Firistaya 27:30\f*
\v 24 Kun kwamaya fa kyad kwamana, nun kang aama hai amawa nun muɗang kukwakhtaara amma nun muɗang thlǝkhmu.
\p 
\v 25 Kawama, famalǝmgya ngyakhrha Musa tǝ Farisaya, fathlǝrɓuya! Nun tsaɓang ƙǝsǝr wuhuleurha ɗǝ tǝ tasau, amma ahurghǝn nǝghǝn lǝlǝgɗa tǝ nggǝm alteena tǝ hukrha!
\v 26 Sa kwamad tǝfarisarha! Tsaɓang hur wuhuleurha ɗǝ tǝ tasau ˈwan, tǝna ƙǝsǝrghǝn narha tsǝtsaɓaɗǝ ƙǝm.
\p 
\v 27 “Kawama, famalǝmgya ngyakhrha Musa tǝ Farisaya, fathlǝrɓuya! Nuwun kǝla ten kwaya ƙǝmang nanda tǝ penti na pǝpet, nagha ngga hu yirha, amma hurghǝn lǝlǝgɗa tǝ aal nafiya mǝrgha tǝ paarha ɗǝɗamǝn-ɗǝɗamǝn.\f + \fr 23:27 \ft Tar Fathlǝngya 23:3\f*
\v 28 Tǝ ƙǝm ahu yirha naa fiya a na kun ka nafiya, amma ahur nun sǝ nuwun lǝlǝgɗa tǝ thlǝrɓuyirha tǝ mbǝlfeerha.”
\p 
\v 29 “Kawama, famalǝmgya ngyakhrha Musa tǝ Farisaya, fathlǝrɓuya! Nun tǝn ten kwaya a annabiya, tǝ kǝm nun sakhɗang nda ten kwaya yi ka fiya fǝrgha ƙǝkafek a Faara.
\v 30 Tǝrgha nun ndaarha, ‘Andam nǝghǝm sǝ a sayid chichiyinǝm, kam ɗangwan kanda sǝ ɓǝlang nda annabiya wa.’
\v 31 Amma a naɗun a ndaarha kee, nun a thlǝghanggǝn altennun tǝ ndaarha kunni chichiya nafini ɓǝlangga annabi yini.
\v 32 Ɗama mbeeɗǝ ngwalanggǝn ˈya katǝrangna chichiyi nun hai.”
\v 33 \f + \fr 23:33 \ft Matta 3:7; 12:34; Luka 3:7\f*Kun huthlingya, wangya huthlingya na tǝ mbǝlfeerha yid! Ƙǝƙǝn nun hǝrǝkrha ma ngwa kumad hwanga?
\v 34 Tsaunǝn kee niya thlǝnang annabiya kun ɗǝ tǝ fasǝngya, tǝ famalǝmngya ngyakhrha Musa. Amma nun a ɓǝlang fingya tǝ taurha ɗǝ, nun a tsaɗa fingya ahu ƙǝn tsahad Yahudaya, nun takkwa kanda tala-tala, kun a sǝsang kanda.
\v 35 Tsaunǝn kee, niya thlǝnang nafina ɗǝ ya ƙǝsǝr na hakked ka nafini ɓǝlang nun a tsaurha a ten nun heu ka a sayi far Habila kaniifa ɗǝgha ten Dzakariya wan Mberikiya, ɓǝlang nun a pathlang Ƙǝn Faara na a Urshalima tǝ mbǝd ǝna sataka.\f + \fr 23:35 \ft Kyarhaɓa 4:8; 2 Laɓarya 24:20-21\f*
\v 36 Niya pǝrang kǝkafek kun, na ǝnggini a katǝrarha hai hu ƙǝshiid weeriya.
\s1 Sǝb hur Yeeso ɗǝ aten Urshalima
\r (Luka13:34,35)
\p 
\v 37 Aiya Urshalima, Urshalima! Fa ɓǝl annabiya tǝ muk fathlǝngya Faara tǝ feera thlǝnna nda thlǝmadwa ɗǝ! Saara kurmi tǝrna minna a wumanggi kun kamuna ɓa kǝla na ɗiyarha ngwang wanggighǝn kamughǝn ɗǝ, amma karɗun fa.
\v 38 Kǝlama hai nanǝnya, malang nda wuri nun kun fa tsauɗǝ kwad wure.\f + \fr 23:38 \ft 1 Kutǝrya 9:7,8; Irmiya 22:5\f*
\v 39 Ƙǝsǝr niya pǝranggǝn kun, mbun a nggǝr na nggi ɓal wa ƙǝl fara ndanun, “Tǝ parkani niifɗi na a ɓarha ɓa hu thlǝm Chinǝm.”\f + \fr 23:39 \ft Dzabura 118:26; Matta 21:9\f*
\c 24
\s1 Əngya na a katǝrarha hai a mii ngwala ƙǝshiirha
\r (Markus13:1-2; Luka21:5-6)
\p 
\v 1 Na Yeeso a mal Ƙǝn Faara na a Urshalima, kyaɗangga fatsahayighǝn tur tǝngya Ƙǝn Faara.
\v 2 Amma nggǝranggǝn kanda sǝ, “Naɗun tur tǝnggini na heu ya? Niya pǝrang kǝkafek kun, mbǝ feera sǝ ko tǝtal na nda a mala aten shadghǝn wa, kahad nanda chang nda kanda hai!”
\s1 Katǝra sǝsaarha
\r (Markus13:3-13; Luka21:7-19)
\p 
\v 3 Tsǝɓaku na Yeeso tsau a ten ɗǝfya wumnda Dzaitun, ɓagha fatsahayighǝn thlǝmadghǝn ɓa ɓǝɓee ndang ngganda, “Pǝranggǝn kan a kwan na ǝnggini katǝrarha hai ya? Mani a tsaurha ǝnsakhrha wuttuwa ɓa tǝ ngwala mii ƙǝshiirha?”
\p 
\v 4 Ndangga Yeeso kanda, “Kwarama, a nggǝmɗun fa nggaɓagha niifa kun wa,
\v 5 ƙǝsǝr nafiya hangga na a ɓarha ɓa hu thlǝmna, na nda a ndaarha, ‘Nggini Ƙǝrǝsti,’ har na nda nggaɓa fiya hangga.
\v 6 Nun a sǝk laɓar yangya, tǝ mii ndaama aten yangya, amma a tǝrǝmɗun wa, tsauɗǝ tǝtani a katǝragha ǝnggini hai, amma ɓawa mii ngwaladghǝn ɓa ˈwan wa.
\v 7 Na tur a thleng tur fa tǝ yanda, na kutǝryirha a thleng kutǝryirha fa. Na miirha a narha sǝ tǝ rǝprha ƙǝshiirha fa a mbǝya ɗǝɗamǝn-ɗǝɗamǝn.
\v 8 Amma heu ǝngginiya katǝra mii sǝsarha ni kee.”
\p 
\v 9 “Na nda a ƙǝsang nda kun, sǝsang ngganda kun tǝ kǝm ɓǝlang ngganda kun. Ƙǝshiirha heu na nda kar kun ƙǝsǝr ka thlǝmna.\f + \fr 24:9 \ft Matta 10:22\f*
\v 10 Fiya hangga na a mal fǝrƙǝkafekkid ndan, na nda a fǝr ndan tǝ kar ndan.
\v 11 Na annabiya fa nggaɓaya a kyarhaɓa hangga, nggaɓa fiya nda hangga.
\v 12 Na mbǝlfeerha a mulgha hai, nggǝm ndan nǝn a tsaurha shishiu.
\v 13 Amma kala niifa ƙǝrǝsgha ta mii ngwaladghǝn ɗǝ nǝn a hǝrǝkrha.\f + \fr 24:13 \ft Matta 10:22\f*
\v 14 Laɓarɗi na Mbǝnggǝn yi kutǝryid Faara na nda a pǝrghǝn kahad hu ƙǝshiirha ɗǝ, ƙǝsǝr ka sǝkka talya ndǝn; a mbǝra ɓagha mii ngwaladghǝn ɓa.”
\s1 Sǝsaarha na ɓayi
\r (Markus13:14-23; Luka21:20-24)
\p 
\v 15 “Nun a naa ǝn tsanda na rǝk fiya, ƙǝt hu Ƙǝnna na Chahal ƙǝla ndaana annabi Ndaniyel. (Ngwa walangga tǝ karatarha),\f + \fr 24:15 \ft Tar fathlǝngya 16:13; Ndaniyel 9:27; 11:31; 12:11\f*
\v 16 Tǝrgha nafiya na ahur Yahudiya tǝtani ɗanda wumngya sǝ.
\v 17 Niifa na aten ƙǝnna a ndaa ɗǝ nǝn a tǝra hai ɗǝgha tǝr ˈya ɓa a wuri wa.
\v 18 Niifa na hee a ndaa ɗǝ nǝn wutta wure ɗǝ ɗǝgha tǝrang kootodghǝn ɓa wa.
\v 19 Nǝn a tsaurha ǝn kawa a nishya na a hur tǝ nishya na tǝ waya ƙǝsǝr ahu sayidɗi!
\v 20 Hwanama Faara amana ɗadɗi naarha a sayid mbiirha nduwa afar yibrha Yahudaya wa.
\v 21 Ƙǝsǝr a farɗi na sǝsarha a naarha sǝ kaan ˈwawa tam naarha sǝ kee ka a far katǝra ƙǝshiirha ta weeri ɗaɓa ya, mbǝ turghǝn a nggǝr naarha sǝ ɓalwa.\f + \fr 24:21 \ft Ndaniyel 12:1; Sǝsǝnid Yahaya 7:14\f*
\v 22 A mbǝ thlaghang nanda ɓenggina haaɗǝ ya wa, mbǝ niifa sǝ na a naarha tǝ yibrha wa. Amma ƙǝsǝr ka nafiya wurna Faara ndǝn nanda thlahang ɓenggina haaɗǝ.”
\p 
\v 23 “Ahu sayidɗi a ndang niifa kun, ‘Kuloɗǝ, kulo Ƙǝrǝsti ɗiya!’ Nduwa ‘Kulo ndǝghǝn taarha!’ A fǝrna ƙǝkafek sǝ wa.
\v 24 Ƙǝsǝr na fa nggaɓaya Ƙǝrǝsti sǝ tǝ fa nggaɓaya annabiya a kyarhaɓa, na nda a ǝna ǝnsakhkya mǝmanggǝn tǝ ǝnwuteengya ka a nggaɓa fiya nda har tǝ fingya wurna nda anaɗǝ a ǝnaarha hai.”
\p 
\v 25 “Ƙǝlama hai, ˈWaɗi teena yanangɗi kun ƙǝtǝm.”
\p 
\v 26 “Nanǝn kee a ndang niifa kun, ‘Kulo ndǝghǝn taarha a kaheerha,’ a kyaɗun ƙǝsha ɗǝ wa; nduwa, ‘Kulo ndǝghǝn ahur ƙǝnna ya,’ a fǝrɗun ƙǝkafek sǝ wa.
\v 27 Ƙǝsǝr ƙǝla na ˈyaara kyatta a man kyat faara nǝn djaara hai ta man hǝmndǝghǝn ɗǝ, nanǝn kee na wutta Wan niifa ɓa a narha kee.”\f + \fr 24:27 \ft Luka 17:24; Matta 8:20\f*
\p 
\v 28 “Mbǝrha nana mǝrra sǝ, a mbǝɗani na sǝkhɗiya wumnda sa hai.”\f + \fr 24:28 \ft Luka 17:37 \f*
\s1 Wutta Wan niifa ɓa
\r (Markus13:24-27; Luka21:25-28)
\p 
\v 29 Akwasamad sǝsadɗi ya,
\b
\q1 “ ‘Na yanfaara a tsaurha wula,
\q2 ndǝree ƙǝm mbǝ a kyat kukwaryirha wa.
\q1 Na wufǝlngarya mukrha hai a fǝrakh-amshi,
\q2 ǝngya na mǝmanggǝn na talara nanda tsǝˈyafa.’”\f + \fr 24:29 \ft Ishaya 13:10; 34:4; Ezikiyel 32:7; Djoyel 2:10,31; Dzafaniya 1:15; Sǝsǝnid Yahaya 6:12, 13; 8:12\f*
\b
\p 
\v 30 “Ahu sayidɗi na nda a naa ǝnsakhrha a fǝrakh-amshi yi Wan niifa. Nafiya ƙǝshiirha heu nanda tǝrha ka hǝreenga. Nanda a na Wan niifa ɓayi ahu hashmbe a fǝrakh-amshi hai, tǝ sǝsǝmnda tǝ mamnggirha kaan.\f + \fr 24:30 \ft Ndaniyel 7:13; Dzakariya 12:10-14; Sǝsǝnid Yahaya 1:7\f*
\v 31 Nǝn a thlǝn fathlǝnggighǝn ɓa tǝ pi kodwomnda, na nda wumang nafighǝn ɓa na wuwura hu kudma faɗa na ahu ƙǝshiirha.”
\s1 Tsaharhaha a ten ɗǝf shiɓarha
\r (Markus13:28-31; Luka21:29-33)
\p 
\v 32 “Nanǝnya tsahama ˈya a fat shiɓadɗiya, ana wuhwaryighǝn a kyaharra hai, nǝn a tsǝtsǝtta, nun sǝndasǝ nduwus fegrha ɓa.
\v 33 Nǝghǝn kee kǝm, anaɗun ǝnggini heu ya, nun a sǝnda sǝ nduwus wuttǝghǝn ɓa, nǝghǝn a mii kwatminda fa.
\v 34 Niya pǝrang ƙǝkafek kun, nafiya ƙǝshidɗiya mba nda mǝra wa, kǝl ma katǝra ǝnggina hai ya.
\v 35 Nda talara tǝ hweeɗe na nda a ngwalarha hai amma Laɓarna mbǝ tam ngwalarha hai wa.”
\s1 Mbǝ niifa sǝ sǝngga far ɓad Ƙǝrǝsti ɓa wa
\r (Markus13:32-37; Luka17:26-30,34-36)
\p 
\v 36 “Mbǝ niifa sǝ sǝngga farɗi, nduwa sayi na ǝnggini a katǝrarha hai ya wa, ko fathlǝngya Faara na talara nduwa Wanggǝn tafadghǝn wa, ƙǝl Chin katenggǝn.
\v 37 Ƙǝla katǝra nǝn hai a thlakh mbǝd Nuhu, nǝn a naarha kee a far wutta Wan niifa ɓa.\f + \fr 24:37 \ft Katǝrarha 6:5-8\f*
\v 38 A faryini kapa na aam afa afa ɗi ɓarha ɓa, fiya a hǝbrha tǝ saarha, kanda kakhrha tǝ fǝr wanggindan chimarha ɗǝ, ta farɗa ɗǝ kyana Nuhu hu kombuwol hai.\f + \fr 24:38 \ft Katǝrarha 6:14\f*
\v 39 Sǝngwanda ˈya na katǝrarha hai wa, har ɓana aam afa afa ɗaɓa hwanggǝn kanda ɗǝ. Nǝn a naarha kee a far wutta Wan niifa ɓa.\f + \fr 24:39 \ft Katǝrarha 6:24\f*
\v 40 Nafiya sǝri a ǝna taara kyab a hee, na nda tǝr tal mal tahadghǝn nda.
\v 41 Nishya sǝri a hǝrha ahu fǝna, na nda tǝrang nda tal mal tahadghǝn nda.”
\p 
\v 42 “Tsaunǝn kee, tsawama nggungwa fa, ƙǝsǝr sǝnggun farɗi na Chinun a ɓarha ɓa wa.
\v 43 Amma a sǝnunsǝ: A ndam na turi ɗi a sǝn farɗi na ngaara a ɓarha ɓa a fiɗikrha, kam mbǝ a shiirha malanggǝn ngaarɗi kyagha minda keeghǝn hai wa.
\v 44 Nanǝn kee tsawama nggugwafa, ƙǝsǝr na Wan Niifa a ɓarha ɓa a sayidɗi sǝngwawa nun sǝ.”\f + \fr 24:44 \ft 1 Tasalonikaya 5:6; Luka 12:39-40\f*
\s1 Ka niifa tǝ ndǝrwid niifa
\r (Luka12:41-48)
\p 
\v 45 “Wunni mafadɗi na tǝ ƙǝkafek fa, ɗǝfang na turighǝn tǝkǝla wurighǝn ha, na fǝrang ǝnnarhami fingya mafaya ahu sayidɗi kamngga?
\v 46 Nǝn a naarha ngga a fad mafadɗi a wud turighǝn ɓa ɓagha walghǝn a ǝna targhǝn.
\v 47 Niya pǝrang kǝkafek kun, nǝn a ɗǝfang nda tsauka mam a ten karidghǝn heu.
\v 48 Amma andam mafadɗi tǝ mbǝlfeerha ni, nǝn a ndang nda altenggǝn, ‘Turina mbǝ a wutta ɓa wet wa.’
\v 49 Tǝrgha katǝranggǝn ɗǝk fingya mafaya hai, ndǝghǝn a hǝbrha tǝ sarha tǝ fingya na a nggal mbalya,
\v 50 a ǝnaɗǝ kee na turighǝn a wutta ɓa ahu sayidɗi tǝ farɗi sǝngwawa nǝn sǝ.
\v 51 Nǝn a kyathlang nda ɗǝ ɗawal-ɗawal tǝ kǝm fǝrang mbǝrha nǝn a thlǝmad fa thǝrɓuya. A mbǝɗi na tǝrha sǝ tǝ ƙǝt mee.”
\c 25
\s1 Karapu aten wutaraya kum
\p 
\v 1 Tǝrgha ndagha Yeeso, “Kutǝryid talara nǝghǝn ƙǝla wutaraya kum tǝrang nanda patillad ndan ka ɗaa nda wal wutsamnda.\f + \fr 25:1 \ft Luka 12:35\f*
\v 2 Tuf ahur wutarayini nurya ni, tuf ƙǝm na nda ndǝndǝl.
\v 3 Fingya yini na nurghǝn takhkwa nda fǝɗeerha haɗǝ ka ɗaa nda ira hu patilla yindan hai wa.
\v 4 Amma fingyayini tuf na ndǝndǝl takh nda fǝɗeerha haɗǝ ahu ƙǝthlikrha ka patilla yindan.
\v 5 Ɓawana wutsamnda ɓa wed, ƙǝsgha ɓeena kanda shii nda ɗǝ.”
\p 
\v 6 “A manad fǝɗikrha thlii nda sǝ ka mbeela sǝk nanda. ‘Kulo wutsamnda ya thleema sǝ ɗun hwathlaghǝn fa!’
\v 7 Tǝrgha wutarayini kum thlii nda sǝ tangsang ngganda patilla yindan.
\v 8 Nurya wutarayini tuf tsahang fǝɗeerha nda wutarayini tuf na ndǝndǝl, Naghan a hwan kun, ‘Ənaman fǝɗed nun kan ha ngguchit lee, ƙǝsǝr na patilla yinan a mǝra hai.’
\v 9 Amma nggǝrangga fingyayina sǝ, ‘Mbǝ tsǝghang ƙǝm heu wa. Ɗama ɗǝ ɗun hii yinun ɓa.’”
\v 10 Wii nanda ka hii fǝɗedɗa ɗǝ, a samad ndan ɓagha wutsamnda ɓa. Tǝrgha fingya yini ngwagha fa kya nda a mbǝd wutsǝfayid kahadɗa ɗǝ, chang ngganda kwakirma.
\p 
\v 11 Tsǝɓaku sǝlgha fingya yina ɓa ɗǝgha ka hii fǝɗedɗa ɗǝ, isha nda a ƙǝshi na nda a aah farha, “Chinǝm! Chinǝm! Inang kwakirma kan hai!”
\v 12 Amma nggǝrangga wutsamnda kanda sǝ, “Ƙǝkafek, sǝngwi kun wa.”\f + \fr 25:12 \ft Luka 13:25\f*
\p 
\v 13 “Tsaunǝn kee tsawama nggungwa fa, ƙǝsǝr sǝnggun farɗi nduwa sayidɗi niya wutta ɓa wa.”
\s1 Karapu aten mafaya mahan
\r (Luka19:11-27)
\p 
\v 14 Tǝ ƙǝm kutǝryid Talara nǝghǝn ƙǝla niifa na a wii tala a mbǝrha ɗǝ inggun. Aah mafayighǝn nǝn ɓa fǝrang ƙǝnaghǝnǝn kanda.
\v 15 Fǝrang wuɗǝɓǝl wurirha nǝn yi tal yawarha tuf, yi sǝri fǝrang wuɗǝɓǝl wurirha nǝn yawarha sǝri, mafarha yi mahan fǝranggǝn yawarha tal, kowunni mǝmǝl tǝ ˈya nǝn a mbang nda. Tǝrgha wii fayighǝn nǝn.
\v 16 Yi mafarha thlǝgha wuɗǝɓǝla yawarha tuf, ǝna shafili nǝn sǝ wal chikrha nǝn yawarha tuf.
\v 17 Yi thlǝgha yawarha sǝri ndǝghǝnggi ƙǝm ǝna shafili nǝn sǝ wal chikrha nǝn yawarha sǝri.
\v 18 Amma yi thlǝgha yawarha tal wiigha ɗǝgha ra kwaarha ɓǝɓenggǝn wuɗǝɓǝlɗi ki turighǝn sahai.
\p 
\v 19 Mǝnnǝn ha wudgha turi mafayina ɓa aah kanda nǝn ɓa a fǝrang kirassa ˈya nda ǝnana nda tǝ wuɗǝɓǝlghǝn.
\v 20 Yi mafarha fǝrang nǝn wuɗǝɓǝl wurirha yawarha tuf ɓagha ɓa ndǝghǝn, “Turina, fǝrenna wuɗǝɓǝl wurirha yawarha tuf ka a ǝna shafili ni sǝ, walɗi chikrha yawarha tuf atenggǝn.”
\v 21 Falghǝna turighǝn, ndǝghǝn, “Usakko ka mafanna. Ənanna ƙǝkafekkirha ahu ˈya ngguchit. Niya ɗǝforha aten ǝngya hangga. Ɓoɓa ɓa ǝna wutsǝfayirha tǝ nggi.”
\p 
\v 22 Mafadɗi thlǝgha wuɗǝɓǝl wurirha yawarha sǝri ɓagha ɓa ndǝghǝn, “Turina, fǝrenna wuɗǝɓǝl wurirha yawarha sǝri, ǝnaɗi shafili sǝ, walɗi chikrha yawarha sǝri atenggǝn.”
\v 23 Ndangga turiɗi, “Usakko ka mafanna na tǝ ƙǝkafek fa. Ənana ƙǝkafekkirha ahu ˈya ngguchit, niya ɗǝforha aten ǝngya hangga. Ɓoɓa ɓa ǝna wutsǝfayirha tǝ nggi.”
\p 
\v 24 Tǝrgha yi mafarha thlǝgha wuɗǝɓǝl wurirha yawarha tal ɓagha ɓa, ndǝghǝn, “Turina, sǝnɗi sa na ngyangthlang, na hathla a mbǝrha hǝfwa nana tǝ ƙǝm na wumang ǝnnarhami hai huɗawana na. Sa ƙǝm na midwa sǝ ǝn ka kaan.
\v 25 Nanǝn kee tǝrǝmɗi raɗi kwarha ɓǝɓeng ɗi wuɗǝɓǝl wa sǝ. Kulo ndǝghǝn ya thlu ǝnwa.”
\p 
\v 26 Amma ndangga turighǝn, “Sa tǝmbǝlfed mafarha na tǝ sǝbrha yid! Ashe kyanna sǝnda sǝ ni hathla a mbǝrha hǝfwa ni tǝ ƙǝm ni wumang ǝnnarhami hai a mbǝrha huɗawani,
\v 27 mani ɗǝfewana wuɗǝɓǝl na hu mbanki? A wuɗɗi ɓa kam niya thlǝghǝn har tǝ chikrha atenggǝn.”
\v 28 Tǝrgha ndǝghǝn, “Thlaama wuɗǝɓǝlɗi na a harghǝn, fǝrang nggǝnun yanɗi natǝ wuɗǝɓǝl wurirha yawarha kum.
\v 29 Ƙǝsǝr kala yanɗi natǝ ˈyaha na nda chighanggǝn, tǝnǝn waala ha kaan. Amma kala niifa mbuwa tǝghǝn ha, ko yanɗi na ngguchit nanǝn tǝghǝn ha na nda a thlang hai a haarghǝn.\f + \fr 25:29 \ft Matta 13:12; Markus 4:25; Luka 8:18\f*
\v 30 Nanǝnya muwaman ka wuɗi mafadɗiya a ƙǝsha ɗǝ, ahu wula ɗǝ, a mbǝɗani na nanda a tǝrha sǝ tǝ ƙǝt mee.”\f + \fr 25:30 \ft Matta 8:12; 22:13; Luka 13:28\f*
\s1 Far ngwala mii ngwa kumarha
\p 
\v 31 A fara ɓana Wan Niifa ɓa ahu mamnggitghǝn, tǝ fathlǝngya Faara a thlǝmadghǝn, nǝn a tsaurha ahu tsǝnggam mamnggitghǝn a talara.\f + \fr 25:31 \ft Matta 16:27; 19:28\f*
\v 32 Nafiya ƙǝshiirha na nda a wumnda a mbedghǝn ɓa, nǝn wurang nda fiya ɗǝ ƙǝla na tǝlafrha wurang nda chauraya ɗǝ ahur ˈwalya.
\v 33 Nǝn a sang chauraya a yisǝmadghǝn ˈwalya ƙǝm a yikawadghǝn.
\v 34 Tǝrgha na kutǝra a ndang nda fingya na a yisǝmadghǝn, “Ɓama ɓa, kun fǝrangna Pǝpa parka, harama langaad kutǝryidɗi ɗǝfang nanda ka kun ka ǝnana nda ƙǝshiirha.
\v 35 Ƙǝsǝr ƙǝs miirha nggi fǝree ɗun ǝnnarhami. Ƙǝs hushimnda nggi fǝree aam saarha nun. Tsauɗi ronga, thlǝ nggi nun fa ahu wurayinun.
\v 36 Niyi tawalth hai fǝree ǝn ƙǝnda nun. Fanna ɓee, pu nggi nun. Muwenda ahu porsǝna ɗǝ, ɗun ka ndee ˈyaɗǝ.”
\p 
\v 37 “Tǝrgha ka nafiya na nda a nggǝrang sǝ, ‘Chinǝm, akwanni nanan sa a miirha fǝro ǝnnarhami nan? Nduwa ƙǝs hushimnda sa furo aam saarha nan?
\v 38 Nduwa ronga ni sa thlǝ sa nan fa? Nduwa sa tawalth furo ǝn kaala nan?
\v 39 Akwan nanan sa fadwa ɓee nduwa ahu porsǝna ɗan ndoˈya?’
\v 40 Na kutǝrɗi a nggǝrang kanda sǝ, ‘Niya pǝrang ƙǝkafek kun, a ǝnang ɗun tal na ngguchit kaan ahur wanman nggini kyana ya, ǝna nun ndǝn a nggi.’
\p 
\v 41 “Tǝrgha na kutǝrɗi a kyaharra thlǝmad nafina ɗǝ na a yikawadghǝn ndanggǝn kanda, ‘Weema ma thlǝmadna, kun shiwangna Faara, ɗun hu waarha ɗǝ mbuwa mǝra hai tangsang nanda hai ka sheetan tǝ fathlǝnggighǝn.
\v 42 Ƙǝsǝr nggi hu miirha, fǝreewun ǝnnarhami wa. Ƙǝs hushimnda nggi fǝreewun aam saarha wa.
\v 43 Tsauɗi ronggirha thlǝwun nggi fa ahu wurayinun wa. Nggi tawalth hai, fǝreewun ǝn kaala fa wa. Fanna ɓee tǝ ƙǝm nggi ahu porsǝna ɗuwun ka ndee ˈyaɗǝ wa.’
\p 
\v 44 “Kanda ƙǝm na nda a nggǝrang sǝ ndaa nda, ‘Chinǝm, akwan ni nanan sa a miirha nduwa a hushimnda nduwa ronga ni sa nduwa tawalth nduwa fadwa ɓee nduwa ahu porsǝna, ɗowan sǝ wa?’
\v 45 Nǝn a nggǝrang nda kanda sǝ, ‘Niya pǝrang ƙǝkafek kun, a karɗun ɗang nda wanmanggina sǝ na nggu-ngguchit ya, kar nun ɗeerha sǝ.’
\v 46 Tǝrgha na nda a ɗǝrha hu sǝsaarha ɗǝ mbuwa tam ngwalaarha, amma ka nafiya na nda a ɗǝrha hu yibrha ɗǝ mbuwa tam ngwalaarha.”\f + \fr 25:46 \ft Ndaniyel 12:2\f*
\c 26
\s1 Ƙǝnang mamngya Yahudaya hai a ɓǝlang ngganda Yeeso
\r (Markus14:1-2; Luka22:1-2; Yahaya11:45-53)
\p 
\v 1 Ngwalang na Yeeso thlǝk ǝnggini heu, ndanggǝn fatsahayighǝn,
\v 2 “Ƙǝla sǝnnunsǝ, takhƙǝn ɓeena sǝri na a ǝna wutsǝfayid tǝɗaarha nda, na nda a fǝr Wan Niifa ka a tawang ngganda ɗǝ.”\f + \fr 26:2 \ft Kyarhaɓa 12:1-27\f*
\p 
\v 3 Tǝrgha mamnda firistaya tǝ shingya na nda a wumnda hai a kwakirǝm Firis na manggǝn, na thlǝmnggǝn Kayafa.
\v 4 Ƙǝnang ngganda hai na nda a ƙǝsang Yeeso ɓǝɓee ɓǝlang ngganda.
\v 5 Ndaa nda, “Amma mbǝ a sayid wutsǝfayidɗi wa. Naɗǝ fiya ǝna kakyathlaanga.”
\s1 Irang nuneefa fǝɗeerha Yeeso teena a Mbetani
\r (Markus14:3-9; Luka7:37-38; Yahaya12:1-8)
\p 
\v 6 Nana Yeeso a Mbetani, a minda kii Siman ˈwana termeerha ƙǝsa.
\v 7 Nanǝn a hǝb ǝnnarhami, ɓagha nuneefa ɓa tǝ ƙǝthlikrha urdi na sǝdghǝn mbǝnggǝn na tǝ wuɗǝɓǝla fa kaan iranggǝnǝn Yeeso a tenggǝn.\f + \fr 26:7 \ft Luka 7:37-38\f*
\v 8 Amma nana fatsahayina ndǝn sǝbgha hur ndan ɗǝ ndaa nda, “Yanɗiya sǝbrha ni ɗǝ kee.”
\v 9 “A ndam kwang heng nda fǝɗedɗa ɗǝ na nda a wal wuɗǝɓǝla sǝ kaan fǝrang wuɗǝɓǝlghǝn nda fa yamiya.”
\p 
\v 10 Amma sǝnang na Yeeso ǝnɗa hai na nda a thlǝkrha ndanggǝn kanda, “Kama nun a ɓilla nuɗiya? Ai ǝnaɗǝ ˈya na ngga a nggi.
\v 11 Ƙǝtsar na fa yamiya narha tǝ kun, amma mbi naarha ƙǝtsar tǝ kun wa.\f + \fr 26:11 \ft Nggurub Ngwa Kumaarha 15:11\f*
\v 12 Iree nǝn urdi ɗa fa ya, ngwe nǝn fa ka yi panna.
\v 13 Niya pǝrang ƙǝkafek kun, Kala mbǝrha pǝrna nda laɓar Faara sǝ ahu ƙǝshidɗiya, ǝnɗi ǝnana nuɗiya mbǝ tam mbǝtta wa na nda naarha ɗalghǝn teena.”
\s1 Nggǝm Yahuda fa a fǝr Yeeso nǝn
\r (Markus14:10-11; Luka22:3-6)
\p 
\v 14 Tǝrgha Yahuda Iskaryoti tal ahur fatsahaya Yeeso kumkap sǝri ɗǝgha thlǝma mamnda firistaya ɗǝ
\v 15 tsakhmee nǝn, “Ma nun a fǝreerha a fǝrangɗi Yeeso kun?” Nanǝn kee fǝrang wuɗǝɓǝl wurirha nda kumnggit mahan.\f + \fr 26:15 \ft Dzakariya 11:12\f*
\v 16 Ka a farɗi nagha Yahuda a kaɗa kwamana na a fǝrang Yeeso nǝn kanda.
\s1 Hǝb Yeeso ǝnnarhami yi Tǝɗaarha tǝ fatsahayighǝn
\r (Markus14:12-21; Luka22:7-13; Yahaya13:21-30)
\p 
\v 17 A katǝra far wutsǝfayidɗi yi mburodi kula mekhna, ɓagha fatsahaya Yeeso thlǝmadghǝn ɓa tsahang mee nda, “A yanggi na midwa ɗan nggorha fa ɗǝna hǝb ǝnnadmid tǝɗaarha sǝ?”
\p 
\v 18 Ndanggǝn kanda, “A kyaɗun hu wupǝri ɗa hai, na niifa sǝ nun a naarha. Ndaman, ‘Ndagha mala, nduwus sayid na ɓa, ni a hǝb ǝnnadmid Wutsǝfayid Tǝɗaarha tǝ fatsahayina a minda kyawa.’ ”
\p 
\v 19 Nanǝn kee ǝnagha fatsahayini ƙǝla ndangna Yeeso kanda ngwa nda fa tǝ ǝnnadmid Wutsǝfayid Tǝɗaarha a mbǝɗi.
\p 
\v 20 Tsǝna figrha hai tsauka Yeeso hai hǝb ǝnnarhami nǝn tǝ fatsahayighǝn kumkap sǝri.
\v 21 Na nanda a hǝb ǝnnarhami ndangga Yeeso kanda, “Niya pǝrang ƙǝkafek kun, tal ahur nun nǝn a fǝr nggi.”
\p 
\v 22 Sǝbgha hur ndan ɗǝ nagha kowunni a ndang nda, “Nggini wa, Chinǝm?”
\p 
\v 23 Nggǝrangga Yeeso kanda sǝ, “Tal ahur nun hǝbgha ǝnnarhami tǝ nggi hu tasau tal nǝn a fǝr nggi.\f + \fr 26:23 \ft Dzabura41:9\f*
\v 24 Ƙǝsǝr tǝtani a mǝrgha Wan Niifa, ƙǝla thlǝkna Ɗeleewar Faara ƙǝtǝm. Amma ǝn kawa ni a niifɗi fǝrgha ndǝn. Nǝn a tsaurha a fad niifɗi a nggushi nggǝt waana ndan.”
\p 
\v 25 Tǝrgha Yahuda yanɗi na a fǝr Yeeso, ndǝghǝn nggi ƙǝm Tsakhmee nǝn, “Mala, nduwa nggini wa?”
\p Nggǝrangga Yeeso sǝ, “Sa ma thlǝk nan.”
\s1 Hǝb ǝnnarhami yi Chinǝm
\r (Markus14:22-26; Luka22:14-20; 11:23-25)
\p 
\v 26 Na nanda a hǝb ǝnnarhami, tǝrangga Yeeso mburodi sǝ usa Faara nǝn kyanggǝn hai fǝranggǝnǝn fatsahayighǝn ɗǝ ndanggǝn kanda, “Thlaama kyaman, thlu fanna ni ya.”
\p 
\v 27 Tǝranggǝn wuhuleurha sǝ na tǝ aam inabi usa Faara nǝn atenggǝn. Fǝranggǝnǝn kanda ɗǝ ndǝghǝn, “Saama kun heu.
\v 28 Ƙǝsǝr farna ni ya yi lǝghǝtta ɗǝfmee, irang nanda ɗǝ ka fiya hangga yi chakh ɗimiyirha.\f + \fr 26:28 \ft Kyarhaɓa 24:8; Irmiya 31:31-34\f*
\v 29 Niya ndang nda kun, mbiya nggǝr sa aam inabiɗi ya wa, ƙǝl a farɗi niya sa weerǝn ndǝghǝn tǝ kun ahu Kutǝryid Pǝpa.”
\p 
\v 30 Tǝrgha Yeeso tǝ fatsahayighǝn aah amshe nda, kya nda sǝ ɗǝnda wumnda ɗǝfya Dzaitun ɗǝ.
\s1 Na Mbiturus a ngaal sǝnda Yeeso
\r (Markus14:27-31; Luka22:31-34; Yahaya13:36-38)
\p 
\v 31 Tǝrgha ndangga Yeeso kanda, “A fǝɗik weeriya kun heu nun a ɗaarha ma nggi. Ƙǝsǝr nǝghǝn chichirethlee hai ahu ɗeleewar Faara,
\b
\q1 ‘Niya ɗǝk tǝlafǝdɗi,
\q2 na chiɓǝd chaukhrayini a weela hai.’”\f + \fr 26:31 \ft Dzakariya 13:7\f*
\b
\p 
\v 32 “Amma a thliiɗi sǝ ahu mǝrra, niya ˈwaarha ma kun a Nggalili ɗǝ, a mbǝɗani ɗǝnǝm ƙǝmarha sǝ.”\f + \fr 26:32 \ft Matta 28:16\f*
\p 
\v 33 Tǝrgha Ndangga Mbiturus, “Ko ɗad fiya heu ma sa, nggi kam mbi ɗaarha ma sa wa.”
\p 
\v 34 Nggǝrangga Yeeso sǝ, “Niya pǝro ƙǝkafek, Mbiturus, a fǝɗik ɗiya, kapa na kilngaara tǝtaarha, na a ngaal sǝndǝna katǝra mahan.”
\p 
\v 35 Amma ndagha Mbiturus, “Ko nǝm a mǝra kyab, mbi tam ngaal sǝnduwa wa!” Fingya fatsahaya ƙǝm ndaa nda kee.
\s1 Hwan Yeeso Faara a Nggetsǝmani
\r (Markus14:32-42; Luka22:39-46)
\p 
\v 36 Tǝrgha ɗǝgha Yeeso tǝ fatsahayighǝn a mbǝrha ɗǝ na nda aarha Nggetsǝmani, ndanggǝn kanda, “Tsawama a mbǝɗiya, ɗǝni mbǝɗaɗǝ taarha ɗi hwan Faara.”
\v 37 Tahanggǝn Mbiturus haaɗǝ tǝ wangya Dzabaɗi sǝri Yakubu tǝ Yahaya, nagha tǝ sǝbrha hura tǝ ɓillaarha.
\v 38 Tǝrgha ndanggǝn kanda, “Niyi tǝ sǝbrha hura kaan ƙǝla ni mǝra. Tsawama a mbǝɗiya a shiiɗun wa nam a ƙǝlaarha tǝ nggi.”
\p 
\v 39 Nduwusgha mbeeɗǝ kwanggǝn tenggǝn hweeɗe hai, hwan Faara nǝn, “Pǝpa, a naɗǝ a ǝnaarha hai, tǝrang wuhuleu sǝsadɗiya ma nggi. Ko nanǝn kee, mbǝ nggǝmnda hurna ni wa, amma nggǝmnda hur wa.”
\p 
\v 40 Tǝrgha wudgha thlǝmad fatsahayighǝn ɗǝ ɗǝgha wal kanda a shiirha. Ndanggǝn Mbiturus, “Mbun mbang naarha a ƙǝlaarha ko tsun tsǝɓaku wa?
\v 41 Tsawama a ƙǝlaarha non a hwan Faara, amawa nun kyaarha hu ƙǝƙǝrra hai. Na mid sǝsǝna sǝ, amma tsǝ thlu farha shishiu!”
\p 
\v 42 Wiigha Yeeso ma kanda yi sǝri hwan Faara nǝn, “Pǝpa, a mbǝ a ǝnaarha hai tǝrgha wuhuleu ɗaɗǝ ya wa ƙǝl a saaɗi ndǝn, ngwa tsauka nggǝmnda hurwa kee.
\v 43 Nggǝr nǝn wutta thlǝmad ndan ɗǝ, ɗǝgha wal kanda a shiirha, ƙǝsǝr nggalang ɓeena yid ndan.”
\p 
\v 44 Nanǝn kee nggǝrghǝn wiirha ka hwan Faara ɗǝ yi mahan, nagha a thlǝkrha ƙǝla ˈwanǝn thlǝkrha.
\v 45 Tǝrgha wudgha thlǝmad fatsahayighǝn ɓa ndanggǝn kanda, “Ɗaama mbeeɗǝ tǝ shiirha, yiɓun. Ƙǝlama hai mbiya nduwus sayi ɓa, fǝr nda Wan Niifa a haar faɗimiya hai.
\v 46 Thleema sǝ, tama wiim! Kulo niifɗi fǝrgha nggi ɓaɗa ɓa!”
\s1 Ƙǝsang nda Yeeso
\r (Markus14:43-50; Luka22:47-53; Yahaya18:3-12)
\p 
\v 47 Kapa na Yeeso nggǝlang miighǝn, Yahuda tal ahur fatsahaya Yeeso kumkap sǝri sǝlɗa ɓa tǝ fiya hangga a samadghǝn ƙǝs nda thlaukh ƙǝlarya ha tǝ sǝsalya. Mamnda firistaya tǝ shingya thlǝngga kanda ɓa.
\v 48 Tǝ thlǝrɓu ɗi, Yahuda, saghang ɗǝ kwamana kanda tǝ ndaarha, “Yanɗi fǝɓang ni niifɗa ni ƙǝsaaman.”
\p 
\v 49 Ɗǝgha Yahuda thlǝmad Yeeso ɗǝ ndanggǝn, “Niyi a ndoˈya Mala!” Tǝrgha fǝɓangga Yahuda.
\p 
\v 50 Nggǝrangga Yeeso sǝ, “Pashinna, ɗu mbeeɗǝ tǝ ˈya ɓoogha ɓa.” Tǝrgha nafini ƙǝsang ngganda Yeeso.
\p 
\v 51 Amma tal ahur fiya na a thlǝmad Yeeso ƙǝɗanggǝn thlaukh ƙǝlara sǝ kyathlanggǝn thlǝmad mafad firis ɗǝ.
\v 52 Ndangga Yeeso niifɗi, “Wuɗang thlaukh ƙǝlar wa ahu ƙǝnggǝn hai, ƙǝsǝr kala niifa tǝrgha thlaukh ƙǝlara, thlaukh ƙǝlara ni a ɓǝlang nda.
\v 53 Sǝnggun sǝ ni mbang hwan pǝpa, puwanggǝn fathlǝngya Faara ɓa kalgha kiwad sodjaya kumkap sǝri wa?
\v 54 Amma a ǝnaɗi kee, ƙǝƙǝn na laɓar Faara lǝghǝtta ndanǝn nǝn a katǝrarha hai ƙǝla nanǝnya?”
\p 
\v 55 Tǝrgha ndangga Yeeso fiya wumngga hai, “Tǝrwun nggi niifa ni na tǝmbǝng, nun ɓaarha ɓa tǝ thlaukh ƙǝlarya tǝ sǝsalya ka a ƙǝseewun wa? Ƙǝtsar nggi a thlǝmad nun, nggi a tsaharhaha ahu Ƙǝn Faara na a Urshalima ƙǝseewun wa.\f + \fr 26:55 \ft Luka 19:47; 21:37\f*
\v 56 Amma katǝraghǝn hai heu kee ka a lǝghǝdgha ˈya ndaana annabiya na chichirethlee hai ahu ɗeleewar Faara.” Tǝrgha fatsahayighǝn ɗaa nda mal Yeeso nda.
\s1 Ɗǝnda tǝ Yeeso a mbed kognaya ɗǝ
\r (Markus14:53-65; Luka22:54-55,63-71; Yahaya18:13-14,19-24)
\p 
\v 57 Tǝrgha nafini ƙǝsangga Yeeso ɗǝnda tǝghǝn a minda ƙi Kayafa ɗǝ mamnda firistaya, a mbǝɗani wumna famalǝmngya ngyakhrha sahai tǝ shingya.
\v 58 Amma Mbiturus mbuɗǝ samadghǝn ɗǝ inggun ta pǝpal minda mamnda firis ɗǝ. Kyagha sahai tsauka hai a thlǝmad fa ƙǝlaya ha nagha a ƙǝla ˈyaha na a katǝrarha hai.
\v 59 Mamnda firistayini tǝ kogna yini wumngga hai na nda a kaɗa kwamana na a ƙǝsangganda Yeeso tǝ ˈya na ɗimi, tǝna nda ɓǝlang nda.
\v 60 Amma walwa nda wa ko nanǝn fingya sǝ hangga nggǝmngga fa na nda a thlǝghang nggaɓaarha fa ǝnawa nda taara tǝ palth ndan wa. Akwasamadghǝn kyagha nafiya ɓa sǝri
\v 61 ndaa nda, “Ndagha kamshiɗiya, ‘Ni mbang chang Ƙǝn Faara hai na a Urshalima nggǝr yi tǝnang ahu ɓeena mahan.’ ”\f + \fr 26:61 \ft Yahaya 2:19\f*
\p 
\v 62 Tǝrgha thliigha mamnda firis sǝ ndanggǝn Yeeso, “Mba mbang nggǝra sǝ wa? Ma na ndaarha aten pathɗi thlǝkna nafini aten wa ya?”
\v 63 Amma nggasgha Yeeso tip. Tǝrgha ndangga mamnda firis, “Na minna sǝ ahu thlǝm Faara natǝ yibrha, pǝranggǝn kan ana sa ni Ƙǝrǝsti, Wan Faara,”
\p 
\v 64 Nggǝrangga Yeeso sǝ, “Pǝr nan. Amma niya ndang nda kun heu a mbee nun a na Wan niifa tsau a yisǝmad Faara Amshi tǝ ƙǝm ɓayi ahu hashmbe a talara hai.”\f + \fr 26:64 \ft Ndaniyel 7:13\f*
\p 
\v 65 Tǝrgha mamnda firis ɗi djaranggǝn luwudghǝn ɗǝ, ndǝghǝn, “Sarɗǝ Faara! Palthma nǝm nggǝr kaɗaarha faɗǝn? Sǝkɗǝm ndǝn hai a miighǝn laɓar sar Faara.\f + \fr 26:65 \ft Ɗeleewar Firistaya 24:16\f*
\v 66 Ma ndaa nun?” Kanda heu ndaa nda, “Kamɗǝ a mǝrgha!”\f + \fr 26:66 \ft Ɗeleewar Firistaya 24:16\f*
\p 
\v 67 Tǝrgha chahang yakhrha nda fa ɗǝkƙǝn nda. Fingya ƙǝm mbighǝnda,\f + \fr 26:67 \ft Ishaya 50:6\f*
\v 68 na nda a ndaarha, “Kulang kansǝ, Ƙǝrǝsti! Wun mbiigha sa?”
\s1 Ngaal Mbiturus sǝnda Yeeso
\r (Markus14:66-72; Luka22:56-62; Yahaya18:15-18,25-27)
\p 
\v 69 Nanǝnya Mbiturus tsau a ƙǝshi a pǝpal minda, kyagha mafad wee nuwun ɓa ndanggǝn, “Sa na tal ahur nafini na a mbu samad Yeeso tǝ Nggalilad ɗi.”
\p 
\v 70 Amma ngaalghǝna Mbiturus a mbed ndan heu. Ndanggǝn, “Sǝngwi ǝnɗi na a thlǝkrha ya wa,”
\v 71 Tsǝɓaku kyagha kwakirma sǝ nggǝrgha mafad wee nuwun naghǝn ndanggǝn fiya na a mbǝɗi, “Niifɗiya kanda ni tǝ Yeeso tǝ Nadzarat.”
\p 
\v 72 Nggǝrgha Mbiturus ngaalghǝn, har tǝ aah thlǝm Faara ndǝghǝn, “Sǝngwi niifɗi nun a thlǝkrha ya wa.”
\p 
\v 73 Nggǝrna nda tsǝrha tsǝɓaku nafini na ƙǝƙǝt a mbǝɗi ɗǝnda thlǝmad Mbiturus ɗǝ ndang ngganda, “Sa mbǝ ngaala sǝ wa na tal ahur ndan, ƙǝsǝr ahu laɓar wa kyadɗǝ ndaarha tǝ Nggalilarha ni sa.”
\p 
\v 74 Tǝrgha nagha Mbiturus a ang shiurha fadghǝn fa ɓa aah nǝn thlǝm Faara a Kanda ndaanǝn, “Sǝngwi niifɗi wa!” Tsu kee tǝtaagha ɗiyarha.
\p 
\v 75 Tǝrgha ɗalgha Mbiturus teena hai tǝ laɓar Yeeso ndang nǝn, “Kapa na ɗiyarha tǝtaarha yi sǝri na ngaal sǝndǝna katǝra mahan.” Kyagha ƙǝshaaɗǝ tǝgha kaan.
\c 27
\s1 Ɗǝnda tǝ Yeeso a mbed Mbilatus ɗǝ
\r (Markus15:1; Luka23:1-2; Yahaya18:28-32)
\p 
\v 1 A tsar ƙǝrǝt, mamnda firistaya tǝ shingya heu, wuma nda hai ka a kaɗa kwaman ɓǝlla Yeeso nda.
\v 2 Kǝnang ngganda, ɗǝnda tǝghǝn a mbed Mbilatus ɗǝ, ngwamnad Romaya.
\s1 Mǝrra Yahuda
\r (Tar fathlǝngya1:18-19)
\p 
\v 3 Kǝlaana Yahuda hai fǝrgha Yeeso, ngwang nda kumad mǝrra Yeeso sǝ. Tǝrgha sǝbgha hurghǝn ɗǝ, haranggǝn wuɗǝɓǝl wuridɗa sǝ kumggit mahan wuɗanggǝnǝn mamnda firistaya ɗǝ tǝ shinggini.
\v 4 Ndanggǝn kanda, “Ənaɗi ɗimiyirha, ƙǝsǝr fǝrɗi niifa ǝnawa ɗimiyirha.” Ndang ngganda, “Mbǝ ˈya sǝ djiɗangwa kan wa, kǝl ˈya ǝnana.”
\p 
\v 5 Tǝrgha Yahuda tsamanggǝn wuɗǝɓǝlɗa hai ahu Ƙǝn Faara, wiigha ɗǝgha waghang altenggǝn sǝ.
\p 
\v 6 Harangga mamnda firistaya wuɗǝɓǝlɗa sǝ, ndaa nda, “Kamngwa a ɗǝfanggǝm wuɗǝɓǝlɗi ya a mbǝd ɗǝfǝd yi Ƙǝn hwan Faara wa, nanǝn wuɗǝbǝl ƙǝna ɓǝl farha ni.”
\v 7 A kwasamadghǝn ƙǝnang ngganda hai na nda a hii pǝpal yi taɓǝd tǝn ɓǝya sǝ tǝ wuɗǝɓǝlɗi, tsawang ngganda mbǝɗi, mbǝd ten kwad rongya.
\v 8 Ndǝn na nda aah mbǝɗi, Pǝpal fara.
\p 
\v 9 Tǝrgha lǝghǝdgha ˈya ndana annabi Irmiya ndanǝn, “Tǝrang ngganda wuɗǝɓǝl wuridɗa sǝ kumggit mahan, wuɗǝɓǝlɗi kyana nafiya Isǝreela.
\v 10 Hii mbǝd taɓǝd tǝn ɓǝya nda sǝ kǝla ndaana Chinǝm”.
\s1 Tsahang Mbilatus mee Yeeso
\r (Markus15:2-5; Luka23:3-5; Yahaya18:33-38)
\p 
\v 11 Nana Yeeso ƙǝt a mbed Mbilatus ngwamnad Romaya, tsahangga ngwamnaɗi mee, “Sani kutǝr Yahudaya wa?” Nggǝrangga Yeeso sǝ, “Ooh, ƙǝla ndaana.”
\p 
\v 12 Amma nana mamngya firistaya tǝ shingya a ˈyarghǝn, nagha Yeeso tip fayighǝn.
\p 
\v 13 Ndangga Mbilatus, “Mbuwana a sǝk ǝnɗi na nda a thlǝkrha atenwa wa?”
\p 
\v 14 Amma nggǝrang ngwa Yeeso kanda sǝ aten ǝnggini heu thlǝk nanda wa, ƙǝsgha ǝnwulteena ngwamnaɗi kaan.
\s1 Ngwang nda kumad mǝrra Yeeso sǝ
\r (Markus15:6-15; Luka23:13-25; Yahaya18:39,40; 19:16)
\p 
\v 15 Nanǝnya ǝntin ngwamna ɗa ni nǝn yakh kalang niifa kanda hai tal na ahu porsǝna na min ndan a far wutsǝfayid Tǝɗaarha.
\v 16 Ahu sayidɗi na niifa sǝ na tǝmbǝng, ƙǝnang na nda ahu porsǝna, na nda aarha Mbarabas.
\v 17 Tsaunǝn wum fiya hai a kwakirǝm Mbilatus, tsahangga Mbilatus mee kanda, “Wun na minnun a kalang nggǝni kun hai, Mbarabas wa, nduwa Yeeso nanda aarha Ƙǝrǝsti wa?”
\v 18 Sǝn ɗa sǝ ƙǝsang na shingya Yeeso ƙǝsǝr ka sǝrǝkrha.
\p 
\v 19 Nana Mbilatus tsau a mbǝd tsawud ngwa kumarha, thlǝngga nukƙun farha a thlǝmadghǝn ɗǝ a ndang ngganda, “Ma ǝnangna ˈya ka niifɗa fa ya wa ƙǝsǝr sǝsaaɗi kaan hu sǝsǝniirha atenggǝn a fǝɗik weeriya.”
\p 
\v 20 Amma mamngya firistaya tǝ shingya shik fiya nda, a ndang ngganda a kal Mbarabas nǝn hai, ɓǝlang ngganda Yeeso.
\v 21 Nggǝrgha kutǝr ɗi tsakh mee, “Wun na minnun a kalang nggǝni kun hai ahur nafiyini na kyab ya?” Tǝrangga fiya urad ndan sǝ, “Mbarabas!”
\p 
\v 22 Ndangga Mbilatus kanda, “Mani ǝnaarha tǝ Yeeso na nda aarha Ƙǝrǝsti?” Tǝrang ngganda urad ndan sǝ, “Tawaman ɗǝ!”
\p 
\v 23 Ndangga Mbilatus kanda, “Kama nda? Ma ǝnanǝn na ɗimi?” Amma nagha fiya a tǝrang urad ndan sǝ, “Tawaman ɗǝ!”
\p 
\v 24 “Ƙǝlaana Mbilatus hai mbǝ ˈyasǝ nǝn mbang ǝnaarha wa, na nda a katǝrang kakyathlaanga. Tǝrgha thlǝn farha nǝn a ɓang aama nda ɓa tsaɓanggǝn harghǝn ɗǝ a mbed fiya, ndagha, Nggi, mbǝ harna tsuwar faar ka niifa fa wa. Kun ndǝn sǝngga ǝnnun.”
\p 
\v 25 Nggǝmangga fiya heu, “Ngwa tsauka hakked farghǝn aten nan, kan tǝ wagginan!”
\p 
\v 26 Tǝrgha Mbilatus kalang Mbarabas nǝn kanda hai. Fǝr Yeeso nǝn tsaɗa ghǝnda tǝ wutǝteerha, fǝranggǝnǝn sodjad Romaya ka ɗanda tawang ɗǝ.
\s1 Waa sodjaya Yeeso
\r (Markus15:16-20; Yahaya19:2-3)
\p 
\v 27 Fingya sodjaya ngwamnaɗi tǝrangga nda Yeeso a mbǝd tar ndan ɗǝ, aah sodjaya nda ɓa heu.
\v 28 Ƙǝɗangga nda lukkighǝn hai, kalang kaɓarha nda fa yiɓa.
\v 29 Yam wuhar ndakhkya nda ƙǝla matuwel, panggǝnda atenggǝn, fǝrang sǝsal kutǝryirha nda a yisǝmadghǝn. Ɓǝra nda hai a mbedghǝn waaghǝn nda, na nda a ndangˈya, “Alvari, kutǝr Yahudaya!”
\v 30 Chahang yakhrha nda fa, thlǝ sǝsal ɗa nda na nda a ɗǝkƙǝn sǝ a tenggǝn.
\v 31 Ɗakhna mindan ɗǝ tǝ waaghǝn, ƙǝɗang ngganda kaɓadɗa hai a fadghǝn, nggǝrgha nda kalang yighǝn lukrha fa. Tǝrgha wii nda tǝghǝn ka ɗa nda tawang ɗǝ.
\s1 Tawang nda Yeeso ɗǝ
\r (Markus15:21-32; Luka23:26-43; Yahaya19:17-27)
\p 
\v 32 Nana nda aten wiirha, ɗa nda wal tǝ Sayirarha, thlǝmnggǝn ni Siman, ngyaɓang tǝr kaɗidɗa nda fa.
\v 33 Sǝlna nda a mbǝrha ɓa nanda aarha Nggolggota, ndaarha ni mbǝd ɓalhwar teena,
\v 34 Fǝrangga sodja yini aam inabi nda kukurɗa tǝ ˈya na iˈikh, amma taarang nǝn, kar sad ghǝnǝn.
\p 
\v 35 A kwasamadɗi tawang na nda ɗǝ, ndǝghang ngganda lukkighǝn hai tǝ ǝna chacha.
\v 36 Tǝrgha tsawa nda hai a mbǝɗi, nanda a ƙǝlaghǝn ha.
\v 37 Chireelth ǝn sak ɗimiyidghǝn nda a man tenggǝn tǝ ndaarha, “KULO YEESO YA, KUTƏR YAHUDAYA!”
\v 38 Na fathlee kwamangya sǝ sǝri tawang na nda kanda ɗǝ a thlǝmadghǝn, tal a man yisǝmadghǝn, tal a yikawa.
\p 
\v 39 Nagha fiya na a mbǝra ɗǝ a huhwang nda, na nda a tsang ˈya ten ndan fa yi waa farha.
\v 40 Na nda a ndaarha, “Ndaana na mbang chang wuri Faara hai na a Urshalima tǝnangga sǝ hu paara mahan, ana Wan Faara ni sa, hǝrghang altenwa lee tǝra na hai a ten kaɗidɗiya!”
\p 
\v 41 Mamngya firistaya tǝ famalǝmgya ngyakhrha Musa, tǝ shingya ƙǝm waa Yeeso nda.
\v 42 “Hǝrghang ɗǝ fingya, amma mbangwa hǝrghang nda altenggǝn wa. Ana ndǝghǝn ni kutǝr Isǝreela! Tǝrgha hai a ten kaɗidɗi nanǝnya lee, nǝm a fǝrƙǝkafek a ndǝghǝn.
\v 43 Fǝrɗǝ ƙǝkafek a Faara, ngwa hǝrghangga Faara nanǝnya anaɗǝ na midghǝn sǝ! Ƙǝsǝr ndǝghǝn, Wan Faara ni nggi.”
\p 
\v 44 Ko fa thlee kwaman nggina ni tawang na nda kanda ɗǝ tǝghǝn, waa ghǝnda kǝla ǝnana fiya.
\s1 Mǝrra Yeeso
\r (Markus15:33-41; Luka23:44-49; Yahaya19:28-30; Markus15:16-20; Yahaya19:2-3)
\p 
\v 45 Yanfara a sǝrǝkrha, nggǝlangga wula chehwedɗi heu har yargha yanfaara hai.
\v 46 Yarna yanfaara hai kalgha Yeeso sǝ tǝ urarha manggǝn, “Eloi, Eloi, lama sabaktani?” Ndaarha ni, “Faarna, Faarna, kama karna nggi?”
\p 
\v 47 Fingya na ƙǝƙǝt a mbǝɗi sǝngwa nda sǝwa tamngga nda ndaarha nanǝn a aah annabi Ilya.
\v 48 Ɗagha niifa ɗǝ tal ahur ndan tǝtǝnanggǝn soso tǝ aam inabi na chichakh, panggǝn hu sǝsaala hai fǝranggǝnǝn sǝ ka a saagha.
\p 
\v 49 Amma ndagha fingya, malaman, ƙǝlaghǝnǝm ha, asǝmha ɓana Ilya hǝrghang nda.
\p 
\v 50 Tǝrgha nggǝrgha Yeeso tǝrang uradghǝn sǝ kaan tǝgha, mbǝ kal yiɓǝdghǝnǝn hai.
\p 
\v 51 A mǝmǝlla sayidɗi djargha shishamar Ƙǝn Faara hai sǝri, a talara hai ta hweeɗe hai. Rǝbgha ƙǝshiirha fa, fǝlgha ferya ɗǝ.
\v 52 Ingga ten kwaya ɗǝ, ka nafiya Faara hangga mǝrgha, thlii nda sǝ.
\v 53 Kyanda sǝ ahu ten kwaya, a kwasamadɗi thliina Yeeso sǝ ahu mǝrra, ɗǝnda ahu wupǝri ɗǝ tǝ peɗǝnda, kyad fandan nda a fiya hangga.
\p 
\v 54 Mamnda sodja Romaya tǝ fingya sodjaya na a ƙǝla Yeeso ha, nana nda rǝbrha chehwedɗi tǝ ǝngya heu katǝrarha hai tǝrma nda, ndaa nda, “Ƙǝkafek niifɗiya Wan Faara ni!”
\p 
\v 55 Tǝ nishya hangga ɓagha ɓa mbuwa samad Yeeso a Nggalili ɓa ka a ndang ngganda sǝ tǝ ˈya na midghǝn na nda a ƙǝlarha ɓa inggun.
\v 56 Ahur ndan na Mairamu Magdaliya sǝ, tǝ Mairamu man nda Yakubu tǝ Yisǝfu, tǝ man nda Yakubu tǝ Yahaya, wangya Dzabadi.
\s1 Pang nda Yeeso
\r (Markus15:42-47; Luka23:50-56; Yahaya19:38-42)
\p 
\v 57 Tsǝna figrha hai, na tǝ ƙǝna sǝ ɓagha ɓa a Aramatiya, thlǝmnggǝn ni Yisǝfu, tsauka tǝ takkwa Yeeso,
\v 58 ɗǝgha thlǝmad Mbilatus ɗǝ tsakh mǝrra Yeeso nǝn, ndagha Mbilatus fǝraman ndǝghǝn.
\v 59 Tǝrangga Yisǝfu mǝrɗi faɗanggǝn hu kaɓaarha hai na ngga pǝpet.
\v 60 Ɗǝgha pang ahu yighǝn weerǝnda ten kwarha hai ranǝn ahu feera. Tǝrgha kwatǝranggǝn feera ɓa na manggǝn, nggǝlanggǝn mii tenkwadɗa sǝ wiigha.
\v 61 Nda Mairamu Magdaliya tǝ tahad Mairamu ɗi kanda tsǝtsau a mii ten kwadɗi kanda a naghǝn.
\s1 Fa ƙǝla tenkwadɗa ha
\p 
\v 62 Ɗathna mbǝrha hai a far yiɓǝd Yahudaya, Mamnda firistaya tǝ farisaya ɗǝnda thlǝmad Mbilatus ɗǝ.
\v 63 Ndang ngganda, “Alvari, ɗal ɗan teena hai aten ˈya ndaana tǝnggaɓad ɗi ndǝghǝn ɓalɗǝ tǝ yibrha, ‘A kwasamad ɓeena mahan nǝn a thliirha sǝ ahu mǝrra.’
\v 64 Nanǝn kee furu kwamana a ƙǝla ten kwadɗa ndaha yi ɓeena mahan. A mbǝ kee wa ɓana fatsahayighǝn ngaarang, ndangganda fiya thliinǝn sǝ ahu mǝrra.”
\p 
\v 65 Ndangga Mbilatus kanda, “Harama sodjaya ƙǝla mbǝɗaha, ngga.”
\p 
\v 66 Nanǝn kee mǝlɗeng ngganda ten kwadɗi, sǝ sodjaya nda sǝ na ƙǝlaghǝn ha.
\c 28
\s1 Thlid Yeeso sǝ ahu mǝrra
\r (Markus16:1-8; Luka24:1-12; Yahaya20:1-10)
\p 
\v 1 A kwasamad far yiɓǝd Yahudaya, a tsar ƙǝrǝt a far ladi Mairamu magdaliya tǝ tahad Mairamu wii nda ka ƙǝlang tenkwadɗa ɗǝ.
\v 2 Kula sǝndǝndan sǝ rǝbgha hweeɗe fa kaan, ƙǝsǝr tǝthlǝnda Faara tǝrgha hai a talara, kwatǝranggǝn ferɗi a man patu ɗǝ, tsauka a tenggǝn.
\v 3 Nagha pǝmnggǝn a chimnda fa ƙǝla yan fara, lukkighǝn ƙǝm pǝpet ƙǝla humba kaɓarha.
\v 4 Tǝrǝmngga nafini na a ƙǝla ten kwadɗa ha, nagha fandan a rǝbrha fa, muwa nda hweeɗe hai, shiwit kanda nǝn in.
\p 
\v 5 Tǝrgha kalangga tǝthlǝndǝ ɗi nishyina sǝ, ndǝghǝn, “Ma tǝrǝm ɗun wa sǝnɗisǝ nun a kaɗa Yeeso, tawang nanda ɗǝ.
\v 6 Mbǝ a mbǝɗiya wa, thliiɗa sǝ ahu mǝrra, ƙǝla ndaanǝn nǝn a katǝrarha hai. Ɓamaɓa, ɓun na mbǝɗi huna nǝn sahai.
\v 7 Nanǝnya, weema ƙǝkar ɗun thlǝghanggǝn fatsahayighǝn tǝ ndaarha thliiɗasǝ ahu mǝrra, nǝn a mbed nun ɗǝnǝn Nggalili ɗǝ. Ɗǝnun naghǝn a mbǝɗi. Ɗalama teena hai tǝ ˈya ndang ni kun.”
\p 
\v 8 Ɗagha nishyini ƙǝkar ma ten kwadɗi, tǝrǝm nda kaan amma naa nda lǝlǝgɗa tǝ wutsǝfayirha fa, nagha pǝr laɓarɗi a kukwasang kanda fa pǝrang na tǝthlǝndǝɗi kanda a fatsahayighǝn.
\v 9 Ɓa Yeeso wal kanda, ndang ˈya nǝn kanda. Ɓa nda thlǝmadghǝn ɓa, fǝb saryighǝn nda fa, manangganda thlǝmnggǝn.
\v 10 Tǝrgha ndangga Yeeso kanda, “Ma tǝrǝm ɗun wa, ɗama ɗǝ ndanggun wanmanggina ɓanda a Nggalili ɓa, ɓana nda na nggi a mbǝɗi.”
\s1 ˈYa thlǝkna fa ƙǝla ten kwadɗa ha
\p 
\v 11 Nana nishyini a ten kwamana, fingya fa kǝla mbǝɗaha ɗǝnda ahur wupǝri ɗǝ thlǝghang ǝnɗa nda mamnda firistaya ǝnɗi katǝragha hai heu.
\v 12 Aah shingya nda wuma nda hai, ƙǝnangganda hai na nda a fǝrang wuɗǝɓǝla kanda manggǝn.
\v 13 “Ndang ngganda sodja yini, ‘A ndaama, fa tsahaya Yeeso ɓagha ɓa a fǝɗikrha nanan a ɓeena, ngaarang ngganda mǝrrǝghǝn.’
\v 14 A sǝk ngwamna laɓarɗiya, kan ƙǝm nan a isha a mbed nun, amanun sǝsarha.”
\p 
\v 15 Tǝrgha sodja yini ƙǝm thlǝ wuɗǝɓǝlɗa nda ǝna nda ƙǝla saghang nanda kanda. Ɗǝgha laɓar ɗaɗǝ inggun ahur Yahudaya, ɓagha ta weeri ɗaɓa ya.
\s1 Taara fǝrang na Yeeso fatsahayighǝn
\r (Markus16:14-18; Luka24:36-49; Yahaya20:19-23; Tar fathlǝngya1:6-8)
\p 
\v 16 Tǝrgha fatsahayini kumkap tal ɗǝnda Nggalili ɗǝ, tǝra nda wumnda sǝ ndangna Yeeso kanda.\f + \fr 28:16 \ft Matta 26:32; Markus 14:28\f*
\v 17 Nana ndan manang ngganda thlǝmnggǝn, amma fingya sǝ ngalgha ndǝn.
\v 18 Ɓagha Yeeso ɓa ndanggǝn fatsahayighǝn, “Fǝreenda sǝsǝmnggit talara tǝ yi hweeɗe heu.
\v 19 Tsaunǝn kee ɗaama ɗǝ, ɗun tsahang fiya ha heu, ǝnang mbaptisǝma nun kanda, hu thlǝm Pǝpa tǝ yi Wee, tǝ yi Sǝsǝna tǝ Peɗǝnda.\f + \fr 28:19 \ft Tar Fathlǝngya 1:8\f*
\v 20 Tsahaman kanda ha a ǝna taara nda tǝ ǝngya heu ndang ni kun. A sǝnunsǝ niyi tǝ kun ƙǝtsar ta mii ngwala ƙǝshiirha ɗǝ.”
